NK067(ju)004:1: // rat+na ko sha s+y+aa k+sha dar+sha ka n+aa ma sh+r+ai
NK067(ju)004:2: gu h+ya ga r+b+ha s+ya ta n+t+ra s+ya sa m+aa
NK067(ju)004:3: n+aa r+tha la g+hu w+aa gem bi b+he d+aa sti
NK067(ju)004:6: // // dpal gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud kyi spyi don nyung
NK067(ju)004:7: ngu'i ngag gis rnam par 'byed pa rin chen mdzod
NK067(ju)004:8: kyi lde mig ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK067(ju)004:11: // na mo gu ru sh+r+ai m+aam badz+ra sa t+w+aa ya /
NK067(ju)004:14: // dpal ldan bla ma rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK067(ju)004:16: sdeb sbyor mnyam pa'i brit+ta'i nang tshan phyed mnyam pa'i pras+t+aa ras kun nas mdzes par bcings pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:19: // pa ra m+aa r+tha d+h+aa tu bi bri t+aa d+ha
NK067(ju)004:20: k+ta bi ng+k+aa ya ba dz+ra si d+d+ha te dza
NK067(ju)004:22: don dam dbyings dang sgrib bral rig pa'i sku //
NK067(ju)004:23: mi phyed rdo rje grub pa'i gzi brjid sprin //
NK067(ju)004:26: // na ma m+aa ya dz+aa la gu ru k+aa y+aam
NK067(ju)004:27: sha tsa kre sha k+aa ra ta n+t+ra se na
NK067(ju)004:29: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skur mdzad rgyud sde'i dbyangs //
NK067(ju)004:30: kun khyab 'khor lo'i dbang phyug bla mar 'dud //
NK067(ju)004:32: gsang mchog rgyud sde'i snang bas gdul bya'i gling //
NK067(ju)004:33: grub gnyis lang tsho rgyas pa'i pad tshal du //
NK067(ju)004:34: grub mdzad brgyud gsum bla ma'i nyin mor byed //
NK067(ju)004:35: yid mkha'i ngos la brtan par bzhugs gyur cig /
NK067(ju)004:36: rgyud don zab mo bdag 'dras dpag dka' yang //
NK067(ju)004:37: skyes bu'i brjod pa'i rjes 'brangs brag cha ltar //
NK067(ju)004:38: brgyud ldan bla ma'i legs bshad la brten nas //
NK067(ju)004:39: cha tsam gleng 'dir gzu bo'i blo yis nyon //
NK067(ju)004:40: 'dir snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi bstan pa rgya mtsho'i nang mdzod /
NK067(ju)004:41: gsang sngag chu bo bzhi'i 'byung gnas /
NK067(ju)004:42: rgyud lung man ngag thams cad kyi srog shing /
NK067(ju)004:43: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mthar thug gi snying po bcud du dril ba /
NK067(ju)004:44: sems dang ye shes rang snang bden pa dbyer med
NK067(ju)004:45: du ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK067(ju)004:46: ba gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK067(ju)004:47: pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po'i spyi don gyi rnam bzhag
NK067(ju)004:48: cung zad brjed byang du 'god pa la gsum ste
NK067(ju)004:49: / ston pas ji ltar gsungs tshul /
NK067(ju)004:50: de las ji ltar brgyud tshul /
NK067(ju)004:51: brgyud pa de ldan gyi rgyud don dngos bshad pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:53: 'o skol rnams kyi ston pa bdag nyid sred pa'i 'ching ba mtha' dag las grol yang /
NK067(ju)004:54: sems can 'khor ba'i gzeb tu chud cing rmongs pa'i mun nag stug pos non pa /
NK067(ju)004:55: nges par 'byung ba'i phyogs yongs su mi shes pa
NK067(ju)004:56: rnams la thugs rje chen po'i gzhan dbang du gyur
NK067(ju)004:57: te / nyi ma bye ba phrag brgya'i 'od kyis
NK067(ju)004:58: mi mtshon pa'i dam pa'i chos kyi snang ba rlabs
NK067(ju)004:59: po che 'gyed pa'i slad du skye rgu tshe lo
NK067(ju)004:60: brgya pa la babs pa'i dus su rigs thams cad
NK067(ju)004:61: las rgyal mtshan gyi tog ltar mtho ba sh+aakya'i rigs
NK067(ju)004:62: kyi rgyal po zas gtsang ma'i sras su skye ba'i
NK067(ju)004:63: pad+mo'i dbang 'byor gyi yon tan mtha' yas pa'i rgyan
NK067(ju)004:65: sh+aakya thub pa'am sh+aakya seng ge zhes snyan pa'i ba
NK067(ju)004:66: dan dkar po sa gsum na mngon par gsal ba
NK067(ju)004:67: des / dang por gzhon nu'i rol rtsed dang /
NK067(ju)004:69: btsun mo'i 'khor du bzhugs pa la sogs pa 'jig
NK067(ju)004:70: rten gyi spyod pa'i tshul dang mthun pa'i thabs mkhas
NK067(ju)004:71: pa mang pos sems can yongs su smin par mdzad
NK067(ju)004:72: nas / lo nyi shu rtsa dgu bzhes pa na rgyal po'i srid 'byor spangs te rab tu byung /
NK067(ju)004:73: klung nee rany+dza na'i 'gram du dka' thub mdzad cing
NK067(ju)004:74: bzhugs pa'i tshe phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskul nas
NK067(ju)004:75: btags pa'i lus der bzhag ste ye shes kyi lus
NK067(ju)004:76: 'og min du gshegs nas mngon byang lngas byang chub
NK067(ju)004:77: brnyes / de nas ri rab kyi rtse dang /
NK067(ju)004:80: za hor rnams su gshegs nas 'khor dag pa rnams
NK067(ju)004:81: la 'di nyid la sogs pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud
NK067(ju)004:83: slar btags pa'i lus la zhugs nas byang chub snying
NK067(ju)004:84: por gshegs pa sogs mdzad pa lhag ma rnams mthun
NK067(ju)004:85: snang du bstan / de ltar sprul pa'i skus gsang sngags bstan pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:86: 'og min du longs skus gsang sngags bstan pa gnyis
NK067(ju)004:87: byad dang gzugs brnyan lta bu yin pas phyi ma'i
NK067(ju)004:88: gnas skabs spangs nas snga mar mdzad pa ni ma
NK067(ju)004:89: yin te / slob dpon nyi 'od seng ges rgya cher 'grel du bshad tshul lo //
NK067(ju)004:90: ston pas mi yul du byang chub brnyes pa'i mdzad
NK067(ju)004:91: pa bstan nas theg pa thun mong gi chos 'khor
NK067(ju)004:92: bskyor ba'i dus su longs skus 'og min du rgyud
NK067(ju)004:93: gsungs pa'i phyogs ni sgeg pa rdo rjes spar khab
NK067(ju)004:95: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po yang phyi ma dang mthun par bzhed de /
NK067(ju)004:96: gang du rgyud gsungs pa'i 'og min de la dbang
NK067(ju)004:97: phyug chen po'i 'og min te longs sku'i zhing gi
NK067(ju)004:98: 'og min dang / de'i rjes mthun sprul sku'i 'og min gnyis yod cing /
NK067(ju)004:99: phyi ma la'ang phyed sprul longs skur grags pa rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams dang /
NK067(ju)004:100: gtsang ris lha gnas kyi 'og min gnyis gsungs so //
NK067(ju)004:101: bshad tshul de dag gang yang mi 'gal te /
NK067(ju)004:102: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam 'phrul gyi yul bsam gyis
NK067(ju)004:103: mi khyab pa'i phyir ro zhes mkhas pa dag gsung
NK067(ju)004:104: ngo // spar khab tu bshad tshul 'di la brten nas snga ma kha cig /
NK067(ju)004:105: mi yul du sprul skus thun mong gi theg pa
NK067(ju)004:106: tsam las ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud ma gsungs bar
NK067(ju)004:108: rtsa rgyud nyid las sprul sku'i mdzad pa 'dul ba bzhi'i nang tshan gsung gis 'dul ba'i skabs su /
NK067(ju)004:109: bla na med pa'i theg pa dang zhes gsungs pa sogs dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:110: 'og min du gsungs tshul ni le'u dang pos dngos
NK067(ju)004:111: bstan gtso bo yin pas longs sprul gyis gsungs tshul
NK067(ju)004:112: gnyis ka na gsal ba yin no //
NK067(ju)004:113: gnyis pa la brgyud gsum spyi'i rnam bzhag dang /
NK067(ju)004:114: so so'i ngos 'dzin phyes te bshad pa gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:117: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK067(ju)004:118: dgongs pa rig pa rna par brgyud //
NK067(ju)004:120: gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba'i brda chad thun mong ma yin pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:121: de la rgyal ba dgongs brgyud ni gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:122: dper na nam mkha'i zla ba gcig pu la ri
NK067(ju)004:123: bong gi gzugs yod pa nyid kyis chu zla ji
NK067(ju)004:124: snyed shar ba thams cad ri bong gi rgyan dang
NK067(ju)004:125: ldan par snang ba bzhin du /
NK067(ju)004:126: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs drug pas rgyud don mthar
NK067(ju)004:127: phyin par brnyes pa nyid kyis de las sprul pa'i
NK067(ju)004:129: sems dpa' yab yum zhi khro'i 'khor thams cad rgyud don brnyes par 'jog nus te /
NK067(ju)004:130: de ni gtso 'khor dgongs pa gcig gis brgyud pa yin no //
NK067(ju)004:131: ston pa dang rgyud tha dad pa'i lhan cig pa'i
NK067(ju)004:132: 'khor rnams la zab dbang bskur ba'i dgongs pa mdzad
NK067(ju)004:133: pas ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pa'ang
NK067(ju)004:134: dgongs brgyud kyi tshul gcig go //
NK067(ju)004:135: sems dpa' rig brgyud ces pa ni /
NK067(ju)004:136: gzhan du rig 'dzin brda brgyud ces 'byung ba dang mthun te /
NK067(ju)004:137: 'chad pa po dag pa'i sems dpa' sngags kyi ye
NK067(ju)004:138: shes las grub pa'i sku brnyes pas rgyud yongs su
NK067(ju)004:139: smin pa'i byang sems kyi 'khor la thugs rig pa'i
NK067(ju)004:140: ye shes kyi dgongs pa gtad nas sngags dang phyag
NK067(ju)004:141: rgya'i brda thabs bstan pa tsam gyi de'i mod la
NK067(ju)004:142: 'khor gyi rgyud don mtha' dag rtogs pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:143: 'di yang dgongs pa don brgyud khyad par can yin yang /
NK067(ju)004:144: rgyal ba dgongs brgyud kyi brgyud tshul las gzhan du
NK067(ju)004:145: go ba'i ched du dgongs brgyud ces ma smos par
NK067(ju)004:146: rigs pa'i brgyud pa zhes pa'i brda sbyar ba yin
NK067(ju)004:147: no // rnal 'byor rna brgyud ces pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK067(ju)004:148: dang po nas rig sngags kyi lhar bzhengs pa lta
NK067(ju)004:149: bu ma yin par tha mal pa'i rten bzung nas
NK067(ju)004:150: lam bsgoms te drod ci rigs thob pa yan chad
NK067(ju)004:151: de / 'di ni thun mong gdul bya'i snang tshod dbang btsan par bya'i /
NK067(ju)004:152: gnas tshod ltar na 'di'i rnal 'byor pa la rgyal ba dang sems dapa'ang yod de /
NK067(ju)004:153: slob dpon chen po pad+ma bzhin no //
NK067(ju)004:154: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa snga ma snga ma'i
NK067(ju)004:155: zhal nas phyi ma phyi ma'i snyan du dbang rgyud
NK067(ju)004:156: man ngag rim bzhin brgyud pa ni rna brgyud do
NK067(ju)004:157: // sangs rgyas nang phan tshun la'ang slob pa'i rna
NK067(ju)004:158: brgyud 'dra ba med kyang snyan du brgyud tshul tsam
NK067(ju)004:159: yod pa mi 'gal bar kun mkhyen chen pos gsungs
NK067(ju)004:160: shing mdo rgyud du ma'i lung gis kyang grub pas
NK067(ju)004:161: // / rgyal ba la dgongs brgyud kho na dang
NK067(ju)004:162: sems dpa' la rig brgyud kho na zhes bshad mi
NK067(ju)004:163: // / rung ngo // des na rnal 'byor ba la rna brgyud gtso /
NK067(ju)004:164: sems dpa' nas brgyud tshul thun min rig pa'i brgyud pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:165: sangs rgyas dngos kyis brgyud tshul thun min dgongs brgyud yin ces bshad par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:171: ston pa rigs drug pas rgyal tshab rigs lnga sogs dang /
NK067(ju)004:172: rigs lngas lhan cig pa'i 'khor la brgyud pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:174: mi ma yin la brgyud pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:175: mi dang mi min gnyis ka la brgyud pa gnyis /
NK067(ju)004:177: rgyal sras rigs gsum sems dpas lha klu gnod sbyin
NK067(ju)004:178: gyi rig 'dzin grags ldan mchog skyong sogs gsum la
NK067(ju)004:180: rgyal ba zhi bar gzims nas lo nyer brgyad 'das
NK067(ju)004:181: pa na dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga lang+ka'i
NK067(ju)004:182: yul gyi grong brdal gyi mtsho gling ri ma la
NK067(ju)004:183: ya'i rtse mor rdzu 'phrul gyis 'dus te /
NK067(ju)004:184: sangs rgyas la dmigs nas gdung dbyangs blangs pas dpal
NK067(ju)004:185: phyag na rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas rgyud
NK067(ju)004:187: mi yul du rgyud 'di thog mar byung tshul dang /
NK067(ju)004:188: de las ji ltar brgyud tshul gnyis /
NK067(ju)004:190: bshad ma thag pa ltar gsang bdag gis bka' bsdu
NK067(ju)004:191: mdzad pa'i tshe de'i byin rlabs kyis sa ho ra'i
NK067(ju)004:192: rgyal po dzahste in+t+ra b+hu ti la /
NK067(ju)004:193: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:194: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:195: chos kyi bgro ba byed pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:196: kun gyis dam par bsgrags pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:197: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:198: rin chen char du babs pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:199: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:200: zhes pa'i rmi ltas bdun byung zhing /
NK067(ju)004:201: de dang mthun par pho brang gi steng du rgyud
NK067(ju)004:202: sde'i glegs bam dang phyag na rdo rje'i sku khru
NK067(ju)004:203: gang ba dngos su babs te gsol ba btab pas
NK067(ju)004:204: sngon gsang sngags la sbyangs pa'i 'phro sad de rdor
NK067(ju)004:205: sems zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs nas de dang phyag
NK067(ju)004:206: rdor gyi sku la brten te zla ba drug bsgrubs
NK067(ju)004:207: pas rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mjal zhing byin gyis
NK067(ju)004:208: brlabsa pas glegs bam gyi don mtha' dag mkhyen par
NK067(ju)004:210: rgyal po des ku ku r+aa dza la bshad /
NK067(ju)004:211: de nas rim bzhin in+t+ra b+hu ti /
NK067(ju)004:214: sras mo go ma d+ae wi'i bar du brgyud de /
NK067(ju)004:215: de rnams ni tshom bu dang bcas te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs pa sha stag go //
NK067(ju)004:216: go ma d+ae wis sgeg rdor dang sangs rgyas gsang ba la bshad /
NK067(ju)004:217: sangs rgyas gsang bas slob dpon chen po pad+ma dang
NK067(ju)004:218: bi ma mi tra la gdams te 'phags yul du
NK067(ju)004:221: slob dpon pad+mas rje 'bangs 'dus pa la lta phreng
NK067(ju)004:222: gsungs pa sogs de las brgyud pa'ang yod par snang
NK067(ju)004:223: mod / go nga ma rnams la grags che ba ni /
NK067(ju)004:224: bi ma las rma gnyags gnyis la gdams /
NK067(ju)004:225: de gnyis nas brgyud pa'i chu bo gsum du gyes
NK067(ju)004:226: pa gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes la gcig tu 'dres
NK067(ju)004:227: / des gnubs yon tan rgya mtsho dang so ye shes dbang phyug la bshad /
NK067(ju)004:228: de gnyis ka la nyang shes rab mchog gis zhus de nas nyang ye shes 'byung gnas /
NK067(ju)004:232: sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge'i bar du brgyud /
NK067(ju)004:233: gnyags gnubs zur gsum de dag la gsang sngags kyi babs so gsum du grags /
NK067(ju)004:234: sgro phug pa la thugs zin gyi slob ma bcu
NK067(ju)004:235: gnyis gdugs thogs kyi slob ma grwa sa 'dzin pa
NK067(ju)004:236: stong sogs byung ste rgyud 'di'i phrin las phyogs med
NK067(ju)004:237: du brdal / de'i slob brgyud gtsang nag 'od 'bar /
NK067(ju)004:244: sgrol chen sangs rgyas rin chen /
NK067(ju)004:245: 'gos lo chen po gzhon nu dpal /
NK067(ju)004:246: karma zhwa dmar bzhi ba chos kyi grags pa /
NK067(ju)004:248: rang grol nyi zla sangs rgyas /
NK067(ju)004:249: 'khon jo sras tshe dbang nor rgyas /
NK067(ju)004:251: zur chen bkra shis kun dga' /
NK067(ju)004:252: dar sdings rig 'dzin phrin las lhun grub /
NK067(ju)004:253: gter chen chos kyi rgyal po 'gyur med rdo rje /
NK067(ju)004:254: de la lo chen d+harma sh+r+ais gsan /
NK067(ju)004:255: gter chen sku mched 'di gnyis thugs sras dang bcas pas rgyud 'di'i dbang dang /
NK067(ju)004:259: mtha' dpyod sogs rin po che'i sgron me lta bu'i legs bshad mang du mdzad cing /
NK067(ju)004:260: 'chad nyan gyi rgyun btsugs pas bstan pa la bka' drin bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK067(ju)004:261: de nas rim par brgyud de mkhas grub dam pa
NK067(ju)004:262: dge rtse bsod nams bstan 'dzin nam 'jigs med ngo
NK067(ju)004:263: mtshar nas / rdo rje 'dzin pa pad+ma bkra shis /
NK067(ju)004:264: de la rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas kyis gsan /
NK067(ju)004:265: des bdag cag gi bla ma 'phags pa 'jam dpal
NK067(ju)004:266: gyis thugs sras kun mkhyen sprul pa'i sku o rgyan
NK067(ju)004:267: 'jigs med chos kyi dbang po dang /
NK067(ju)004:268: dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag mkhan chen rdo rje
NK067(ju)004:269: 'chang pad+ma dam chos 'od zer dpal bzang po gnyis
NK067(ju)004:270: la stsal cing / snga mas rdo rje 'dzin pa bsod nams rnam rgyal dang /
NK067(ju)004:271: phyi mas rnam 'dren rje btsun dam pa mi pham
NK067(ju)004:272: rnam rgyal rin po cher gdams pa nas kyang brgyud
NK067(ju)004:273: de / mdor na kho bo 'ba' zhig ma gtogs
NK067(ju)004:274: pa rgyud sde'i gnas la sbyangs bas mkhas pa'i go
NK067(ju)004:275: de / 'phang brnyes shing / 'khor lo'i lha la bsnyen pa las su rung ba /
NK067(ju)004:276: rim gnyis kyi rtogs pa'i drod thob pa'i rnal 'byor
NK067(ju)004:277: dbang phyug gi phreng ba bar ma chad pa brgyud
NK067(ju)004:278: pa las da lta'i bar du dbang gi chu bo
NK067(ju)004:279: ma skam / bshad pa'i sgron me ma nub /
NK067(ju)004:280: byin rlabs kyi gzi 'od ma yal bar byon pa yin no //
NK067(ju)004:281: lo rgyus 'di dag gi zhib cha ni gzhan las shes par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:283: bshad bya 'chad byed 'chad tshul gsum gyi rnam bzhag mdo tsam brjod pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:286: spyir gsang sngags bla med la /
NK067(ju)004:289: a ti yo ga'i rgyud sde gsum ste /
NK067(ju)004:290: de gsum gyi khyad par la /
NK067(ju)004:291: rgyud thams cad kyi snying po'i don mthar thug pa
NK067(ju)004:292: ni 'od gsal gnyug ma'i de kho na nyid zab
NK067(ju)004:293: gsal gnyis su med pa'i mtshan nyid can nyag gcig
NK067(ju)004:294: yin cing / don de la dang por 'jug pa'i sgo mi 'dra ba gsum ste /
NK067(ju)004:295: sku gsum lam byed kyi bskyed chog rgyas pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:296: bskyed chog gi spros pa nye bar bsdus kyang dbyings
NK067(ju)004:297: dang ye shes lam byed kyi phyogs gnyis la rim
NK067(ju)004:299: bcos ma'i bskyed cho ga la mi ltos par rtsol
NK067(ju)004:300: med rang bzhag gi thabs kyis ye shes mngon du
NK067(ju)004:301: byed pa'o // de las dang po gtso bor ston pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:302: gnyis pa dang gsum pa gtsor ston rim bzhin ma
NK067(ju)004:303: h+aa sogs gsum du bzhag par khas blangs na re
NK067(ju)004:304: zhig 'chad bde zhing rog gi bzhed pa dang yang
NK067(ju)004:305: mthun no // ji skad brjod pa'i bskyed chog rgyas bsdus dang /
NK067(ju)004:306: dkyil 'khor rgyas bsdus mi gcig pa la mtha' gcod pa gzhan yang mang ste mang bas 'jigs so //
NK067(ju)004:307: ma h+aa la yang bde 'dus sgrub pa lung gi bka' sgo las /
NK067(ju)004:308: ma h+aa'i ma h+aa ni lha'i dkyil 'khor rim pas bskyed pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:309: ma h+aa'i a nu ni rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:310: ma h+aa'i a ti ni don dam ngo bo ma skyes pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:311: zhes gsungs pa ltar rim 'jug gi spros pa che
NK067(ju)004:312: chung la ltos te gsum du phye ba las 'dir
NK067(ju)004:315: thabs dang shes rab sgor zhugs nas //
NK067(ju)004:316: rang rgyud dag pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK067(ju)004:317: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhis sgrub par byed //
NK067(ju)004:318: ces pa ltar ston pas ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud dang /
NK067(ju)004:319: de'i nang nas kyang chos thams cad ye nas sangs
NK067(ju)004:320: rgyas par rtsal du bton nas ston pas ma h+aa'i
NK067(ju)004:321: a tir 'jog pa sgyu 'phrul mkhan po phal che
NK067(ju)004:322: ba'i bzhed pa ste dpe chung rang gnas kyi 'grel
NK067(ju)004:323: ba bi ma las mdzad pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:324: bde 'dus gsang sngags bka'i lde mig la sogs pa'i khungs dang ldan pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:325: de yang rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po /
NK067(ju)004:326: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK067(ju)004:327: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung khyungs /
NK067(ju)004:329: rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs /
NK067(ju)004:331: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gshegs shul /
NK067(ju)004:332: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam chen po ste che
NK067(ju)004:333: ba brgyad dang ldan pa dpal gsang ba'i snying po
NK067(ju)004:334: yin te / ma h+aa yo ga'i tan+t+ra chen po
NK067(ju)004:335: sde bco brgyad las gsang snying 'di ku ku r+aa
NK067(ju)004:336: dza'i dpal phreng ba dam pa'i 'grel pa ltar na
NK067(ju)004:337: kun gyi bsdus don lta bu'i rgyud dang /
NK067(ju)004:338: kun mkhyen bla ma'i bzhed pa ltar na spyi'i thugs rgyud yin no //
NK067(ju)004:340: lung rig man ngag gsum gyis te /
NK067(ju)004:341: lung ni 'di nyid kyi bshad pa'i rgyud grol lam
NK067(ju)004:342: rim dang cig char ston pa ye shes snying po
NK067(ju)004:344: thabs lam rim dang cig char ston pa rgya mtsho
NK067(ju)004:345: dang thal ba ste bzhi dang rgyud phyi ma sogs
NK067(ju)004:346: so // rtsa bshad gnyis kyi khyad par ni bzhed pa mang yang /
NK067(ju)004:348: thog mar byung zhing bshad byar rgyud pa'i rgyud rtsa rgyud /
NK067(ju)004:349: rjes la byung zhing 'chad byed du gyur pa'i rgyud gzhan bshad rgyud ces gsungs pa ltar 'thad la /
NK067(ju)004:353: rab gsang sngags bla med kyi 'phags lam brnyes pas rgyud don mngon shes kyis 'chad nus pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:354: 'bring yi dam lhas mngon sum du byin gyis rlabs pas rgyud 'grel nus pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:355: tha ma rig 'dzin gong ma'i man ngag gi brgyud
NK067(ju)004:356: pa tshad ldan mnga' ba ci rigs kyis mdzad pa'i
NK067(ju)004:357: rgyud 'grel dang man ngag thor bu rnams te spar
NK067(ju)004:358: khab dang 'grel chung pan+d+ai r+tha sogs dang /
NK067(ju)004:362: rig pa ni rtog ge shes pa'i nga rgyal dang /
NK067(ju)004:363: gzu lum gyis rgyud kyi rdo rje'i gnas la bshad
NK067(ju)004:364: pa byed pa ni rang bzos bstan pa dkrugs pa
NK067(ju)004:365: yin cing / 'di las 'di bshad ces pa'i tshig
NK067(ju)004:366: spyi'i go yul skam po mang du yod kyang rgyud
NK067(ju)004:367: don las gzhan du dkri bar mi nus pa'i nges
NK067(ju)004:368: pa brtan po mi rnyed pas rtsa rgyud kyi don
NK067(ju)004:369: bshad rgyud rnams la brten nas grub thob so so'i
NK067(ju)004:370: man ngag gis ji ltar bkral ba bzhin du 'thad
NK067(ju)004:371: pa'am rgyu mtshan rnam par dag pas rang nyid nges
NK067(ju)004:372: shing gzhan la 'chad mkhas pa gces so //
NK067(ju)004:373: rgyud 'chad pa'i tshul la lha rje zur po che /
NK067(ju)004:377: rgyud man ngag gis bshad pa ste bshad tshul bzhir bzhed pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:382: brgal lan gyis gtan la dbab pa ste bzhir bshad pa sogs rgyud gzhung spyi'i 'chad thabs dang /
NK067(ju)004:383: lta ba brgal brtag gis dang /
NK067(ju)004:387: dam tshig rnam grangs kyis dang /
NK067(ju)004:388: phrin las chog bsgrigs kyis dang /
NK067(ju)004:389: sgrub pa phyag bzhes kyis dang /
NK067(ju)004:390: ting nge 'dzin bskyed rdzogs kyis dang /
NK067(ju)004:391: mchod pa phyi nang gis dang /
NK067(ju)004:392: sngags sgra dag sdebs kyis dang /
NK067(ju)004:393: phyag rgya bskyed rim gyis bshad pa ste rgyud kyi dngos po so so'i bshad thabs gnyis so //
NK067(ju)004:395: gsang bdag sgro phug pa'i bzhed pas /
NK067(ju)004:396: rang bzhin dngos po'i gnas tshul /
NK067(ju)004:398: thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs tshul /
NK067(ju)004:399: brtse ba'i thugs rje skyes tshul /
NK067(ju)004:400: 'gro don ji ltar mdzad tshul dang lngas 'chad pa sogs yod mod kyis /
NK067(ju)004:401: bla ma dam pa rnams sgyu 'phrul khog gzhung las /
NK067(ju)004:402: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK067(ju)004:404: zhes gsungs pa'i rjes su 'brang ste 'chad par mdzad pas 'dir yang de bzhin du bshad par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:406: mgo smos pas go ba'i gdul bya dbang po rab la rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa /
NK067(ju)004:407: cung zad phye ste bshad pas go ba'i dbang 'bring la spyi don rnam par dbye ba /
NK067(ju)004:408: rnam par spros pas go ba'i dbang po tha ma la 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas bshad pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:409: de yang gdul bya shes rab kyi 'jug pa myur
NK067(ju)004:410: ba'i dbang rnon rnams la mtshan don bshad pa tsam
NK067(ju)004:411: gyis rgyud kyi brjod bya'i gnad mtha' dag rtogs nus
NK067(ju)004:412: pas de'i ched du mtshan bstan pa yin yang de
NK067(ju)004:413: kho na'i ched du mtshan bstan pa min te /
NK067(ju)004:414: dbang po 'bring tha gnyis la mgo smos pas go
NK067(ju)004:415: ba'i bag chags bzhag pa'i ched du'ang bstan dgos pa'i
NK067(ju)004:416: phyir ro // dbang 'bring la spyi don bshad pas
NK067(ju)004:417: rgyud don gyi 'gangs gshog pa'i go ba skyed nus
NK067(ju)004:418: pas gtso bor de la bstan par bya ba yin
NK067(ju)004:419: phyir ro // yang / dbang po tha ma la'ang
NK067(ju)004:420: 'bru gnyer dgrol ba'i don du lus rnam bzhag la
NK067(ju)004:421: bslab pas dkyus mthong nas rta rgyug pa ltar gzhung
NK067(ju)004:422: gi tshig don bzung bde ba'i dgos pa yod do
NK067(ju)004:423: phyir ro // yang / // mtshan la rnam grangs
NK067(ju)004:424: gsum gyi dang po rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso
NK067(ju)004:425: bo dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsum gyi mtshan thun
NK067(ju)004:426: mong du bstan pa ni rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu
NK067(ju)004:428: de'i don yang bshad rgyud me long las /
NK067(ju)004:429: chos rnams ma lus gnyis med pa'i //
NK067(ju)004:430: rang rig byang chub sems nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:431: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK067(ju)004:432: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK067(ju)004:434: rdo rje ni mi phyed mi shig pa ste shes rab stong pa nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:435: 'di'i gong 'og tu stong pa nyid ces bshad pa
NK067(ju)004:436: rnams ni 'od gsal gyi rang bzhin rnam par mi
NK067(ju)004:437: rtog pa'i cha la spros pa'i kun rtog dang bden
NK067(ju)004:438: dngos gnyis char gyis stong pas stong pa kho na'i
NK067(ju)004:439: rnam pa can yin pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:440: man ngag dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas de la
NK067(ju)004:441: mnyam par bzhag pa nyid kyis stong nyid la mnyam
NK067(ju)004:442: par bzhag par 'gro bas der brjod de /
NK067(ju)004:443: 'di la kun mkhyen bla ma dang gter bdag gling
NK067(ju)004:444: pa sogs ma yin dgag gi stong nyid ces gsungs
NK067(ju)004:445: te / de ni thabs shes gnyis kyi nang nas
NK067(ju)004:446: shes rab kyi phyogs yin pas shes rab ces bya
NK067(ju)004:447: te / yi / sems byung shes rab min no //
NK067(ju)004:448: sems dpa' ni sa t+wa'i sgra skabs 'dir brtan bsdus rtogs gsum la bshad de /
NK067(ju)004:449: thabs rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems shes rab
NK067(ju)004:450: stong pa nyid dang ro gcig pa'i zung 'jug rang
NK067(ju)004:451: bzhin rnam dag de thog ma dang tha ma med
NK067(ju)004:452: pa'i dus su gnas shing mtshan nyid gzhan du mi
NK067(ju)004:454: de nyid kyi phyag rgyas brtan g.yo kun la btab pa'am /
NK067(ju)004:455: brtan g.yo thams cad de'i cho 'phrul du shar bas
NK067(ju)004:456: mnyam pa nyid du gnas pas na bsdus pa dang
NK067(ju)004:457: / gnas lugs rdo rje lta bu'i don de nyid
NK067(ju)004:458: sgrib pa dang bral zhing tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs pa'i
NK067(ju)004:459: mthus ji bzhin par mngon du mdzad pa ni rtogs
NK067(ju)004:460: / pa ste / snga ma gnyis gzhi 'bras gnyis
NK067(ju)004:461: su med pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' zhes gnas tshul
NK067(ju)004:463: phyi ma 'bras bu'i rdor sems zhes snang lugs dri bral gyi cha nas bzhag go //
NK067(ju)004:464: de nyid mtshan ma'i phyag rgyar snang ba dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)004:465: gyi gtso bo dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu mi bskyod
NK067(ju)004:466: pa la'ang rdo rje sems dpa' zhes grags te /
NK067(ju)004:467: brtan bsdus rtogs gsum gcig tu gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)004:468: gyi gtso bo dngos mi slob zung 'jug yin yang
NK067(ju)004:469: rdo rje brtan bsdus gnyis bsgrub gzhir zung ste rtogs
NK067(ju)004:470: pa'i rdo rje lam byed la gnas pa'i bskyed rim
NK067(ju)004:472: de yar ldan du song ba'i rdzogs rim pa'i rdor sems yang cha 'dra tsam du bya dgos so //
NK067(ju)004:475: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i don //
NK067(ju)004:476: sgyu 'phrul zhes ni bzhir bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:481: lha rtog dbyer med kyi sgyu d+r+wa bzhi las /
NK067(ju)004:483: 'byung ba shes rab rigs kyi yum //
NK067(ju)004:484: zhes pa'i skabs su bshad pa ltar 'byung ba lnga'i
NK067(ju)004:485: bcud 'dus pa'i thig le'i cha phra ba rnams phung
NK067(ju)004:486: khams kyi snang ba ris su ma chad par 'char
NK067(ju)004:487: ba'i gzhir gyur pas na sgyu ma dang /
NK067(ju)004:488: de las phung khams rags pa'i cha sna tshogs su shar ba ni 'phrul pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:489: de gnyis rten dang brten par 'brel ba la d+r+wa ba zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:491: de ltar snang ba sgyu ma ltar ris med du
NK067(ju)004:492: 'char ba'i gnad mthar thug ni shes rab stong pa
NK067(ju)004:493: nyid yin pas de la sgyu ma zhes bya zhing
NK067(ju)004:494: / de'i rang gdangs thabs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes su gsal ba la 'phrul pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:495: de gnyis ngo bo dbyer med du 'brel ba la d+r+wa ba zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:497: de mtshon pa'i rtags kyi phyag rgyar snang ba lha yum rnams ni sgyu ma dang /
NK067(ju)004:499: yab yum kha sbyor bde ba'i skur bzhugs pa d+r+wa ba'i don to //
NK067(ju)004:502: de nyid rang rig rtogs pa'i thabs kyis lhar shar ba ni 'phrul ba /
NK067(ju)004:503: lha rtog rang bzhin gnyis su med par 'brel ba ni d+r+wa ba'o //
NK067(ju)004:504: 'di rnams kyang gzhi dang 'bral bu'i dbang du byas
NK067(ju)004:505: par gsungs pas gzhi la sbyar na rtog tshogs dang
NK067(ju)004:506: / de'i snang gzhi sems nyid 'od gsal te /
NK067(ju)004:507: sgyu d+r+wa snga ma gnyis tsam dang /
NK067(ju)004:508: 'bras bu la sbyar na rtog tshogs ni /
NK067(ju)004:509: 'bras bu'i chos la gzhi'i chos kyi ming gis btags na ma gtogs med la /
NK067(ju)004:510: nges don ni rtogs pa chos kyi sku dang /
NK067(ju)004:511: drang don ni gsang sngags thun min gyi gzugs sku dang /
NK067(ju)004:513: phung khams thams cad ro mnyam rdo rje'i lhar dag pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:514: gtso bo'i dbang du byas na /
NK067(ju)004:515: rdo rje sems dpa' lhag pa don dam gyi phyogs nas dang /
NK067(ju)004:516: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba kun rdzob kyi phyogs nas bshad pa 'dra la /
NK067(ju)004:517: gzhi'i rdor sems sgyu d+r+wa shes nas /
NK067(ju)004:518: 'bras bu'i rdor sems sgyu d+r+wa 'thob phyir du gzhi
NK067(ju)004:519: 'bras gnyis ka lam du byed pa'i lam rgyud la'ang
NK067(ju)004:520: mtshan de ltar 'dogs par gsungs so //
NK067(ju)004:521: gnyis pa che ba las mtshan du btags pa ni /
NK067(ju)004:522: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi zhes pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:523: de'i don yang rdo rje las /
NK067(ju)004:524: so sor bstan pa rgya mtsho'i rgyud //
NK067(ju)004:526: don kun 'di la yongs rdzogs pas //
NK067(ju)004:527: lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin //
NK067(ju)004:529: mtshan nyid theg pa'i gsung rab kyi brjod byar gyur ba mngon mtho dang /
NK067(ju)004:531: thams cad mkhyen pa sgrub pa'i lam thams cad 'di'i lam stegs su bstan cing /
NK067(ju)004:532: gsang sngags phyi pa'i mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi lam dang /
NK067(ju)004:533: khyad par rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud sde mtha'
NK067(ju)004:534: dag gi brjod bya'i snying po zab gsal gnyis med
NK067(ju)004:535: kyi gnad gsang ma lus pa rgyud 'dir ston pa
NK067(ju)004:536: dang / sde snod dang rgyud sde gzhan thams cad
NK067(ju)004:537: 'dir bstan pa'i don de dag nyid las brtsams te
NK067(ju)004:539: bstan pa de dag thams cad rgyud 'di'i dgongs don
NK067(ju)004:540: lhag pa'i bden gnyis dbyer med la 'jug pa'i ched
NK067(ju)004:541: du dngos sam brgyud nas gzhol ba ste /
NK067(ju)004:542: de dag gi phyir lung thams cad kyi spyi chings su gyur ba yin no //
NK067(ju)004:543: 'di la lung dang mthun pa'i mtshan zhes kyang gsung ngo //
NK067(ju)004:544: gsum pa don rang gi ngo bo las btags pa'am man ngag dang mthun pa'i mtshan ni /
NK067(ju)004:545: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK067(ju)004:546: zhes glegs bam gyi klad du 'byung ba nyid de
NK067(ju)004:547: / 'di la bi ma la'i 'grel chung du /
NK067(ju)004:548: rang bzhin gsang ba zhes bya ste //
NK067(ju)004:549: che ba zhes bya snying po'i don //
NK067(ju)004:550: de kho na nyid mtshan nyid de //
NK067(ju)004:551: nges pas nges don mdor bstan pa //
NK067(ju)004:552: zhes mtshan gyi zur bzhi pos rgyud kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK067(ju)004:555: nges pa'i don rnams bstan par bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:556: 'dir spyi'i don phyogs tsam brjod na /
NK067(ju)004:557: mdo phal po che las stong gsum gyi 'jig rten
NK067(ju)004:558: 'di rgyu rkyen ches mang po dang che ba sna
NK067(ju)004:559: tshogs las 'grub pa dper mdzad nas rgyu tshogs nyung
NK067(ju)004:560: ngu dang mdor bsdus pa tsam gyis rdzogs pa'i byang
NK067(ju)004:561: chub mi 'grub par gsungs pa ltar gdul bya rgya
NK067(ju)004:562: chen po la mos pa rnams la bstan pa'i theg
NK067(ju)004:563: chen pha rol tu phyin pa ltar na tshogs gnyis
NK067(ju)004:564: kyi spyod pa'i bye brag dang /
NK067(ju)004:566: slob tshul gyi thabs mkhas mtha' yas pa zhig la
NK067(ju)004:567: ngal ba ma bsten par byang chub 'thob pa gnas
NK067(ju)004:568: med kyang / zab mo la mos pa'i gdul bya
NK067(ju)004:569: skal pa rab mchog ldan pa rnams la bstan pa'i
NK067(ju)004:570: gsang ba bla med kyi skabs 'dir ni dpal kha
NK067(ju)004:571: med kyang / sbyor thig ler / de phyir de rgyas ci zhig bya //
NK067(ju)004:572: mdor bsdus pas ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK067(ju)004:574: lam mdor bsdus kyis 'grub pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:575: de'ang snyigs dus kyi tshe thung gcig la 'grub pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:576: bde blag nyid du 'grub pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:577: lam gzhan bsnan pa la mi ltos par 'di nyid kho nas 'grub pa'i khyad par dang ldan la /
NK067(ju)004:579: phyi rgyud sde gsum man chad du gsal bar ma
NK067(ju)004:580: bstan pa'i ye shes lam byed kyi gnad thun min
NK067(ju)004:581: cig yod pa de gtan la phab pa nyag gcig
NK067(ju)004:583: de 'dra de la rgyud 'di las lhag pa bden
NK067(ju)004:584: gnyis dbyer med kyi chos sku chen po'i rnal 'byor
NK067(ju)004:585: zhes gsungs te / 'di'i brjod bya'i mthil ni de yin no //
NK067(ju)004:586: de'i phyir mtshan gyi zur 'di dag thams cad kyis
NK067(ju)004:587: kyang gtso bor de kho na bstan pa yin no
NK067(ju)004:589: so so'i bshad na gsang ba'i don ni spar khab tu rang bzhin sogs gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:590: bi ma las mi bstan pa'i gsang ba bsnan te bzhir phye na'ang 'dir rgyud nyid las /
NK067(ju)004:591: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK067(ju)004:592: zhes pa ltar gab sbas gnyis su 'du bar rje rong klong gnyis bzhed pa ltar bshad de /
NK067(ju)004:594: gnas lugs rang bzhin gyi rgyud dang /
NK067(ju)004:595: de la ltos pa'i lam 'bras rnams zab cing gting
NK067(ju)004:596: dpag dka' bas shing tu dbang rnon ma gtogs pa
NK067(ju)004:597: gzhan gyis rtogs mi nus pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:599: gsang ba bla med kyi lta sgom spyod pa'i gnad
NK067(ju)004:600: thun min rnams snod min la rnam pa thams cad
NK067(ju)004:601: du sba dgos pas der bzhag ste /
NK067(ju)004:603: rtogs su mi rung ba'i khyad par gyi dbye bar bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:608: dang po'i steng nas bshad na /
NK067(ju)004:609: gcig las mang po 'phro ba'i gzhi la 'jug pas
NK067(ju)004:610: sems nyid rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa las 'khor
NK067(ju)004:612: de gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud 'di yang bstan pa thams cad kyi 'phro gzhir gyur ba'o //
NK067(ju)004:613: hri da ya las bshad na /
NK067(ju)004:614: snying ltar gces spras su bya ba la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)004:615: theg pa'i sgo gang nas zhugs kyang mthar thug 'di
NK067(ju)004:616: las mi 'da' bas byang chub 'dod pa rnams kyis
NK067(ju)004:617: don du gnyer bya'i gtso bor gyur pa ste snga
NK067(ju)004:618: ma la rgyu'i snying po dang /
NK067(ju)004:619: phyi ma la 'bras bu'i snying po zhes bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:620: gar+b+ha ni glegs bam gyi dbu na bzhugs pa gtso bo'i don te /
NK067(ju)004:621: shun pa'i nang gi snying po lta bu bcud 'dus pa'i don la bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:622: de'ang gong 'og gi theg pa thams cad zhal bsdur yang /
NK067(ju)004:623: 'di'i lam la byang chub sgrub pa'i thabs mkhas kyi
NK067(ju)004:624: gnad 'dus shing rdzogs pa las lhag pa'i lam gzhan
NK067(ju)004:625: med pas gzhi lam 'bras bu'i gnad bcud du 'dril
NK067(ju)004:626: ba'o // de kho na nyid ni gsum ste /
NK067(ju)004:629: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:631: gdod nas rang bzhin dag pa'i ye shes glo bur
NK067(ju)004:632: ba'i kun rtog de'i bag chags kyi rnyogs pas bslad
NK067(ju)004:634: de gtan log pa la sangs rgyas su btags shing /
NK067(ju)004:635: gsang sngags kyi thabs mkhas kyis gnyug ma'i rang bzhin
NK067(ju)004:636: rjen la phyungs te bsgoms pa kho nas chab rom
NK067(ju)004:637: chur zhu ba ltar bslad pa de rang log tu
NK067(ju)004:638: 'gro bas 'od gsal snying po'i lam la rgyu'i de
NK067(ju)004:641: lam des rang gnas kyi ye shes dri bral du
NK067(ju)004:642: byas pa kho nas sku dang ye shes kyi 'khor
NK067(ju)004:643: lo thams cad gsal bar rang 'byung ba ste 'bras
NK067(ju)004:644: bu'i de kho na nyid ces bya /
NK067(ju)004:646: de ltar na shes bya gzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:647: bsgrub bya 'bras bu gnyis ka gnyug ma mi shigs pa'i sems gcig pu las gud na med de /
NK067(ju)004:648: de la rgyu 'bras ro gcig pa'i de kho na nyid ces kyang bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:650: de ltar gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rnam bzhag mdzad pa
NK067(ju)004:651: de dag kyang gdul bya kha drang ba'i don du
NK067(ju)004:652: bstan pa'i ldem dgongs lta bu ma yin te /
NK067(ju)004:653: dbang rnon mchog gi gdul bya la rgyal ba nyid
NK067(ju)004:654: kyis ji ltar thugs su chud pa'i dgongs don mthar
NK067(ju)004:656: mtshan nang gsang ltar bshad pa phyogs mthong tsam ni /
NK067(ju)004:657: nang ltar na snying ga'i mi shigs pa ni gdon
NK067(ju)004:658: nas rang la gnas kyang mtshon dka' bas gsang ba
NK067(ju)004:659: / de nyid la gsang sngags kyi zab gnad thams cad 'dus pas snying po /
NK067(ju)004:660: bla ma dam pa'i man ngag gis ye shes kyi
NK067(ju)004:661: snang ba de nyid gsal bar sad pa de kho
NK067(ju)004:662: na nyid / snying po'i thig le de gzhi lam
NK067(ju)004:663: 'bras gsum gyi srog tu nges pas na nges pa
NK067(ju)004:664: na nyid / ste / rgyud sde'i rdzogs rim rnams
NK067(ju)004:665: su rtsa 'khor gang la gnad du bsnun pa'i khyad
NK067(ju)004:666: par mi 'dra ba mang yang gsang ba sgyu 'phrul
NK067(ju)004:667: las snying ga'i 'khor lo gtso bor byed pas de
NK067(ju)004:668: ltar gsungs te bshad tshul gcig go //
NK067(ju)004:669: yang 'khor lo bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK067(ju)004:670: lte ba'i dbyings phyug lnga'i thig le ni gsang ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:671: snying ga'i ye shes snying po'i thig le ni snying po dang /
NK067(ju)004:672: mgrin pa'i rngams ma'i thig le ni /
NK067(ju)004:674: spyi bo'i kun tu bzang po'i thig le la nges pa zhes bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:676: rtsa gnas kyi thig le bde ba'i ye shes kyi
NK067(ju)004:677: ro dang bcas par rang chas su yod kyang ma
NK067(ju)004:679: thig le de la phung khams thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pas snying po /
NK067(ju)004:680: thabs lam zab mos gnas du bsnun pas lhan skyes
NK067(ju)004:681: kyi rang zhal ji bzhin mthong ba de kho na
NK067(ju)004:682: nyid / thig le de nyid gzhi lam 'bras bu
NK067(ju)004:683: gsum ka'i gnad srog tu nges pa la nges pa
NK067(ju)004:684: zhes bshad de bla ma brgyud pa'i man ngag go
NK067(ju)004:685: nyid / // de ltar na rgyud 'di rgyud lung
NK067(ju)004:686: man ngag gsum gyi gnad bsdus yin pas rgyud dang
NK067(ju)004:687: mthun pa sogs mtshan gsum du byung zhing /
NK067(ju)004:688: rang gi ngo bo ma h+aa yo ga la ltos
NK067(ju)004:689: pa'i man ngag a ti yo ga'i rgyud du gnas
NK067(ju)004:690: pas glegs bam gyi klad du man ngag dang mthun
NK067(ju)004:691: pa'i mtshan 'ba' zhig smos zhes gsungs ngo //
NK067(ju)004:693: don gyi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:694: tshig gi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba'o //
NK067(ju)004:698: 'bras bu yongs su shes par bya ba rgyud don /
NK067(ju)004:700: 'khor la gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa ste lnga las /
NK067(ju)004:702: gang du ston 'khor tshogs pa de'i tshe rgyud 'byung
NK067(ju)004:703: bas phun sum tshogs pa lnga ldan ni gleng gazhi'o
NK067(ju)004:705: gleng gzhi'i skad don d+aa na zhes pa sbyin pa la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)004:706: khungs ldan gyi lo rgyus ma rnyed pas yid mi
NK067(ju)004:707: ches pa rnams la nges pa sbyin pa'i phyir dang
NK067(ju)004:708: / rgyud don gleng ba'i gzhir gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:710: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:711: thun mong gi gleng gzhi gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:713: thabs lam dang sbyar ba ste /
NK067(ju)004:714: de la'ang steng 'og gi sgo'i lam dang sbyar ba gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:716: gnas snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:717: ston pa rtsa 'khor de'i dbus na sems mi shigs
NK067(ju)004:718: pa dwangs ma lnga'i thig le la brten te bzhugs
NK067(ju)004:719: pa dang / 'khor rtsa 'dab la rgyu ba'i las
NK067(ju)004:720: rlung gi bzhon pa can gyi rnam shes tshogs brgyad
NK067(ju)004:721: pa dang / dang / bstan pa'am chos bde gsal
NK067(ju)004:722: mi rtog pa'i ye shes bsam mi khyab kyi dgongs
NK067(ju)004:723: pa ste mi shigs pa sad stobs kyis las rlung
NK067(ju)004:724: ye shes su sbyangs shing tshogs brgyad bde stong gi
NK067(ju)004:725: ros khyab pa ni ston pas 'khor la chos bstan
NK067(ju)004:726: pa dang / dang / pa dang / dus ni
NK067(ju)004:727: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid du bsdam pa dus med
NK067(ju)004:728: kyi dgongs pa mngon du gyur pa'i dus so //
NK067(ju)004:730: rdo rje btsun mo'i pad+ma las bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas dang /
NK067(ju)004:731: thabs kyi rdo rje nor bu'i dbus na rtsa khams
NK067(ju)004:732: kyi bcud 'dus pa'i byang sems kyi thig le bzhugs
NK067(ju)004:734: byed bcing gi thabs dang bcas pa'i yab yum gnyis kyi gsang ba'i rnam shes ni 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)004:735: thabs lam gyi sems lnga rdzogs pa'i mtha'i lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni chos dang /
NK067(ju)004:736: ston pa de'i mthus 'khor de dag chos de'i ngo
NK067(ju)004:737: bor skyes pa ni ston 'khor zhu 'chad byas pa'i
NK067(ju)004:738: don dang / dus sngar bzhin te /
NK067(ju)004:739: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa lnga'o //
NK067(ju)004:740: 'di dag rgyud kyi thog mar 'byung ba'i e bam
NK067(ju)004:741: m+aa y+aa zhes pa'i yi ge bzhi dang sbyar nas
NK067(ju)004:742: bshad rgyud kyis ji ltar 'grel pa sogs dgongs rgyan
NK067(ju)004:743: las shes shing / le'u gnyis pa'i gsang dbang ston pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:744: dbang phyi ma gnyis ston pa'i rgyud tshig gi shugs
NK067(ju)004:745: kyis kyang rim bzhin steng sgo dang 'og sgo'i gleng
NK067(ju)004:746: gzhi thon par bshad rung par mngon te /
NK067(ju)004:747: nang gsang gi phun tshogs lnga ldan 'di dag gleng gzhir 'gyur tshul gyis shes pa'i phyir te /
NK067(ju)004:748: gleng bslang gi skabs su lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams
NK067(ju)004:749: la ston pas 'bras dbang bskur nas de rnams nang
NK067(ju)004:750: gi mngon byang lngas byang chub pa na go phye
NK067(ju)004:752: e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK067(ju)004:753: sogs ched brjod zhus lan mdzad pa las 'phros te rgyud yong rdzogs byung ba yin la /
NK067(ju)004:754: de lta bu'i mngon byang lnga po'ang snying ga dang
NK067(ju)004:755: gsang ba'i 'og min du 'tshang rgya tshul yin pa'i
NK067(ju)004:756: gnad kyis de la ltos pa'i phun sum tshogs pa
NK067(ju)004:757: lnga gleng gzhir song ba yin zhes dam pa snga
NK067(ju)004:759: gnyis pa la longs sku'i gleng gazhi'am rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:760: de'ang zhar byung gdul bya dgos ched du bstan pa khro bo'i gleng gzhi /
NK067(ju)004:761: sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba'i gleng gazhi'am bstan pa spyi'i gleng gzhi ste gsum las /
NK067(ju)004:764: ston gnas 'khor dang sdud pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:765: bstan pa dus kyis shes par bya //
NK067(ju)004:766: zhes phun sum tshogs pa drug tu bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)004:767: 'dir sdud po phun tshogs 'khor la bsdus nas lngar bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:774: dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min dang lnga bshad pa'i
NK067(ju)004:775: ya gyal phyi ma ste 'dir bstan kyi dbang phyug
NK067(ju)004:776: chen po ni bla na med pa'i chos kyi rgyal
NK067(ju)004:777: srid kyi dbang phyug ste longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o
NK067(ju)004:778: // de lta bu'i gnas de rang bzhin dang ngo
NK067(ju)004:779: bo gnyis kyi sgo nas bshad pa'i dang po la
NK067(ju)004:782: mtha' dbus med pa'i chos kyi dbyings //
NK067(ju)004:783: de ni gnas kyi bla mar 'dod //
NK067(ju)004:784: ces pa ltar chos kyi dbyings yin la /
NK067(ju)004:785: cha shas so so'i rang bzhin ni /
NK067(ju)004:786: 'og gzhi 'khor lo'i rang bzhin ye shes lnga dang /
NK067(ju)004:787: gru chad kyi bden bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:788: bar khyams kyi bden pa dbyer med la sogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:790: rnam pa'i khyad par te 'grel chung las /
NK067(ju)004:791: gzhal yas gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya //
NK067(ju)004:792: dbyibs dang glo 'bur rtse mo dang //
NK067(ju)004:793: rgyan dang sgo khyud rta babs dang //
NK067(ju)004:794: mtshan nyid gdan gyi rnam pa ste //
NK067(ju)004:795: bcu gcig dag gis dbye bar bya //
NK067(ju)004:797: ston pa phun tshogs bshad pa la'ang rang bzhin dang ngo bo gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:798: de'ang dkyil 'khor gyi brda don ngo sprod la dkyil
NK067(ju)004:799: 'khor gyi de nyid bstan pa zhes brjod pa ltar
NK067(ju)004:800: dag pa'i rten dang brten pa'i ye shes kyi de
NK067(ju)004:802: gzugs kyi rnam pa la ngo bo zhes btags pa yin pas rang bzhin chos sku'i phyogs nas dang /
NK067(ju)004:803: ngo bo gzugs sku'i phyogs nas bstan dgos so //
NK067(ju)004:804: de la ston pa'i rang bzhin ni 'grel chung las /
NK067(ju)004:805: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo dang //
NK067(ju)004:806: chos rnams rol par longs spyod dang //
NK067(ju)004:807: phyogs dus bde gshegs bdag po dang //
NK067(ju)004:808: chos so cog dang dbyer med pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:810: de'i dang po la'ang chos nyid de bzhin nyid sgrib
NK067(ju)004:811: byed kyi dri ma mtha' dag spangs bas mnyam par
NK067(ju)004:812: ma bzhag pa med pa'i tshul gyis mngon du mdzad
NK067(ju)004:813: pa de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i rang bzhin
NK067(ju)004:814: dang / de'i dbang gis 'bras bu'i chos rgya mtsho
NK067(ju)004:815: lta bu rtsol med rang byung du brnyes pa yon
NK067(ju)004:816: tan ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)004:817: ye shes re re'ang kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin
NK067(ju)004:818: yin pas tshad 'di tsam zhes bzung du med pas
NK067(ju)004:819: ye shes mtha' dbus dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)004:820: spangs rtogs mthar phyin gyi go 'phang la bzhugs kyang
NK067(ju)004:821: srid zhi'i mtha' gnyis gang gi phyogs su'ang brjod du
NK067(ju)004:822: med pa'am / yang na mnyam bzhag gi dgongs pa
NK067(ju)004:823: mtshan ma'i yul can gang gis kyang mtshon du med
NK067(ju)004:824: pa 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad kyang ngo bo bstan
NK067(ju)004:825: du med pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK067(ju)004:827: ye shes sgyu ma'i spyod yul tshad med pa la
NK067(ju)004:828: dbang bsgyur yang gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i chos nyid
NK067(ju)004:830: 'di la mnyam pa nyid mngon du mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin zhes kyang bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:832: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba thams cad bsdu na
NK067(ju)004:833: rigs lngar 'du zhing lnga po'ang rigs drug pa la
NK067(ju)004:834: 'du bas rigs thams cad kyi bdag por bzhugs pa
NK067(ju)004:835: ste / gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i rang bzhin zhes kyang bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:837: khams gsum dus gsum gyi bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i chos
NK067(ju)004:838: thams cad kyang lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med kyi
NK067(ju)004:839: don las phyi rol du gyur ba med cing bden
NK067(ju)004:840: gnyis de dag la rgyal ba drug pa'i dgongs pa
NK067(ju)004:841: rtag khyab tu bzhugs pa ste gnyis su med pa'i
NK067(ju)004:842: bdag nyid chen por dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i
NK067(ju)004:844: gnyis pa ngo bo la'ang bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)004:845: ston pa sku gsum gyi bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags /
NK067(ju)004:846: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i don rtags /
NK067(ju)004:847: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i don rtags /
NK067(ju)004:848: rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i don rtags so //
NK067(ju)004:849: dang po la'ang chos sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don
NK067(ju)004:850: rtags su sku mdun dang rgyab med par phyogs thams
NK067(ju)004:851: cad du thal ler gzigs pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:852: longs sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags su mtshan
NK067(ju)004:853: dpe'i yon tan mthar thug pa dang ldan pa dang
NK067(ju)004:854: / sprul sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags su
NK067(ju)004:855: sku'i ba spu'i sgo re re las kyang sprul pa
NK067(ju)004:856: dpag tu med pa phyogs bcur spro ba'o //
NK067(ju)004:859: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyis mi gnas myang 'das
NK067(ju)004:860: la bzhugs pa'i brdar yab yum gnyis ka mtshungs par
NK067(ju)004:861: skyil krung du bzhugs nas 'khril ba'o //
NK067(ju)004:863: ye shes lngar rang byung gi ye shes dang drug brnyes pa'i rtags su phyag drug dang /
NK067(ju)004:864: des 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags su rdo rje la sogs pa'i mtshan ma drug 'dzin pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:868: thugs smon pa med pa ste gsum po dbyer med
NK067(ju)004:869: pa'i rtags su mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum mnga'
NK067(ju)004:870: ba'o // 'khor phun sum tshogs la lhan cig pa dang dgo phye ba'i 'khor gnyis /
NK067(ju)004:871: dang po rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i /
NK067(ju)004:872: rig pa khyad par can gyi /
NK067(ju)004:873: dad pas gtam nyan pa'i 'khor ro //
NK067(ju)004:875: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po sogs rgyal ba rigs lnga ste /
NK067(ju)004:876: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po zhes pa 'di la
NK067(ju)004:877: kun mkhyen chen po rnam par snang mdzad yin pa'i
NK067(ju)004:878: sgrub byed mang du 'god par mdzad la /
NK067(ju)004:879: zur ba ni glang chen rab 'bog gi rgyud dang /
NK067(ju)004:881: rdo rje las rim sogs kyi khungs la brten nas mi bskyod par bzhed de /
NK067(ju)004:882: gter bdag gling pa sku mched sogs kyang phyi ma'i rjes su 'brang ngo //
NK067(ju)004:883: rigs lnga 'di dag thal ba las /
NK067(ju)004:885: bdag po kun bzang 'khor rnams la //
NK067(ju)004:887: mi bskyod rgyal po mdun na gnas //
NK067(ju)004:888: zhes pa ltar rigs drug pa rgyud kyi ston par bzhengs pa la ltos te 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)004:889: spyir 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga zhes grags pa
NK067(ju)004:890: ltar ston pa'ang yin pas ston 'khor gnyis ka'i gzhi
NK067(ju)004:893: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK067(ju)004:894: rang snang rgyal ba sems sogs dang //
NK067(ju)004:895: zhes pa ltar ston pa'i thugs rig pa sngags kyi
NK067(ju)004:896: ye shes kyi khyad par las rang snang ba'i phyir
NK067(ju)004:897: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor zhes bya ste
NK067(ju)004:898: / de la'ang rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:899: mthong bar bya ba sogs sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug dang /
NK067(ju)004:901: rtag par ma yin pa sogs 'joms byed khro bo yab yum brgyad de /
NK067(ju)004:902: sangs rgyas kyi sas bsdus la dbang yul sogs ngo
NK067(ju)004:903: bo tha dad med kyang ro mnyam rdo rje'i phung
NK067(ju)004:904: khams skye mched kyi ldog cha so so las gshegs
NK067(ju)004:905: pa gshegs ma dang sems dpa' yab yum sogs tha
NK067(ju)004:906: dad du sprul bar shes pa'i ched du phung khams
NK067(ju)004:907: sogs kyi ming gis lha la btags pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:908: de dag ni ma 'ongs pa'i rjes 'jug rnams kyis
NK067(ju)004:909: gleng gzhi dang mthun par dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo
NK067(ju)004:910: sgom pa'i dbang du mdzad nas rgyud tshig gis dngos
NK067(ju)004:911: su bstan pa'i 'khor rnams yin gyis /
NK067(ju)004:912: rje sgro phug pa dang nye ston sogs kyi bzhed
NK067(ju)004:913: pa ltar ston pa las rgyud gzhan du gyur pa'i
NK067(ju)004:914: 'phags pa slob pa yang mtha' yas pa zhig lhan
NK067(ju)004:915: cig pa'i 'khor la yod dgos te /
NK067(ju)004:916: de lta ma yin na le'u gnyis par ston pas
NK067(ju)004:917: 'khor la zab dbang bskur nas rtog pa'i dri ma
NK067(ju)004:918: bsal bar gsungs pa mi 'grigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:921: dad pas nyan pa'i lha chen rnams //
NK067(ju)004:923: phyi'i khor yug la gnas pa legs ldan ma h+aa
NK067(ju)004:924: d+ae wa la sogs pa'i lha chen po rnams so
NK067(ju)004:926: sngags la mos pa'i dbang rnon skal ba dang ldan pa rnams te /
NK067(ju)004:927: 'di dag 'og min du tshogs pa'i 'khor min yang
NK067(ju)004:928: rgyud kyi ched du bya ba'i gdul bya yin pas
NK067(ju)004:929: rdo rje sems dpa'i 'khor dra smos so //
NK067(ju)004:930: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)004:931: gnyis med rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di nyid dang /
NK067(ju)004:933: gleng gzhi'i ston 'khor sogs tshogs pa'i dus so //
NK067(ju)004:934: gnyis pa la'ang phun sum tshogs pa lnga las gnas ni /
NK067(ju)004:935: 'bar ba'i dur khrod chen po shin tu 'jigs pa'i rgyan chas kyi spros par ro //
NK067(ju)004:937: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK067(ju)004:938: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK067(ju)004:939: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK067(ju)004:940: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK067(ju)004:942: phrin las phyag rgya'i khro bo ste /
NK067(ju)004:943: de la'ang drang srong khros pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:945: dpal chen rngams brjid kyi cha byad gsum las phyi ma'o //
NK067(ju)004:946: 'khor la gdul bya dang 'dul byed kyi 'khor gnyis kyis /
NK067(ju)004:948: ru dra 'khor dang bcas pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:949: de'ang 'dir bstan gyi ru dra 'di gnas tshod la sprul pa yin par bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)004:950: snang tshod ltar na sngon sangs rgyas kyi rig sngags drag po bzlas shing /
NK067(ju)004:951: de lta bu'i sngags kyi lha bsgoms kyang lta ba
NK067(ju)004:952: zab mo'i gnad kyis ma zin cing dam tshig nyams
NK067(ju)004:953: pa'i chad pas ngan 'gro brgyud pa'i mthar las kyi
NK067(ju)004:954: srin po rig sngags kyi mthu can 'phags pa'i gnas
NK067(ju)004:955: lnga ma gtogs pa'i 'dod gzugs kyi khams thams cad
NK067(ju)004:956: sngags kyis dbang du bsdus shing 'jig rten phung bar
NK067(ju)004:957: byed pa / gdug cing gtum pa'i 'khor mang po dang ldan par gyur pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:961: dbang phyug nyer brgyad ni gdul bya dang 'dul byed kyi 'khor gnyis kar gtogs zhes gsung ngo //
NK067(ju)004:963: pho rgyud rnams la sgrol ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:964: mo rgyud la sbyor ba'i sgo nas rang gnas kyi
NK067(ju)004:965: ye shes mngon du bstan pas sbyor sgrol gnyis so
NK067(ju)004:967: sngags kyi gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i dus la babs pa na'o //
NK067(ju)004:970: de bzhin gshegs pas sngon slob lam du smin lam
NK067(ju)004:971: gyis ji ltar bzung ba bzhin grub pa'i sprul sku'i
NK067(ju)004:972: zhing ste / zhing 'di dang sbyar na gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgya'i bdag nyid dang /
NK067(ju)004:973: spyir gling bzhi bye ba khrag khrig du ma dang ldan pa'i sprul sku'i zhing yang yod do //
NK067(ju)004:975: bstan pa 'di'i dbang du byas na sh+aakya'i rgyal po ste /
NK067(ju)004:976: gdul bya rigs drug la ltos te thub pa drug tu bzhag go //
NK067(ju)004:978: dmyal ba dang yi dwags kyi 'gro ba la gshin rje'i rgyal po dang /
NK067(ju)004:979: dud 'gro kha cig la ri dwags dbang po sog rigs mthun gyi gzugs dang /
NK067(ju)004:980: mtshan dpes spras pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa'i gzugs dang /
NK067(ju)004:981: mchog gi sprul sku dngos kyis 'dul ba sogs mang
NK067(ju)004:982: du yod kyang mchog sprul nyid gtso bo dang rtsa
NK067(ju)004:983: ba'i sku yin bas rgyud kyi tshig zin gtso bo
NK067(ju)004:984: de yin no // 'khor ni gtso bo'i dbang du
NK067(ju)004:985: byas na lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa zhes
NK067(ju)004:987: de'i yang gtso bo 'khor rnam pa bzhi dang spyir 'gro ba drug ka ci rigs su yod do //
NK067(ju)004:994: de la dang po ni mdzad chen bcu gnyis dang ldan pa'i sku ste /
NK067(ju)004:995: gang gis chos ston pa'i rten no //
NK067(ju)004:997: cho 'phrul gsum gyis chos ston tshul te /
NK067(ju)004:998: dang por rdzu 'phrul gyis 'khor 'dun par mdzad /
NK067(ju)004:999: de nas mngon shes kyis 'khor gyi sems la gzigs nas kun brjod par mdzad /
NK067(ju)004:1000: de'i 'og tu gdams ngag dang rjes bstan 'bogs par
NK067(ju)004:1001: mdzad pa'i phyir ro snyam zhing go rim de bzhin
NK067(ju)004:1002: mi 'byung ba ni snga ma bzhin dgongs so //
NK067(ju)004:1003: dus ni rdzogs smin sbyang gsum grub nas sgron ma bkod pa'i dus so //
NK067(ju)004:1004: de'ang le'u gnyis pa ltar lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams
NK067(ju)004:1005: 'bras dbang gis snang gsum gyi bag chags sam 'pho
NK067(ju)004:1006: ba'i bag chags phra mo'i bdud bcom pa na de'i
NK067(ju)004:1007: rtags snang phyi rol du khro bo'i gleng gzhir snang
NK067(ju)004:1008: ba yin zhing / der ma zad sprul sku 'gro
NK067(ju)004:1009: 'dul gyi gleng gazhi'ang le'u dang po'i sku gsung thugs
NK067(ju)004:1010: sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba /
NK067(ju)004:1013: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK067(ju)004:1014: ces pa las 'phros pas 'di gnyis zhar byung gi gleng gzhir 'gyur zhes bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:1016: ston 'khor zhus lan gyi sbyor bas rgyud don gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par 'byung ma rag pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:1017: de ni gleng bya rgyud don nyid gleng bar bskul
NK067(ju)004:1018: ba'i sgo nas bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen byed pas
NK067(ju)004:1020: dbye na thun min dang thun mong ba gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:1021: dang po la gsang dbang bskur ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:1022: dbang gong ma gnyis bskur ba'i tshul lo //
NK067(ju)004:1024: ston pa yab yum snyoms par 'jug pa las byung
NK067(ju)004:1025: ba'i nyi zla byang chub kyi sems kyis lhan cig
NK067(ju)004:1026: pa'i 'khor gyi rig 'dzin rnams la dbang bskur zhing
NK067(ju)004:1027: yab kyis thabs kyi cha bzung nas 'khor 'das brtan
NK067(ju)004:1028: g.yo thams cad dag pa rab 'byams lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)004:1029: gcig tu sangs rgyas par ched du brjod cing /
NK067(ju)004:1030: yum gyis shes rab kyi cha bzung nas brtan g.yo
NK067(ju)004:1031: thams cad gdod nas rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1032: dbyings las mi gzhan par ched du brjod pas 'khor
NK067(ju)004:1033: rnams kyis thun mong ma yin pa'i bden gnyis kyi
NK067(ju)004:1036: sems ye shes su bskyed pa'i ched du brjod pa e ma mtshar lnga gasungasate /
NK067(ju)004:1037: de'i tshe 'chad bar 'gyur ba'i g.yo ldang /
NK067(ju)004:1040: smon pa ste sems bzhi sngon du 'gro bas dga'
NK067(ju)004:1041: ba bcu drug lugs 'byung gi mtha'i lhan skyes sher
NK067(ju)004:1042: dbang gi ngo bo nyid thob cing /
NK067(ju)004:1043: slar mas brtan gyi dga' ba bcu drug gi mthar
NK067(ju)004:1044: bde ba chen po'i dbang rdzogs te ston 'khor dgongs
NK067(ju)004:1045: pa dbyer med du gyur pa'i mthar phyin byang chub
NK067(ju)004:1046: kyi sems thob pa ni 'og tu dri zhus 'byung
NK067(ju)004:1047: ba'i rkyen yin pas na gleng bslang ngo //
NK067(ju)004:1048: 'dir ston pa kun tu bzang po khu rdul rlung
NK067(ju)004:1049: gsum dag pa'i ye shes kyi sku can gyis 'khor
NK067(ju)004:1050: la dkar dmar gyi thig le'i rdzas dbang bskur ba
NK067(ju)004:1051: dang / 'og min gyi rten can sa mthor bzhugs
NK067(ju)004:1052: pa'i rig 'dzin lus khu khrag dang sems 'khrig sred
NK067(ju)004:1053: kyis dben pa phyag rgya la brten nas dbang gong
NK067(ju)004:1054: ma gnyis nod pa mi 'gal ba'i tshul ni /
NK067(ju)004:1055: ston pa dbang 'byor gyi mthu'i pha rol tu byon
NK067(ju)004:1056: pas 'khor gyi ched du nyi zla byin gyis rlob
NK067(ju)004:1058: dag pa'i 'khor la 'khrig sred kyi nyon mongs med
NK067(ju)004:1059: kyang lhan skyes kyi bde ba don gnyer yod la
NK067(ju)004:1060: / spyi btang 'og min gyi rten la khu khrag
NK067(ju)004:1061: med kyang bla med kyi sngags spyod pa'i 'og min
NK067(ju)004:1062: pa kha cig la khams drug ldan gyi rten khyad
NK067(ju)004:1063: par can de 'dra 'byung ba dmigs bsal yin pa'am
NK067(ju)004:1064: / / lo chen rin po che'i bzhed pas slob
NK067(ju)004:1065: ba'i rten la khu rdul phra mo dag pa mi
NK067(ju)004:1066: srid pas de'i phyogs nas bshad kyang rung bar sems
NK067(ju)004:1068: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal pos grol ba'i thig le
NK067(ju)004:1069: drangs nas bshad pa sogs ltar na rgyal sras mthar
NK067(ju)004:1070: lam pa mi slob lam du sher dbang nas zhugs
NK067(ju)004:1071: pas chog pa 'dra yang 'dir gsang dbang nas 'jug
NK067(ju)004:1072: par bshad pa ni lugs gnyis kyi gsang dbang gi
NK067(ju)004:1073: lam 'jog tshul mi 'dra bas yin nam /
NK067(ju)004:1074: yang na 'bras dbang bskur tshul 'di gsang dbang bskur
NK067(ju)004:1075: tshul dang chos mthun pas gsang dbang du brjod pa
NK067(ju)004:1076: tsam yin ces 'chad pa gang bde dpyad dgos shing
NK067(ju)004:1077: / dbang phyi ma gnyis la'ang dogs pa gcad rgyu yod de des shes nus so //
NK067(ju)004:1079: de ltar zab dbang la brten nas ston pa'i thugs
NK067(ju)004:1080: kyi gsang ba ji lta ba bzhin mngon du byas
NK067(ju)004:1081: pa na don de gsang ba bzhis chod nas 'khrul
NK067(ju)004:1082: pa'i gzhan dbang du gyur pa'i sems can rnams la
NK067(ju)004:1083: rgyud bshad par / e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK067(ju)004:1084: la sogs pa'i shugs kyis gsol ba btab pas srid
NK067(ju)004:1085: pa'i sdug bsngal mtha' dag 'dzin pa phyin ci log
NK067(ju)004:1086: gi rtsa ba can yin pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1087: de nyid kyi phyir 'bral rung glo bur ba kho na yin pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1088: gshis bcing grol gnyis su med pa nam mkha' ltar
NK067(ju)004:1089: dag pas rgyud bstan pa don yod par mkhyen nas
NK067(ju)004:1091: smin ma g.yo ba sogs dgyes tshul drug gis ston par zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:1092: gsum pa 'bras bu yongs shes rgyud don la /
NK067(ju)004:1093: rgyud gsum gyi rnam bzhag spyir bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1094: lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bcu bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:1095: snga ma brjod bya gtso che ba'i dbang du bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1096: phyi ma rjod byed gtso che ba'i dbang du bshad pa zhes kha cig las so //
NK067(ju)004:1098: gang rtogs par bya ba gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud /
NK067(ju)004:1099: gang gis rtogs shing bgrod pa thabs sam lam gyi rgyud /
NK067(ju)004:1100: gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud dang gsum du bshad de /
NK067(ju)004:1101: til la mar yod par shes na btag btsag gi
NK067(ju)004:1102: ngal ba la mi 'dzem par zhugs nas mar 'thob
NK067(ju)004:1103: pa bzhin du rang rgyud la sangs rgyas kyi bsgrub
NK067(ju)004:1104: gzhi mthar thug yod tshul dang /
NK067(ju)004:1105: de'i khyad chos legs par shes na de nyid shin
NK067(ju)004:1106: tu rnam dag 'bras bu'i gnas skabs dang rnam pa
NK067(ju)004:1107: mthun par lam du byas nas yar ldan du 'khyer
NK067(ju)004:1108: ba'i thabs mkhas kyi gnad la nges pa rnyed nas
NK067(ju)004:1110: des mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:1111: tshul 'dis gzhi lam 'bras gsum rgyun gcig tu 'brel bas na rgyud ces gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:1113: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de //
NK067(ju)004:1118: 'di gsum la glan nya tshal ba /
NK067(ju)004:1122: lo chen rin po che ni /
NK067(ju)004:1123: de ltar na lta ba chos can /
NK067(ju)004:1124: lam rgyud ma yin par thal /
NK067(ju)004:1125: lam rgyud la 'jug pa zhes pa'i mtshan nyid kyis khyab pa gang zhig /
NK067(ju)004:1126: khyod 'jug pa ma yin pa'i phyir //
NK067(ju)004:1129: khyod shes pa'i mtshan nyid gang zhig /
NK067(ju)004:1130: shes 'jug gi mtshan nyid gnyis mi gcig pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:1134: mtshan nyid gsum gyi dang po de 'jug pa lam
NK067(ju)004:1135: gyi rgyud yin yang shes 'jug gnyis kyi zlas phye
NK067(ju)004:1136: ba'i 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ma yin pa'i khyad par
NK067(ju)004:1137: 'thad pa'i phyir / zhes lan btab na dpyad dgos so //
NK067(ju)004:1139: 'bras bu'i rgyud la yon tan kyi smin pa mthar thug pa zhes gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:1140: lam gyur gyi 'bras bu la ma khyab gsung /
NK067(ju)004:1142: chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa gzhi /
NK067(ju)004:1143: shes 'jug gi byed rtsol dang bcas pa lam /
NK067(ju)004:1144: chos nyid mngon gyur bogs dbyung du med par son pa 'bras bu zhes bzhed do //
NK067(ju)004:1146: gtso bo'i don gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:1147: zhar byung 'khrul pa btags pa'i gzhi ste gnyis /
NK067(ju)004:1150: 'ching grol med pa'i gnas lugs rang rig pa byang
NK067(ju)004:1151: chub kyi sems bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang
NK067(ju)004:1152: bral bar ye nas gnas pa zhes gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:1153: de la rgyal ba'i gsung rab rnams su brtan g.yo'i
NK067(ju)004:1154: chos thams cad las sems kho na gtso bo yin
NK067(ju)004:1155: par lan cig ma yin par gsungs shing /
NK067(ju)004:1156: sems de la phra rags mang du yod pa las
NK067(ju)004:1157: 'dir ni shin tu phra ba'i sems mthar thug sems
NK067(ju)004:1160: rang bzhin lhan skyes la sogs pa'i ming gis btags pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:1161: rgyud 'dir sems dang ye shes rang snang ba zhes
NK067(ju)004:1162: gsungs pa'i ye shes kyang de kho na yin cing
NK067(ju)004:1163: / sems rags pa gzhan rnams la de gnyis kyi zlas drang ba'i sems zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:1164: de 'dra ba'i ye shes de ni sems gzhan rnams
NK067(ju)004:1165: las nyon dang sdug bsngal gyi 'ching bas gzir bzhin
NK067(ju)004:1166: pa na'ang ngo bo cung zad kyang ma spags pas
NK067(ju)004:1167: bcing grol med pa zhes bya /
NK067(ju)004:1168: rgyud la gsal bar nyams su myong ba na ye
NK067(ju)004:1169: shes rang gi gnas lugs stong pa nyid rig pa
NK067(ju)004:1170: las mtshan ma'i spros pas mi 'phrog pa'am snang srid
NK067(ju)004:1171: thams cad rang snang nyag gcig tu rig pa'i ye
NK067(ju)004:1172: shes kyi snang bar 'gyur bas rang rig pa zhes
NK067(ju)004:1173: bya / gzhan du sems rags pa 'di nyid tshogs
NK067(ju)004:1174: gnyis kyi lam bsgoms pa'i mthus sangs rgyas kyi ye
NK067(ju)004:1175: shes su nar son ba tsam las cher ma bshad
NK067(ju)004:1176: kyang lugs 'dir sems de dag gi gnad gsang rdo
NK067(ju)004:1177: rje'i ye shes 'di kho na byang chub chen po'i
NK067(ju)004:1178: ye shes kyi snying por bzhed pas byang chub kyi
NK067(ju)004:1179: bya / sems zhes bya / bden pa gnyis la
NK067(ju)004:1180: spyir 'jog tshul mang yang 'dir ni gsang ba sgyu
NK067(ju)004:1181: 'phrul ba'i thun mong ma yin pa'i lugs kyi bden
NK067(ju)004:1182: gnyis sam lhag pa'i bden gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:1183: lhag pa don dam bden pa ni /
NK067(ju)004:1184: dbyings spros pa dang bral ba'i cha nas rang bzhin don dam /
NK067(ju)004:1185: rang gsal sgrib g.yogs dang bral ba'i cha nas ye shes don dam /
NK067(ju)004:1186: de nyid sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las te
NK067(ju)004:1187: 'bras chos lnga'i gter du bzhugs pa 'bras bu'i don
NK067(ju)004:1188: dam ste phyi ma la lngar phye bas don dam
NK067(ju)004:1190: mdor 'od gsal gyi mi rtog pa'i cha dang /
NK067(ju)004:1192: des 'bras chos kyi rten byed pa'i cha las so sor phye bar zad do //
NK067(ju)004:1194: de'i rtsal snang zhes bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)004:1195: bde gshegs zur chung ba chos thams cad rig pa'i cho 'phrul du snang ba ma h+aa /
NK067(ju)004:1196: rig pa'i rtsal du snang ba a nu /
NK067(ju)004:1197: rig pa nyid rang snang ba a ti'i lugs zhes
NK067(ju)004:1198: gsungs pa ltar na cho 'phrul zhes brjod na legs
NK067(ju)004:1199: pa 'dra ste / don dam de'i cho 'phrul snod
NK067(ju)004:1200: bcud thams cad dag pa'i 'khor lo rab 'byams su
NK067(ju)004:1202: bu'i don dam gnyis 'byed dka' zhes zer ba yod
NK067(ju)004:1203: kyang 'char gzhi dang shar chos kyi khyad che'o //
NK067(ju)004:1204: bden gnyis de dag ngo bo gcig tu gnas pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1205: zung 'jug ni lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med ces
NK067(ju)004:1206: bya'o // de 'dra ba'i bden gnyis zung 'jug de
NK067(ju)004:1207: blos bcos pa tsam min pa'i yin tshul rjen par
NK067(ju)004:1208: mthong ba ni yul dang yul can du snang ba'i
NK067(ju)004:1209: spros pa rags pa can gyi sems la med pas
NK067(ju)004:1210: sems kyi spyod yul las 'das pa'am spyod yul dang
NK067(ju)004:1212: blo'i spyod yul dang bral bar bstan pa 'di 'dra
NK067(ju)004:1213: rnams kyis 'khrul gzhi byas nas don dam bden pa
NK067(ju)004:1214: shes bya min zhes smra bar ni mi bya ste
NK067(ju)004:1215: / de ltar smra na he ru ka galpo las /
NK067(ju)004:1216: shes bya'i nang nas dam par ni //
NK067(ju)004:1217: gyur phyir nges pa'i tshig yin no //
NK067(ju)004:1219: zhal lung du mdo'i don bsdus drangs par /
NK067(ju)004:1220: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK067(ju)004:1221: ji bzhin ngang du ye gnas pa //
NK067(ju)004:1222: shes par bya ba'i rgyud don yin //
NK067(ju)004:1224: rig 'dzin gong ma thams cad kyis gzhi shes pa
NK067(ju)004:1225: dang 'bras bu thob pa ste lam rgyud kyi bya
NK067(ju)004:1226: ba gnyis byed par gsungs pa sogs dang dngos su
NK067(ju)004:1227: 'gal zhing rig pa'i gnod pa mtha' yas pa'i phyir
NK067(ju)004:1228: ro // gzhan yang ji skad brjod pa'i ye shes
NK067(ju)004:1229: de sems kyi gnyug ma'i rang bzhin las ngo bo
NK067(ju)004:1230: gzhan du mi 'gyur bar bzhugs pas na ye nas
NK067(ju)004:1232: snang gsum 'pho ba'i bag chags las skyes pa'i sems
NK067(ju)004:1233: rags pa ni 'bras bu'i sa na med cing de'i
NK067(ju)004:1234: dbang gis de dag stong gzhir byas pa'i stong nyid
NK067(ju)004:1235: kyang de na med pas de bzhin gshegs pa'i chos
NK067(ju)004:1236: nyid kyi skur 'gro rgyu'i de kho na nyid ni
NK067(ju)004:1237: gnyug ma'i ye shes 'di'i dbyings la bzhag dgos pas
NK067(ju)004:1238: 'khor lo tha ma'i mdo sde rnams su gang la
NK067(ju)004:1239: dgongs te bde gshegs snying po bstan pa'i dgongs gzhi
NK067(ju)004:1240: mthar thug kyang 'di nyid yin cing /
NK067(ju)004:1241: 'on kyang de la dgongs te gsungs pa'i mod sde
NK067(ju)004:1242: dag gnyug sems ston pa'i sde snod ni min zhes
NK067(ju)004:1244: 'dir ni rgyal ba klong chen pa sogs mchog gzigs
NK067(ju)004:1245: gong ma mang po mdo de dag gis bstan pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1246: gshegs snying dang / 'dir bstan gnyug sems don gcig
NK067(ju)004:1247: pas de dag gi dgongs gzhir ma zad brjod bya
NK067(ju)004:1248: yang 'di kho na yid zhes bzhed la /
NK067(ju)004:1249: de lta na mdo sngags khyad med du mi 'gyur ram zhe na /
NK067(ju)004:1250: 'di la smin gling lo chen rin po che sogs
NK067(ju)004:1251: ni rig pa 'gyur med sbyang gzhir 'dod pa la
NK067(ju)004:1252: khyad med kyang de nyid lhan skyes mi 'gyur ba'i
NK067(ju)004:1253: bde ba'i rang bzhin du 'dod pa sngags kyi khyad
NK067(ju)004:1255: don 'di dka' ba'i gnad yin pas kun mkhyen yab
NK067(ju)004:1256: sras kyi gzhung la brten nas dpyad pa'i sgo tsam
NK067(ju)004:1257: smos na / bla med kyi rgyud nas gsungs pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1258: gnyug sems dang 'khor lo tha ma nas bstan pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1259: gshegs snying gnyis ming mi 'dra yang don gcig la
NK067(ju)004:1260: smos na / / don de 'gro ba thams cad
NK067(ju)004:1261: la khyab par bzhugs kyang gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa'i sems
NK067(ju)004:1262: kyis bsgribs nas ma mthong ba yin pas /
NK067(ju)004:1263: de mngon du byed pa la 'khrul pa'i sems 'di
NK067(ju)004:1264: sbyang dgos par bzhed pa la'ang mdo sngags khyad par
NK067(ju)004:1265: med mod kyi / sbyang tshul mi 'dra ste /
NK067(ju)004:1266: mdo sder ma zad rnal 'byor rgyud man chad du'ang
NK067(ju)004:1267: sems rags pa 'di nyid kho na'i steng nas zab
NK067(ju)004:1268: cing rgya che'i lam bsgoms te rim gyis rnam par
NK067(ju)004:1269: mi rtog pa'i dbyings su sbyangs nas /
NK067(ju)004:1270: mthar gshegs snying dngos la rig par ston pa sha stag yin la /
NK067(ju)004:1271: rdo rje slob dpon gyis dbang bskur ba'i thabs kyis
NK067(ju)004:1272: bde gshegs snying po'i 'od gsal de sku gsum du
NK067(ju)004:1273: sad pa'i rten 'brel bsgrigs pa sngon du btang bas
NK067(ju)004:1274: da lta nas kun rtog 'khrul pa'i sems 'di thad
NK067(ju)004:1275: kar gcod pa'i thabs mkhas kyi 'phrul gsang zab mos
NK067(ju)004:1276: gnyug sems mngon du phyung ste de nyid yar ldan
NK067(ju)004:1277: du khyer nas 'bras bu la bde myur du sbyor
NK067(ju)004:1278: byed 'khor dang bcas pa ni bla med kyi rgyud
NK067(ju)004:1279: las gzhan du bstan pa med cing /
NK067(ju)004:1280: lam sgrub tshul snga ma'i skabs su mi mkho ba'i rtsa rlung thig le'i rnam bzhag dang /
NK067(ju)004:1281: gnyug sems bde ba chen po'i ldog pa nas bstan pa sogs kyang mdo sde'i phyogs na med do //
NK067(ju)004:1282: de ltar bshad na theg pa gong 'og gi rnam
NK067(ju)004:1283: bzhag thams cad kyang pad+ma'i 'dab ma ltar ma 'dzing
NK067(ju)004:1285: bde gshegs snying po'i mdo mnyan du rung ba la
NK067(ju)004:1286: dbang thob dgos par thal bar yang mi 'gyur te
NK067(ju)004:1287: / dbang bskur ba ni gtso bor bla med kyi lam la slob pa'i ched yin pa'i phyir te /
NK067(ju)004:1288: dper na lugs gzhan du'ang bla med kyi skabs su
NK067(ju)004:1289: 'bad pa du mas lhan skyes kyi bde ba bsgrubs
NK067(ju)004:1290: pa'i don po bde ba des stong nyid sgom pa
NK067(ju)004:1291: yin yang stong nyid mnyan pa la dbang nod mi
NK067(ju)004:1293: mdo sde'i phyogs nas de 'dra'i gshegs snying bstan pa
NK067(ju)004:1294: de da lta nas lam du bya ba'i ched min
NK067(ju)004:1295: na dgos pa ci yod ce na /
NK067(ju)004:1296: 'di'i skyon spong byed tshul rgyud bla ma'i /
NK067(ju)004:1297: sprin dang rmi lam sgyu bzhin de dang der //
NK067(ju)004:1298: zhes sogs kyi skabs rgyu mtshan lnga gsungs pa la sogs pa'i steng nas shes dgos te /
NK067(ju)004:1299: de la'ang gzhi bca' dgos shing /
NK067(ju)004:1300: rgyud bla'i 'grel par gshegs snying la rtag pa'i chos nyid ces gsungs pa sogs dang /
NK067(ju)004:1301: de bas kyang ches bshad dka' ba 'ga' zhig yod
NK067(ju)004:1302: pa'i 'gal spongs sogs kun mkhyen chen po'i gzhung rnams
NK067(ju)004:1303: khog bsgrigs nas shes par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:1306: 'khor lo tha ma'i mdo dang rgyud bla ma sogs
NK067(ju)004:1307: la brten nas sngags kyi 'od gsal gtan la phab
NK067(ju)004:1308: pa rnams / mdo bstan bcos de dag rang rang
NK067(ju)004:1309: gi dgongs gzhi mthar thug dang sbyar ba'i steng nas
NK067(ju)004:1310: bshad na 'di ltar 'gyur zhes zab mo'i mdo sde
NK067(ju)004:1311: rnams kyi dgongs don mthar thug gsang sngags bla med
NK067(ju)004:1312: la gzhol tshul bstan pa tsam du dgongs pa blang
NK067(ju)004:1313: na'ang 'gal ba cher ma mthong ste /
NK067(ju)004:1314: rang lugs 'dzin pa rnams kyis zhib tu dpyad par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:1315: ye shes de 'khor 'das gnyis kyi gzhir 'gyur tshul ni /
NK067(ju)004:1316: sems can rnams 'gro ba lngar 'khor ba na phung
NK067(ju)004:1317: po snga mas chu la thim pa sogs kyi rim
NK067(ju)004:1318: pas 'od gsal gyi dbyings de nyid du sdud cing
NK067(ju)004:1319: / slar yang de nyid gzhom med kyi rlung dang
NK067(ju)004:1320: bcas pa las snang ba gsum dang kun rtog gi
NK067(ju)004:1321: rlung sems rim gyis mched de bar srid dang skye
NK067(ju)004:1322: / ba 'grub la / skye ba blangs nas kyang
NK067(ju)004:1323: las nyon gyis phyi ma'i sdug bsngal gyi phung po
NK067(ju)004:1324: phyi snod dang bcas pa 'du byed cing /
NK067(ju)004:1325: ji ltar 'du byas pa bzhin du 'grub ste /
NK067(ju)004:1326: de ltar zo chun gyi 'khor lo ltar 'khor ba
NK067(ju)004:1327: ni bla med kyi rgyud gsar rnying phal cher nas
NK067(ju)004:1328: gsungs la / da lta gson lus la gnas dus
NK067(ju)004:1329: kyang gzung 'dzin rags pa'i rlung sems kyi cha thams
NK067(ju)004:1330: cad nyi 'od dang de'i drod bzhin du ye shes
NK067(ju)004:1331: kyi rlung sems kyis khyab nas gnas pas yul snang
NK067(ju)004:1332: thams cad la yang 'od gsal ye shes kyi snang
NK067(ju)004:1333: ba'i cha re med mi srid la /
NK067(ju)004:1334: de dag las ye shes kyi rlung sems rnams ni gnyug ma'i cha dang /
NK067(ju)004:1335: rags pa'i cha rnams de'i cho 'phrul du byung ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:1336: de srog tu yod pa'i dbang gis rang rang gi bya ba la 'jug pa yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1337: ye shes 'khrul pa'i rlung sems su mched pa na
NK067(ju)004:1338: de'i dbang gis ye shes kyi snang ba'ang 'khrul snang
NK067(ju)004:1339: du song ba yin pas snang sems thams cad kyi
NK067(ju)004:1340: rtsa ba'i gzhi sems nyid 'od gsal kho nar 'dod
NK067(ju)004:1341: pa ni gsang sngags snga 'gyur nas bshad pa ste
NK067(ju)004:1342: / 'od gsal gyi ye shes lus la gnas pa
NK067(ju)004:1343: dang shar ba mi gcig cing 'char ba'i thabs kyang
NK067(ju)004:1345: 'chi dus su shar ba sogs nam mkha' rkyen gsum
NK067(ju)004:1346: dang bral ba lta bu'i stong sang gi rnam pa
NK067(ju)004:1347: can dang / d+h+au ti'i rtsa 'khor gyi nang kho
NK067(ju)004:1348: nar 'char ba sogs yin yang 'od gsal gang yin
NK067(ju)004:1349: thams cad de ltar ma nges te /
NK067(ju)004:1350: 'di tsam zhig snang ba lhar sgrub sogs skabs du
NK067(ju)004:1351: mar mkho bas smos kyi rgyas par rdzogs chen gyi
NK067(ju)004:1352: skor las 'byung ba ma bkod do //
NK067(ju)004:1353: de ni kun nyon 'khor ba'i chos kyi gzhi byed lugs yin la /
NK067(ju)004:1354: rnam byang phyogs kyi gzhi byed lugs gzhan yang yod mod de //
NK067(ju)004:1355: gtso bo ni gong du byang chub sems kyi don bshad par brjod zin to //
NK067(ju)004:1356: 'di dag gi skabs su ye shes rang snang zhes
NK067(ju)004:1357: bshad pa ni ye shes nyid las gzhan du ma
NK067(ju)004:1359: ye shes kyi rang dbang gi 'char tshul ltar bzhag pa dag pa'i snang ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:1360: sems rang snang zhes pa ni ye shes de sems
NK067(ju)004:1361: kyis dkrugs pa'i dbang gis snang sems rang rgyud par
NK067(ju)004:1362: 'char ba ma dag pa'i dngos snang rnams te /
NK067(ju)004:1363: de dag kyang sems rang gis btags pa tsam gyi snang char zad kyi /
NK067(ju)004:1364: ngo bo nyid kyis grub pa med pas rang snang zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:1365: phyi ma'i gnas lus sogs ni ye shes kyi cha
NK067(ju)004:1366: dang sems kyi char gyur pa gang yang min pas
NK067(ju)004:1367: rang snang dngos ma yin yang /
NK067(ju)004:1368: sems ye shes su bskyed pa'i le'ura /
NK067(ju)004:1369: nyid las gzhan zhes bya ba'i chos //
NK067(ju)004:1370: btsal yang rgyal bas mi brnyes so //
NK067(ju)004:1371: zhes sogs snang srid dag mnyam du bstan pa rnams
NK067(ju)004:1372: kyi dgongs don gtan la dbab pa'i phyir 'khor 'das
NK067(ju)004:1373: kyi chos thams cad rang snang gi phyogs su bsdus
NK067(ju)004:1377: 'khrul pa la gzhi yod ces rog bde gshegs chen po gsung ba ltar /
NK067(ju)004:1378: gnyug ma'i rang bzhin la 'khrul pa med kyang de'i cho 'phrul 'khrul par shar te /
NK067(ju)004:1379: gnas lugs kyi rang zhal 'gebs shing sgrib par byed
NK067(ju)004:1380: pa'i zhen snang ni phyin ci log tu sgro btags
NK067(ju)004:1381: nas 'khor ba phra rags kyi rten du gyur pas
NK067(ju)004:1382: 'khrul pa btags pa'i gzhi zhes bya /
NK067(ju)004:1383: de yang gzhung spyi skad dang bstun na snang sems
NK067(ju)004:1384: la phyin ci log tu snang zhing snang ba ltar
NK067(ju)004:1385: zhen pas na zhen snang zhes sbyor dgos par mngon
NK067(ju)004:1386: yang / 'di'i bka' srol du 'das pa snang yang 'khor bar zhen pa zhes gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:1387: de ltar na snang ba lhar ma rtogs par gzhan du zhen pa zhes bshad par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:1388: gang ltar yang don du gnyis med la gnyis su 'dzin pa la 'jog par bshad de /
NK067(ju)004:1389: rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid las gzhan du ma
NK067(ju)004:1390: gyur pa'i dngos po rnams la phyi rol du gyur
NK067(ju)004:1391: pa'i snang ba rang rgyud pa'am rang dbang ba dang
NK067(ju)004:1393: de'ang gnas lugs kyi don las gzhan du gol ba'i
NK067(ju)004:1394: rgyu'i gtso bo rmongs pa ma rig pa yin zhing
NK067(ju)004:1395: / de la lhan skyes dang kun btags gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:1396: de gnyis kyang 'dir grub mtha' ngan pas btags ma
NK067(ju)004:1397: btags la ma bzhag par ngo bo'i dbyings la rmongs
NK067(ju)004:1398: tsam gyi ma rtogs pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1399: snang sems rang rgyud du zhen pa'i log rtog gi
NK067(ju)004:1400: ma rig pa gnyis la bshad pa'i gtso bo phyi
NK067(ju)004:1401: ma ste // 'dir bstan zhen snang ni de'o //
NK067(ju)004:1402: sangs rgyas su 'grub pa'i bsgrub gzhi'i dbang du byas nas ngo bo'i gzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:1403: sems can du gol ba'i 'khor rtsa'i dbang du byas nas btags pa'i gzhi bstan par sems te /
NK067(ju)004:1404: snga ma ma bstan na 'di'i grub mtha'i snying po
NK067(ju)004:1405: chos thams cad ye sangs rgyas par gtan la dbab
NK067(ju)004:1406: du med la / phyi ma ma bstan na de
NK067(ju)004:1407: la ltos pa'i sbyang bya'i gtso bo ngos mi zin
NK067(ju)004:1408: pas dngos dang zhar byung gi tshul du gnyis smos
NK067(ju)004:1409: du med la / so // gnyis pa ni /
NK067(ju)004:1410: skyed byed shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis bskyed bya
NK067(ju)004:1411: thun mong dang mchog gi sems lnga skyes sam skyes
NK067(ju)004:1413: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK067(ju)004:1414: sems lnga skyes par bstan pa yin //
NK067(ju)004:1416: 'dir thun mong gi sems lnga ni /
NK067(ju)004:1420: phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi lam rnams re re zhing sems lnga re brtsi ba yin la /
NK067(ju)004:1422: ma h+aa yo ga'i rang lam nyid la brtsi ba ste /
NK067(ju)004:1423: lam de dang de la 'jug 'dod kyi sems dang por ldang ba g.yo ldang /
NK067(ju)004:1424: lam de rnyed na ci ma rung snyam du 'dun pa'i shugs cher song ba smon pa /
NK067(ju)004:1425: smon pa bzhin du 'jug pa 'jug pa /
NK067(ju)004:1426: zhugs nas nyams len gyi rgyun la gnas pa gnas pa /
NK067(ju)004:1427: mthar 'dod don grub pa mthar phyin pa'i sems te /
NK067(ju)004:1428: 'di rnams re re'i mthar byang chub kyi sems zhes
NK067(ju)004:1429: sbyar snang ba mchog gi sems lnga'i dbang du byas
NK067(ju)004:1430: pa'am / yang na nyan rang gi theg pa'i sems
NK067(ju)004:1431: lnga'am de dag rang gi byang chub la ltos nas
NK067(ju)004:1432: de ltar brjod pa'am sgra 'jug pa la bshad du
NK067(ju)004:1433: yod pas ma khyab pa gang bde'i steng nas bsnyad
NK067(ju)004:1434: pa'am / par bya'o // de'ang nyan thos kyi sde
NK067(ju)004:1435: snod nas de'i lam rnams sems lngar bsdus te bstan
NK067(ju)004:1437: rgyud sde 'di'i gzhung las nyan thos kyi lam rnams sems lngar bsdus nas bstan pa sogs yin no //
NK067(ju)004:1438: ci ltar na thabs sam lam gyi rgyud du 'gyur zhe na /
NK067(ju)004:1439: thob bya 'bras rgyud mngon du byed pa'i lhan cig byed rkyen yin pas thabs dang /
NK067(ju)004:1440: gang gis gang du bgrod pa'i shul yin pas lam mo //
NK067(ju)004:1441: de la gtso phal gyi sgo nas dbye na /
NK067(ju)004:1442: nye ba'i lam bla med sgyu d+r+wa'i lam 'di nyid dang /
NK067(ju)004:1443: ring ba'i lam thun mong gi theg pa bzhi dang phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi lam rnams te /
NK067(ju)004:1444: de'ang 'di'i dngos kyi gdul byas lam 'di bor nas
NK067(ju)004:1445: de dag la 'jug na mchog gi dngos grub las
NK067(ju)004:1447: theg pa gzhan gyi rigs can gyis rang lam sgrub na'ang dman lam sngon song lta ci /
NK067(ju)004:1448: dang po nas phar phyin dang phyi rgyud kyi lam
NK067(ju)004:1449: nas zhugs kyang lam 'di pa la ltos na rdzogs
NK067(ju)004:1450: byang dus ring mo zhig na 'grub pas ring lam
NK067(ju)004:1451: zhes bya yi / khog gzhung las /
NK067(ju)004:1452: thun mong lam stegs tsam nyid du //
NK067(ju)004:1453: pha rol phyin bcu rgyu 'bras spyod //
NK067(ju)004:1454: ces pa ltar 'di'i lam la dbang po dang bsam
NK067(ju)004:1455: pa'i snod sbyong ba'i ched du thun mong gi rtogs
NK067(ju)004:1456: rigs la slob pa tsam ni nye ring thun mong
NK067(ju)004:1458: khyad par gyi lam de la dbye na /
NK067(ju)004:1459: thabs kyis nges pa'i lam dang /
NK067(ju)004:1460: shes rab kyis rnam par grol ba'i lam gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:1462: grol lam thabs su rnam par bstan //
NK067(ju)004:1464: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
