NK067(ju)004:1465: spyir thabs lam zhes pa'i tshig zur gyi thabs ni grol lam gyi nang du'ang yod de /
NK067(ju)004:1467: grol lam gyi skabs su bshad pa'i chos nyid rtogs pa'i shes rab kyang thabs lam la dgos te /
NK067(ju)004:1468: de dang bral na lam gyi snying po stor ba'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:1469: 'on kyang gang zag gcig gi lam la thabs grol gnyis ka 'jog pa'am ma yin te /
NK067(ju)004:1470: thabs lam pa dang grol lam pa zhes gang zag
NK067(ju)004:1471: tha dad kyi lam cha tshang gnyis su bzhed do
NK067(ju)004:1472: // des na lam gyi gzhung shing rdzogs rim la
NK067(ju)004:1473: ltos nas rtsol ba dang por lus la gnad du
NK067(ju)004:1474: bsnun pa'i thabs kyi man ngag la brten pa dang
NK067(ju)004:1475: // / sems rang babs kyi steng du 'jog pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1476: bzhag thabs tsam la brten pa'i khyad par du bshad
NK067(ju)004:1478: 'dir dgongs rgyan ltar gtso bor shes rab gsum gyi
NK067(ju)004:1479: sgo nas rang rgyud kyi 'ching ba chos nyid du
NK067(ju)004:1480: grol bar byed pa grol lam dang /
NK067(ju)004:1481: gtso bor thabs kyi khyad par brtul zhugs kyi spyod
NK067(ju)004:1482: pa rmad du byung ba'i sgo nas 'bras bu myur
NK067(ju)004:1483: du 'grub par byed pa thabs lam du bya ste
NK067(ju)004:1484: nyi ston chos seng sogs kyi bzhed pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:1485: de'ang lhag pa'i bden gnyis dbyer med kyi bzhugs tshul
NK067(ju)004:1486: rtogs nas goms par byed pa ni 'di nyid kyi
NK067(ju)004:1488: gtso bor de tsam gyi steng nas lam bgrod pa ni grol lam dang /
NK067(ju)004:1489: de'i steng du man ngag gi thabs zur pa bsnan
NK067(ju)004:1490: nas de la'ang gtso bor brten te lam bgrod pa
NK067(ju)004:1491: la thabs lam du bzhag pa yin pas /
NK067(ju)004:1492: mtshan nyid gsum gyi khog rgyas par grol lam gyi skabs su bstan zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1493: thabs lam 'chad dus thabs lam rang gi sgos chos
NK067(ju)004:1494: tsam las cher ma bshad pa'ang de'i rgyu mtshan la
NK067(ju)004:1495: thug ste / thabs lam la mtshan nyid gsum med pa ni gtan min no //
NK067(ju)004:1496: dper na phar phyin drug sngags lam la yang tshang mod kyi /
NK067(ju)004:1497: sngags kyi theg pa phar phyin theg pa ma yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1498: phyin drug gi spyod pa'i skor la phar phyin theg pa'i gzhung rnams rgyas la /
NK067(ju)004:1499: sngags su gsang sngags rang gi khyad chos rnams gtso bor ston pa dang 'dra'o //
NK067(ju)004:1500: de ltar thabs grol so sor gtso bor gang byed
NK067(ju)004:1501: kyi lam la khyab che chung bshad pa 'dis mtshan
NK067(ju)004:1502: don dang gleng gzhi sogs kyi skabs su grol lam
NK067(ju)004:1503: ltar bshad pa rnams la thun mong ltar ram spyi
NK067(ju)004:1504: ltar bshad pa zhes 'byung ba'i go don yang shes
NK067(ju)004:1505: par mngon no // lam myur bul gyi dbang du byas na /
NK067(ju)004:1506: grol lam ni rin po che koostu b+ha dang lhan
NK067(ju)004:1507: cig bzhag pa'i rdo'i khams rim gyi gser du 'gyur
NK067(ju)004:1509: thabs lam ni mak+shi ka'i sbyor bas lcags khams yud
NK067(ju)004:1510: tsam gyi gser du sgyur ba lta bur bshad la
NK067(ju)004:1511: / grol lam rim gyis pa thabs lam rim gyis ba las bul yang /
NK067(ju)004:1512: grol lam cig car ba ni thabs lam cig char
NK067(ju)004:1513: ba las kyang myur zhes gsung srol yang snang ngo
NK067(ju)004:1514: // de la thun mong sngon dang khyad par rjes
NK067(ju)004:1515: su bshad pa'i dbang du btang ste grol lam dang
NK067(ju)004:1516: // por dang / 'chad bde ba la bsam nas
NK067(ju)004:1517: thabs lam dang por 'chad pa gang yang rung zhes
NK067(ju)004:1518: gsungs pa las 'dir dgongs rgyan ltar thabs lam sngon
NK067(ju)004:1520: thabs lam nyid la'ang thabs dang thabs byung gi rnal
NK067(ju)004:1521: 'byor gnyis yod pa'i go rim dang bstun na thabs
NK067(ju)004:1522: sngon la 'ong zhing thabs byung grol lam gyi sgrom
NK067(ju)004:1523: nas shes pa'i yang phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:1526: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i lam mo //
NK067(ju)004:1527: d+h+au ti'i nang du khams bzhu brtul gyi las kyis
NK067(ju)004:1528: ye shes 'char bar byed pas na 'ju 'dul gyi
NK067(ju)004:1529: lam dang / rgyud kyi le'u bzhi par yul sku /
NK067(ju)004:1531: rnam shes thugs su gsungs shing lus snang ba 'dod khams /
NK067(ju)004:1533: yid mi snang gzugs med khams su bshad pa'i gtso
NK067(ju)004:1534: bo pad+ma'i reg bya dang rdo rje'i dbang po dang
NK067(ju)004:1535: bde ba'i rnam shes gsum sbyar ba'i sngags kyi rol
NK067(ju)004:1536: rtsed yin pas na khams gsum rol pa zhes bya
NK067(ju)004:1537: ste / snga ma rang lus dang phyi ma gzhan lus la brten pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:1538: 'ju 'dul gyi lam la gtso bor byed pas kyang
NK067(ju)004:1539: bogs 'don du khams gsum rol ba la slob dgos
NK067(ju)004:1540: shing / khams gsum rol pa gtso bor byed pas
NK067(ju)004:1541: kyang sngon du 'ju 'dul gyi lam gyi rtsa thig
NK067(ju)004:1542: rlung gsum las rung nges par 'gro dgos kyang /
NK067(ju)004:1543: gtso bor gang byed la ltos nas gang zag gnyis
NK067(ju)004:1544: kyi lam du bzhag kyang chog ste snga ma bzhin
NK067(ju)004:1545: no // dang po steng sgo'i rnal 'byor la gnyis bshad de /
NK067(ju)004:1550: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK067(ju)004:1551: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK067(ju)004:1552: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK067(ju)004:1558: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo ste rtsa ba'i 'khor lo bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:1559: de 'og sor bzhi gzhal bar lte ba'i gtum mo
NK067(ju)004:1560: las yar 'bar ba rgyud gzhan du tshangs pa'i me
NK067(ju)004:1561: zhes grags pa'i me dkyil dang /
NK067(ju)004:1562: de'i 'og na me de sbor byed thun sel gyi rlung ste rkyen gyi 'khor lo gnyis so //
NK067(ju)004:1566: 'khor lo bzhi'i lte bar dmigs pas gnad du bsnun
NK067(ju)004:1567: pa las ro rkyang gi rgyu ba 'gag cig rlung
NK067(ju)004:1569: d+h+au ti'i lam drang po nas song ste nam mkha'i
NK067(ju)004:1570: ba zhes pa spyi bo'i ham yig bskul te mu
NK067(ju)004:1571: tig lta bu'i byang chub kyi sems babs pa las
NK067(ju)004:1572: yas babs dang mas brtan gyi dga' bzhi nyams su
NK067(ju)004:1573: myong zhing / khyad par du lhan skyes kyi dga'
NK067(ju)004:1574: ba'i dus su gdal khyab spros pa med pa'i dbyings
NK067(ju)004:1575: myong zhing / la spyod pa'o // gnyis pa la /
NK067(ju)004:1576: lus las ye shes skye ba'i gnad dang /
NK067(ju)004:1577: de shes nas gnad du bsnun tshul gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:1579: sngar bshad pa ltar gdon nas rnam par dag pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1580: rang gnas kyi ye shes de da lta rdo rje'i
NK067(ju)004:1581: lus la ji ltar gnas pa'i tshul ni /
NK067(ju)004:1582: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i lte bar dwangs ma
NK067(ju)004:1583: chen po lnga'i dbus na stong gsal bde ba chen
NK067(ju)004:1585: snang ba thams cad kyi 'char gzhir bzhugs te /
NK067(ju)004:1587: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK067(ju)004:1588: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK067(ju)004:1589: mi shigs thig le bde chen po //
NK067(ju)004:1590: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK067(ju)004:1591: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK067(ju)004:1594: mi shigs ye shes thig le ni //
NK067(ju)004:1595: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK067(ju)004:1596: gcig dang du ma rnam spangs pa //
NK067(ju)004:1597: sna tshogs snang la mtshon du med //
NK067(ju)004:1599: de las cho 'phrul 'byung ba'i nus pa rim gyis
NK067(ju)004:1600: sad pa na dang por de nyid dang rjes su
NK067(ju)004:1601: mthun pa dag pa'i snang ba skul ba'i byed las
NK067(ju)004:1602: can gyi dkar dmar rlung gsum gyi cha phra mo
NK067(ju)004:1603: gzhan dag 'byung ba ni nye ba'i dwangs chen te
NK067(ju)004:1604: / dwangs ma gzhan thams cad kyi zungs sam gnad du gyur pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:1605: de dag thog med nas brgyud de 'ongs pa'i log
NK067(ju)004:1606: pa'i zhen snang gi chas dkrugs pa las ma dag
NK067(ju)004:1607: pa'i snang ba ngan pa bskyed pa'i rtsa khams rlung
NK067(ju)004:1608: gsum snyigs ma'i cha gtso bo rnams 'byung zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1609: de dang mnyam du rang snang gi yul rnams kyang
NK067(ju)004:1610: chu shin tu mnyen pa dgun gyi grang reg gi
NK067(ju)004:1611: rkyen gyis rdo ltar sra ba'i khams su 'gyur ba
NK067(ju)004:1612: ltar tha mal ba'i rnam par shar nas slar la
NK067(ju)004:1613: zhen snang rgyas par byed de /
NK067(ju)004:1614: de ltar 'khrul pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi 'khor lo bskor ba yin no //
NK067(ju)004:1615: de'ang cung zad zhib tu bshad na /
NK067(ju)004:1616: lugs 'dir snying ga'i gnad gtso bor byed de /
NK067(ju)004:1617: de la dgongs rgyan ltar rtsa gdab brgyad dam rtsa chen bzhi las /
NK067(ju)004:1618: mdun chos nyid kyi rtsa la nye ba'i dwangs ma mo dang snyigs ma su tri /
NK067(ju)004:1619: g.yas ye shes kyi rtsa la dwangs ma h'u dang snyigs ma a n+ri /
NK067(ju)004:1620: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa la dwangs ma +aahdang snyigs ma pre du'i yi ge rnams gnas te /
NK067(ju)004:1621: yi ge gsum po 'dab ma'i nang phyogs d+h+au ti dang nye ba na dang /
NK067(ju)004:1622: sa bon drug po rtsa 'dab kyi sgab bam mthar gnas so //
NK067(ju)004:1623: nye ba'i dwangs ma de dag ni dbus kyi dwangs ma lnga'i yon tan las byung ste /
NK067(ju)004:1624: yig sha'am rtsa'i dwangs ma shel sbug can gyi yon tan las byung /
NK067(ju)004:1625: lus la rtsa'i dwangs cha dang de'i yon tan rnams
NK067(ju)004:1626: skyed cing skyes zin gyi rgyun gsos nas rgyas par
NK067(ju)004:1627: byed do // +aah yig mi shigs pa'i dmar cha'i yon tan las byung /
NK067(ju)004:1628: khrag gi dwangs cha dang yon tan skyed cing gso /
NK067(ju)004:1629: h'u yig mi shigs pa'i rlung gi yon tan gyi dbang las byung /
NK067(ju)004:1630: dbugs kyi dwangs cha dang yon tan skyed cing gaso'o //
NK067(ju)004:1631: du 'jog pa ni thig le de la dag pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1632: gzugs snang sna tshogs skyed pa'i nus pa shas cher
NK067(ju)004:1633: yod pa'i sgo nas yin te /
NK067(ju)004:1634: sku rdo rje'i sa bon yin pas so //
NK067(ju)004:1635: des mtshon te sgra tshig gi sna ba ris med skyed pa'i sgo nas +aahdang /
NK067(ju)004:1636: ting nge 'dzin bzang po skyed pa'i sgo nas h'u du 'jog pa'ang shes par bya la /
NK067(ju)004:1637: da lta sku sgrub byed kyi las bsags ba rnams gyi steng du gsog pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1638: gsung sgrub byed rnams +aahl gsog pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1639: thugs sgrub byed h'u la gsog par yang bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:1640: de bzhin du su tri gnyis la rtsa'i snyigs ma skyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1641: lha min dang dud 'gro'i snang zhen skyed pa'i nus pa gnyis yod cing /
NK067(ju)004:1642: da lta 'gro ba de gnyis su skye ba'i las
NK067(ju)004:1643: bsags pa rnams kyis kyang de gnyis kyi nus pa
NK067(ju)004:1645: pre du gnyis kyis khrag gi snyigs ma la bya ba 'jug cing /
NK067(ju)004:1646: yi dwags dang dmyal ba'i snang zhen skyed pa sogs dang /
NK067(ju)004:1647: a n+ris dbugs kyi snyigs ma la bya ba 'jug cing /
NK067(ju)004:1648: lha mi gnyis kyi snang zhen skyed pa sogs kyang shes par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:1650: dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi snying po sems mi shigs
NK067(ju)004:1651: pa'i steng na snang ba ris su ma chad pa
NK067(ju)004:1652: spro ba'i nus pa yod pa de da lta 'gro
NK067(ju)004:1653: ba rigs drug gang rung gi sa bon gyi kha
NK067(ju)004:1654: lo drangs te 'khrul snang rang dga' ba'i yo lang
NK067(ju)004:1655: chen po shar ba 'di dag pa rab 'byams kyi
NK067(ju)004:1656: snang bar go 'phos nas don dam dkor bdun gyi
NK067(ju)004:1657: gnas lugs la 'jug pa'i ched du lta ba dang
NK067(ju)004:1658: bskyed rim sngon du btang ste /
NK067(ju)004:1659: kun tu bzang po'i thig le'am snying ga'i mi shigs
NK067(ju)004:1660: pa'i sems 'dzin rtse gcig tu sbyangs pas thig le
NK067(ju)004:1661: de 'bar zhing las su rung nas sems mi shigs
NK067(ju)004:1662: pa 'od gsal bsam mi khyab kyi dgongs pa kun
NK067(ju)004:1663: rtog gi rnyogs pa dang bral bar 'char la /
NK067(ju)004:1664: de'i tshe sngar bskyed rim la sbyangs pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1665: dwangs ma lnga'i sems 'dzin gyi khog tu ye shes
NK067(ju)004:1666: kyi snang ba thun min 'char ba'i rtsa dar skud
NK067(ju)004:1667: lta bu'am shel sbug can la gnad du bsnun pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1668: rgyu mtshan gyis mi shigs pa'i steng gi dag pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1669: snang ba 'char ba'i nus pa gsal bar sad de
NK067(ju)004:1670: me long dwangs pa la gzugs brnyan 'char ba'i tshul
NK067(ju)004:1671: du sku dang zhing gi snang ba tshad med pa
NK067(ju)004:1672: mthong ste / de'i mthus dang po byung ba'i rim
NK067(ju)004:1673: pa ltar yi ge gsum gyi gzi brjid dang nus
NK067(ju)004:1674: mthong ste / pa cher sbar / de dag sbar
NK067(ju)004:1675: ba'i dbang gis mar me gsos na rang 'od mched
NK067(ju)004:1676: nas 'ong ba ltar stod smad kyi lus kun gyi
NK067(ju)004:1677: dwangs ma rnams stobs su gyur cing 'bar nas rtsa
NK067(ju)004:1678: khams bde bas rgyas par 'gyur la /
NK067(ju)004:1679: shin tu phra ba dang rags pa'i phyogs sam dwangs
NK067(ju)004:1680: ma ye shes dang ma dag snyigs ma'i phyogs kyi
NK067(ju)004:1681: rtsa rlung thig le ni gcig rgyas pa na cig
NK067(ju)004:1682: shos zhum 'gro ba chos nyid yin pas yi ge
NK067(ju)004:1683: gsum ji ltar 'bar ba de ltar sa bon drug
NK067(ju)004:1684: pa'i nus pa chung du 'gro ste /
NK067(ju)004:1685: 'di la rdzogs rim pa'i rigs drug sreg sbyang yang zer ro //
NK067(ju)004:1686: 'di ltar mi shigs gnyug ma'i dwangs chen bskul stobs
NK067(ju)004:1687: kyis rtsa 'dab kyi dwangs ma sbar ba ni ji
NK067(ju)004:1688: tsam sbar ba de'i tshod du de rnams mi shigs
NK067(ju)004:1690: rim gyi dwangs ma gzhan rnams rtsa ba'i yi ge gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:1691: de gsum yang dwangs ma lnga ldan la zhugs nas
NK067(ju)004:1692: mchog gi dwangs ma'i nus pa lhag par gsal bar
NK067(ju)004:1694: dwangs ma lnga las sas bde ba brtan par byed /
NK067(ju)004:1695: chus bde ba sdud cing mnyen /
NK067(ju)004:1698: nam mkhas mkha' mnyam rdzogs pa chen por byed ces gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:1699: mdor na bde chen gyi nyams myong 'thug cing rgya che ba dang brtan por 'jug pa'i don te /
NK067(ju)004:1700: de'i stobs kyis stong gzugs kyi snang ba'ang je gsal
NK067(ju)004:1701: dang rgya je cher 'gro zhing brtan par 'gyur ro
NK067(ju)004:1702: // dwangs ma'i gnad skul tshul thun mong ma yin
NK067(ju)004:1703: pa de 'dra 'ong ba la ni dang por bskyed
NK067(ju)004:1704: rim sgom pa'i dus nas cir snang thams cad dkyil
NK067(ju)004:1705: // 'khor dang / de'ang ye shes rang snang zhes
NK067(ju)004:1706: mi shigs pa'i sems las phar mched pa'i cho 'phrul
NK067(ju)004:1708: de'i ched du lta ba'i skabs su de ltar ngo
NK067(ju)004:1709: 'phrod cing thag chod kyi gding rnyed pa zhig srog
NK067(ju)004:1711: skabs 'di'i stong gzugs sgrub tshul dang dus 'khor nas
NK067(ju)004:1712: rlung bcu dbu mar bcings pa'i rtags snang bshad pa
NK067(ju)004:1713: gnyis 'od gsal gyi snang ba tsam du 'dra yang
NK067(ju)004:1714: / 'di ni mi shigs pa'i rlung rang mal du sad pa'i snang ba yin pas mi 'dra ste /
NK067(ju)004:1715: rdzogs chen thod rgal ba'i 'char snang dang 'di gnyis
NK067(ju)004:1716: rig gdangs kyi cha la rtsal 'don byed mi byed
NK067(ju)004:1717: dang / sems 'dzin gyi rtsol ba yod med las phyogs mtshungs so //
NK067(ju)004:1718: de yang snang ba de dag rlung bcu dbu mar
NK067(ju)004:1719: zhugs pa'i rtags su shar ba yin min dpyad par
NK067(ju)004:1720: zad kyi / de dag 'char ba la rlung bcu
NK067(ju)004:1721: dbu mar 'jug mi dgos zhes bshad pa ni min
NK067(ju)004:1722: zad kyi / no // gter chen sku mched sogs kyi rdzogs rim pa'i lha sku mthong ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:1723: thob pa gnyis su bshad pa'i mthong ba tsam dang /
NK067(ju)004:1724: 'od gsal gyi rtogs pa las rung rnyed pa tsam
NK067(ju)004:1725: la kun tu bzang po'i thig le gcig pu bsgoms
NK067(ju)004:1727: lha sku de thob pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1728: rtogs pa'i 'od gsal lam 'thug po'i 'od gsal phul
NK067(ju)004:1729: phyin 'char ba la lte ba'i a thung la dmigs
NK067(ju)004:1730: pa kun tu bzang mo'i man ngag dang /
NK067(ju)004:1731: mgrin pa'i rngams ma la dmigs pa sbyor ba dag pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:1732: spyi bo'i ham yig la dmigs pa khyab brdal chen
NK067(ju)004:1733: po'i man ngag rnams kyang grogs su nges par gces
NK067(ju)004:1734: te / gtum mo'i gnad la dngos su dmigs nas
NK067(ju)004:1735: ji tsam bsgoms pa de tsam du 'bar 'dzags shugs
NK067(ju)004:1736: te / che la / 'bar 'dzags kyis mi shigs
NK067(ju)004:1737: pa tshim stobs che rim bzhin ye shes 'bar ba
NK067(ju)004:1738: te / che la / dang / de'i rang snang
NK067(ju)004:1739: gi lha sku gsal brtan khyad zhugs par 'gyur zhing
NK067(ju)004:1741: btags pa'i gzhi'i srog mkhar gyi sa bon drug po
NK067(ju)004:1743: 'dir rdor bzlas kyi rtsa mdud 'grol ba ma bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)004:1744: lte ba nas spyi bo'i bar gyi dbu ma'i lam
NK067(ju)004:1745: du 'bar 'dzags kyi bde ba cher 'phel te sems
NK067(ju)004:1746: bde bas bsdus pa na rtsa 'dab kyi lug rnams
NK067(ju)004:1748: rlung sems 'jug pa gcig pas so //
NK067(ju)004:1749: de ltar rlung 'drong stobs kyis d+h+au ti'i rtsa mdud
NK067(ju)004:1750: rang zhig tu 'gro bas gnad legs par tshang ngo
NK067(ju)004:1751: // de dag ni steng sgo'i man ngag gi gzhung
NK067(ju)004:1752: rnams khog bsgrigs nas go don cung zad bshad pa
NK067(ju)004:1753: // ste / 'khor lo bzhi'i man ngag sgom pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1754: lag len dngos ni rgyud 'grel phyogs bcu mun sel
NK067(ju)004:1755: // ste / dang / sems nyid ngal gso'i don khrid /
NK067(ju)004:1756: gsang bdag zhal lung sogs su gsal bar bzhugs te /
NK067(ju)004:1757: de dag la'ang mi 'dra ba'i khyad par bag tsam yod pas zhib tu shes par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:1759: rgyud kyi le'u bcu gcig par /
NK067(ju)004:1760: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK067(ju)004:1761: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar phyag rgya mtshan nyid dang ldan pa brtag cing btsal ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:1762: 'gugs shing rnyed nas 'dod pa'i bstan bcos las bshad
NK067(ju)004:1763: pa'i kun spyod kyis rjes chags rtsom pa rnams ni
NK067(ju)004:1764: bsnyen pa dang / yab yum lhar bskyed pa lha'i 'du shes /
NK067(ju)004:1765: mkha' gsang rdo rje dam pad+mara rlob pa sngags kyi 'du shes /
NK067(ju)004:1766: thabs 'di la brten nas lhan skyes kyi ye shes
NK067(ju)004:1767: bsgrub par bya'o snyam pa chos kyi 'du shes te
NK067(ju)004:1768: gsum ldan gyi brda bzhis bsnol mar skul ba sogs
NK067(ju)004:1769: nye bsnyen / phyag rgya bzhis snyoms par zhugs te
NK067(ju)004:1770: rjes chags kyi rlung bskyod pas gtum mo sbar ba'i
NK067(ju)004:1771: 'od kyis zla ba bzhus pa'i yas babs kyi 'gros
NK067(ju)004:1772: kyis 'ongs pa las 'khor lo bzhir dga' bzhi rim
NK067(ju)004:1773: gyis myong ba'i mthar nor bu'i rtser 'dzags med du
NK067(ju)004:1774: bzung bas lhan skyes kyi dga' ba rdzogs par thob
NK067(ju)004:1775: nye bsnyen / sgrub pa / nyi zla rdo rje'i
NK067(ju)004:1776: lces blangs te bzlog pa'i sbyor bas gyen du drangs
NK067(ju)004:1777: te rtsa 'khor gyi gnas so sor dga' ba'i cha
NK067(ju)004:1778: shas rim gyi gang ba'i mthar bde chen 'khor lo'i
NK067(ju)004:1779: ham yig la brtan pa las byung ba'i lhan skyes
NK067(ju)004:1780: mthar phyin pa ni sgrub chen te /
NK067(ju)004:1783: sbyor dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i 'jog tshul gsum gyi nang tshan phyi ma'o //
NK067(ju)004:1784: 'di nyid kyi rgyud phyii ma las ni /
NK067(ju)004:1786: bsnyen pa zhes byar bstan pa yin //
NK067(ju)004:1787: bo la ka ko la sbyor ba //
NK067(ju)004:1788: nye bar bsnyen par brjod pa ste //
NK067(ju)004:1789: rtsa gnyis mngon par 'brel ba ni //
NK067(ju)004:1790: sgrub pa yin par bstan pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:1791: lhan cig skyes gnyis 'brel ba ni //
NK067(ju)004:1792: sgrub ba chen por brjod pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:1793: zhes bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i 'jog tshul khyad par can gzhan gsungs so //
NK067(ju)004:1794: de dag la g.yo ldang la sogs pa'i sems lnga
NK067(ju)004:1795: 'jog tshul yang yod de 'grel pa las shes so
NK067(ju)004:1796: // pho nya'i lam gyi gnad che shos gcig ni /
NK067(ju)004:1798: spangs nas rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsa //
NK067(ju)004:1799: dgug dang bsdam pa ma shes na //
NK067(ju)004:1800: rdo rje'i bskal pa mtha' yas par //
NK067(ju)004:1801: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK067(ju)004:1803: rtsa bcing ba'i gnad nyid yin te phyag rgya brtag pa'i rgyu mtshan yang 'di yin no //
NK067(ju)004:1804: 'grel pa rnams su thabs des rtog tshogs sku dang
NK067(ju)004:1805: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du 'char bar gsungs pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1806: don ni dam pa 'gas rtog pa'i ngos nas tha
NK067(ju)004:1807: dad kyang ye shes kyi ngos nas gcig tu song
NK067(ju)004:1808: ba yin zhes bshad pa ltar rtog tshogs thams cad
NK067(ju)004:1809: bde ba chen po'i ro gcig gis myos te so
NK067(ju)004:1810: sor 'dzin pa'i 'du shes kyi g.ya' dang bral ba
NK067(ju)004:1811: ste / phung khams bde ba'i dkyil 'khor du bsdam pa zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:1812: 'di la sogs pa'i gong 'og du mar ma dag
NK067(ju)004:1813: pa'i phung khams skye mched la rtog tshogs zhes bshad
NK067(ju)004:1814: pa ni rtog pa tha mal snang zhen gyi rnam
NK067(ju)004:1817: 'dis rtog pa zhes pa'i snga ma la bshad kyang rung mod /
NK067(ju)004:1819: gnas dang sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor la sogs pa //
NK067(ju)004:1820: log rtog nyid las gzhan du ci yang med //
NK067(ju)004:1822: ma dag pa'i snang ba thams cad log rtog gi
NK067(ju)004:1823: rnam 'phrul yin pa'i sgo nas bshad na 'thad dam
NK067(ju)004:1824: snyam mo // gong du brjod pa ltar thabs lam
NK067(ju)004:1825: cig char pa la ltos nas kyang dbang gnyis pa
NK067(ju)004:1826: dang gsum pa'i lam go rim nges shing gnyis par
NK067(ju)004:1827: rang lus la brten pa'i thabs kyi gsal bar mtshon
NK067(ju)004:1828: pa'i don de nyid gsum par gzhan lus la brten
NK067(ju)004:1829: nas sgom par zad pas ye shes kyi sku sgrub
NK067(ju)004:1830: tshul sogs snga ma las gzhan du mi bsam mo
NK067(ju)004:1831: snyam mo // // gnyis pa grol lam la'ang /
NK067(ju)004:1832: lam myur bul la ltos nas cig char ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:1833: rim gyis pa'i lam gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:1836: dbang po yang rab kha cig dbyer med chig chod
NK067(ju)004:1837: du rtogs goms mthar phyin par byed pa yod de
NK067(ju)004:1838: cig char ba zhes bya zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1840: de la rim cig char brtsi ba'i gzhi ni mtshan nyid gsum yin la /
NK067(ju)004:1841: mnga' ris pan chen rin po che sogs kyis bzhed pas /
NK067(ju)004:1842: de gsum dus mnyam kho nar rdzogs pa'i cig char ba'ang bzhag chog na'ang /
NK067(ju)004:1843: cig char ba thams cad de ltar ma nges kyi /
NK067(ju)004:1844: rtogs pa shin tu myur ba la cig char ba zhes brjod pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:1845: de ni gang zag yin la /
NK067(ju)004:1846: cig char ba'i lam ni de'i rgyud kyi ting nge 'dzin sogs so //
NK067(ju)004:1847: de'ang 'di'i lam la sbyang ba'i thog mar rtogs pa
NK067(ju)004:1848: bzhi la sogs pa'i gtan tshigs kyi sna rtse re
NK067(ju)004:1849: bkod pa tsam gyis 'od gsal gyi rtogs pa bcos
NK067(ju)004:1851: snang srid thams cad ye shes rang snang ba'i dkyil 'khor nyag gcig tu 'char zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1852: de'i don la mnyam par bzhag pas rkyen thub kyi
NK067(ju)004:1853: rtogs pa 'phel 'grib med par brtan pa 'phral la
NK067(ju)004:1854: thob nas rig 'dzin gyi sa la mig 'phrul bzhin
NK067(ju)004:1856: rtogs pa de ltar myur ba ni rgyud dang dbang
NK067(ju)004:1857: po dang dge rtsa rlabs che ba'i gang zag gi
NK067(ju)004:1858: khyad par 'ga' zhig sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam 'di
NK067(ju)004:1859: la sngon smon lam rlabs po che btab pa la
NK067(ju)004:1860: sogs pa'i rgyu las byung ste /
NK067(ju)004:1861: de yang tshe sngon sgyu d+r+wa'i lam la ma bslab pa yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1862: tshe 'dir lam bgrod tshul dang sgyu 'phrul gyi lam
NK067(ju)004:1863: 'di nyid la ltos te cig char ba yin yang
NK067(ju)004:1864: / tshe snga ma yan chad du 'og ma'i lam la rim gyis sbyangs pa yang mi 'gal lo //
NK067(ju)004:1865: brgyud pa'i bka' srol la de 'dra ba de la sbyang rno cig char ba zhes grags shing /
NK067(ju)004:1866: theg gsum rigs nges ltar sems can gyi rigs dang
NK067(ju)004:1867: dbang po sna tshogs yin pas dbang rno cig char
NK067(ju)004:1868: ba'ang yod ces gsang bdag sgro phug pa chen po
NK067(ju)004:1869: gsung ngo // des rim gyis pa la sbyangs pa
NK067(ju)004:1870: dang rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon gnyis su 'byed tshul
NK067(ju)004:1871: gsung ngo // yang go sla'o // de la mtshan
NK067(ju)004:1872: nyid gsum ni slob dpon chen po'i man ngag lta
NK067(ju)004:1874: de la mtshan nyid gsum gyi don mthar phyin par 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)004:1875: rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi'i tshul rig pa ni shes pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:1876: yang nas yang du goms par byed pa ni 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:1877: goms pa'i mthus mngon du gyur pa ni 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:1878: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK067(ju)004:1879: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin /
NK067(ju)004:1880: mngon du gyur pa'i mtshan nyid 'bras bu ste /
NK067(ju)004:1881: nyams len gyi sbyor ba'i 'jug yul shes par byed pa'am /
NK067(ju)004:1882: bsgom bya'i dbang du mdzad nas lta ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:1883: nyams len gyis sbyor bas 'jug pa'am sgom byed kyi dbang du mdzad nas ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK067(ju)004:1884: bsgom pa'i don mngon du gyur pa'i dbang du mdzad nas 'bras bu bzhag go //
NK067(ju)004:1885: phyi ma 'di la rtogs bya mtha' dag mngon du gyur pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu dang /
NK067(ju)004:1886: ci rigs tsam mngon du gyur pa lam gyur gyi 'bras bu gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:1887: snga ma 'bras rgyud dang gcig la /
NK067(ju)004:1888: lam rgyud skabs kyi mtshan nyid gsum pa ni phyi ma'o //
NK067(ju)004:1889: sems can sangs rgyas kyi khyad sngar bshad pa'i zhen snang dag ma dag yin la /
NK067(ju)004:1890: zhen snang gcod byed kyi gtso bo lta ba yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1891: de nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis yang yang gsos btab
NK067(ju)004:1892: cing bskyed bsring bas rig 'dzin gyi 'bras bu 'grub
NK067(ju)004:1893: pa'i phyir rgyu rkyen 'bras bu gsum du yang bzhag
NK067(ju)004:1894: go // theg chen thun mong gi gzhung du sems bskyed rdzogs byang gi sa bon lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)004:1895: lta ba sogs spyod pa gzhan rnams de'i grogs su gsung kyang /
NK067(ju)004:1896: 'dir dang rnam bzhag tha dad yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:1897: 'dir thun min gyi kun rdzob sems bskyed kyang lta
NK067(ju)004:1898: ba'i phyogs nas 'jog thub pas phyogs 'dzol ba yang
NK067(ju)004:1899: med do // dang po rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid la /
NK067(ju)004:1904: zhen snang ngam snang zhen gyi tshogs pa la bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)004:1905: de'i dgongs pa btsal na log rtog 'khrul pa'i dmigs
NK067(ju)004:1906: yul chos can du byas nas gdod nas rnam dag
NK067(ju)004:1907: gi ngo bor 'jal ba'am gtan la 'bebs pa yin
NK067(ju)004:1908: pas / de 'dra'i chos can dang bsgrub bya'i chos kyi tshogs don de la byed par mngon te /
NK067(ju)004:1910: zhen snang gtan la phab pas chos nyid phebs par
NK067(ju)004:1911: 'gyur te sbrul 'khrul gyi shes pa la dpyad pas
NK067(ju)004:1912: thag khrar rtogs pa bzhin no //
NK067(ju)004:1913: zhes dpe 'jog tshul 'di la legs par brtag na shes nus so //
NK067(ju)004:1916: skabs don rgyu mtshan gyi sgo nas gtan la 'bebs pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:1918: de nyid dngos lnga tshul dang tshig /
NK067(ju)004:1924: sngon byung du ston pa sku lngas 'khor lnga la
NK067(ju)004:1925: gsung lnga'i sgo nas chos nyid kyi don mngon sum
NK067(ju)004:1927: ston pa chos kyi skus 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho la skye med don gyi gsung gis /
NK067(ju)004:1928: longs skus smin pa rgya mtsho la dgongs pa brda'i /
NK067(ju)004:1929: sprul skus mos pa rgya mtsho la brjod pa tshig gi /
NK067(ju)004:1930: rdo rje'i skus dbyer med rdo rje'i 'khor la rdo rje'i /
NK067(ju)004:1931: mngon byang gis rgyal ba rgya mtsho la rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung gis brda sprod pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:1932: 'di la sngon gyi sgyu 'phrul mkhan po rnams sprul
NK067(ju)004:1933: sku ma gtogs pa'i sku bzhi'i 'khor la zhen snang
NK067(ju)004:1934: med pas gsung de dag sngon byung nyid la ltos
NK067(ju)004:1935: na gtan tshigs min yang rjes 'jug rtogs pa'i gtan
NK067(ju)004:1936: tshigs sgrub byed kyi yan lag yin pas gtan tshigs
NK067(ju)004:1937: su btags gsung / gzhan dag sku bzhi'i 'khor la'ang
NK067(ju)004:1938: zhen snang phra ba ci rigs gcad rgyu yod pas
NK067(ju)004:1941: mthar lam na'ang shes sgrib phra mo yod pas phyi ma ltar 'thad gsung /
NK067(ju)004:1943: mthar lam pa rnams longs sku'i lhan cig pa'i 'khor
NK067(ju)004:1944: du song ba nyid kyi chos sku sogs gsum po'i
NK067(ju)004:1946: chos sku dang rjes mthun gyi rtogs pa thob pa la ye shes rgya mtsho'i 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)004:1947: rdo rje dang mngon byang gi sku dang cha 'dra
NK067(ju)004:1948: ba'i rtogs pa thob pa la rdo rje'i 'khor dang
NK067(ju)004:1949: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i 'khor zhes ldog chas phye nas
NK067(ju)004:1950: brjod pa yin nam snyam ste /
NK067(ju)004:1951: slob lam na ye shes chos sku mngon sum du mthong ba med cing /
NK067(ju)004:1952: chos longs sprul gsum tshogs don nyid de gsum ngo
NK067(ju)004:1953: bo dbyer med pa dang ldog pa tha dad pa'i
NK067(ju)004:1954: cha nas rdo rje dang mngon byang gi sku so
NK067(ju)004:1955: sor bzhag pa tsam las med pas ston pa tha
NK067(ju)004:1956: dad du bshad mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:1957: rdo rje'i gsung sogs kyi go don yang /
NK067(ju)004:1958: ston pa sku gsum dbyer med sogs kyi dgongs pa
NK067(ju)004:1959: la mnyam par bzhag pa nyid kyis 'khor rnams rgyud
NK067(ju)004:1960: don gyi rtogs pa mthar phyin pa la brda sprad
NK067(ju)004:1961: pa'i tha snyad sbyar ba ste /
NK067(ju)004:1964: grol lam gyi skabs 'dir rang gzhan gyi lus la
NK067(ju)004:1965: gnad du bsnun pa'i thabs rnams sngon du ma btang
NK067(ju)004:1966: bar gtan tshigs tsam la brten nas rdzogs rim gyi
NK067(ju)004:1967: rtogs pa gsar du 'dren par bzhed de /
NK067(ju)004:1968: de ltar 'dren nus pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK067(ju)004:1969: lam 'di ni gdul bya shes rab ches lhag par
NK067(ju)004:1970: rno ba'i dbang du mdzad pas grol lam shes rab
NK067(ju)004:1971: kyi lam pa zhes bya la /
NK067(ju)004:1972: de 'dra ba des gtan tshigs tsam la brten nas zhen snang gi spros pa gcod nus shing /
NK067(ju)004:1973: de bcad stobs kyis gnyug ma'i bzhugs tshul rjen par mthong nus pa'i gnad kyis yin te /
NK067(ju)004:1974: der ma zad shin tu dbang rnon 'ga' zhig rdo
NK067(ju)004:1975: rje slob dpon gyis dgongs pa gtad pa tsam dang
NK067(ju)004:1977: tshig mgo smos tsam gyis zhen snang bcad de rang
NK067(ju)004:1978: gnas kyi ye shes gsal bar tshon nus pa'ang 'di
NK067(ju)004:1979: ltar yod ces dbang rnon shes rab kyis grol tshul
NK067(ju)004:1980: 'dir bstan 'di la rnam grangs kyi sgo nas nges
NK067(ju)004:1981: pa skyed pa'i dngos tshul tshig gsum gyi dbye ba
NK067(ju)004:1983: bla ma thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung rgyud las kyang /
NK067(ju)004:1984: rtsa rlung thig le'i byed bcing la mi ltos par
NK067(ju)004:1985: gtan tshigs kho nas lam gyi 'od gsal la sbyor
NK067(ju)004:1986: ba ni rgyud 'di'i khyad chos chen po yin pas
NK067(ju)004:1987: 'dir gtan tshigs srog tu bzung dgos zhes gsungs ngo
NK067(ju)004:1988: // de'i phyir sngon byung dngos lnga nas dpyad du
NK067(ju)004:1989: yod pas go ba'i gtan tshigs kyi bar gyi ye
NK067(ju)004:1990: shes mtshon tshul thams cad shes rab kyis grol lugs
NK067(ju)004:1991: su mtshungs pas 'dra ba las btags te dngos lnga
NK067(ju)004:1992: sogs la'ang gtan tshigs zhes brjod do //
NK067(ju)004:1993: de ltar byas na gong du smos pa'i bzhed pa
NK067(ju)004:1994: gnyis po gang la'ang 'thad mi 'thad kyi cha gnyis
NK067(ju)004:1995: re 'byed rgyu yod par rtogs so //
NK067(ju)004:1996: tshul 'di ni grol lam gyi dka' ba'i gnad cig tu snang ngo //
NK067(ju)004:1998: dbang rnon yang rab rnams la snang grags kyi dngos
NK067(ju)004:1999: po thams cad kyis sngon byung sku lnga'i gsung gi
NK067(ju)004:2000: tshul dang mthun par rgyud don ngo sprod pa ste
NK067(ju)004:2005: sprul pa'i sku rnams kyi gsung dang tshul mthun pa'i gtan tshigs rim pa bzhin /
NK067(ju)004:2006: skye med don gyi gtan tshigs skye med mtshon pa nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)004:2007: dgongs pa brda'i gtan tshigs sgrib pa ngos 'dzin pa me long gi gzugs brnyan lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)004:2008: rang rig mngon gsal gyi gtan tshigs rtogs med rang gsal nyi ma'i snying po lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)004:2009: dbyer med rdo rje'i gtan tshigs grags stong dbyer med brag cha lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)004:2010: brjod pa tshig gi gtan tshigs kun yid 'jug pa tshangs dbyangs lta bu'o //
NK067(ju)004:2011: 'di ni rgyal ba gong ma rnams snang ba thams
NK067(ju)004:2012: cad bla ma dang dpe char shar ba zhes gsungs
NK067(ju)004:2014: de'ang yul snang gi brda la brten nas skye med
NK067(ju)004:2015: kyi rtogs pa shar na chos sku'i gsung gi tshul
NK067(ju)004:2017: brda des rang rgyud kyi sgrib pa ngos zin pa na longs sku'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:2018: gsal mdangs 'gag med kyi rig pa ngos zin pa na mngon byang gi dang /
NK067(ju)004:2019: snang dus nyid nas stong pa'i ngo bor shes pa na rdo rje'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:2020: rgyal ba'i tshangs dbyangs gcig nyid gdul bya'i dbang gis
NK067(ju)004:2021: skad rigs dang tshig don sna tshogs su 'char ba
NK067(ju)004:2022: ltar dngos po gcig nyid gsang sngags kyi dgongs pa
NK067(ju)004:2023: sna tshogs shes pa'i sgor mthong ba na sprul sku'i
NK067(ju)004:2024: gsung gi tshul du song ba yin no //
NK067(ju)004:2026: tshul lnga po de dag tshig tu brjod pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:2027: skye med rang snang du ston pa'i tshig rnams chos sku'i tshig dang /
NK067(ju)004:2028: ldem dgongs brda'i tshig rnams longs sku'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:2029: dbyer med rdo rje lta bur ston pa'i tshig rnams rdo rje'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:2030: ye shes rang snang du ston pa'i tshig dang yi ge rnams mngon byang gi dang /
NK067(ju)004:2031: dkri drang brgyud pa'i tshig rnams sprul sku'i tshig go //
NK067(ju)004:2032: de rnams bsdu na lam rim las /
NK067(ju)004:2033: de lta mod kyi bsdu na gnyis //
NK067(ju)004:2034: bzhi rjes mi dpyod gcig rjes dpyod //
NK067(ju)004:2036: dpyad du med pas go ba sku bzhi'i gtan tshigs
NK067(ju)004:2037: zhes gdul bya dbang rnon dpyad pa'i ngal ba la
NK067(ju)004:2038: cher mi ltos par rgyud don go ba'i dbang du
NK067(ju)004:2039: byas pa dang / dpyad du yod pas go ba
NK067(ju)004:2040: sprul sku'i gtan tshigs zhes dbang rtul dpyad pa gtso
NK067(ju)004:2041: bor byas pa la brten nas rgyud don go ba'i
NK067(ju)004:2042: dbang du byas pa gnyis so //
NK067(ju)004:2043: 'di las dpags na tshig lnga'i nang gi skye med
NK067(ju)004:2044: rang snang du ston pa'i tshig la rnam par spros
NK067(ju)004:2046: chos thams cad skye ba med pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:2047: zhes pa lta bu'i ngag gis don bcar phog tu ston pa zhig dgos sam snyam la /
NK067(ju)004:2048: sku gzhan gsum gyi gtan tshigs la'ang rig pa de bsgre bar bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:2049: de ltar na dbang rnon mchog gis rgyud don go
NK067(ju)004:2050: ba gtan tshigs rgyas par bstan pa la mi ltos
NK067(ju)004:2051: mod / 'on kyang de dag rgyu mtshan med bzhin
NK067(ju)004:2052: du rgyud don rtogs pa min pas gtan tshigs kyi
NK067(ju)004:2053: don thub dgos par nges shing /
NK067(ju)004:2054: gtan tshigs bstan dgos pa'i yul gyi gtso bo yang
NK067(ju)004:2055: gong ma la ltos te dbang rtul zhes brjod kyang
NK067(ju)004:2056: spyir shin tu dbang rnon yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2057: rgyud 'di'i ched du bya ba'i gtso bo'i gdul bya yin pa'i phyir te /
NK067(ju)004:2058: rgyud sde thams cad kyi rtse mor gyur pa'i rgyud
NK067(ju)004:2059: 'di dbang rtul la dgongs te gsungs pa'i rgyud yin
NK067(ju)004:2060: zhes smra mi rigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:2061: sprul sku'i gtan tshigs de la gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:2063: mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK067(ju)004:2065: bsgrub bya'i don dang gtan tshigs gnyis sgra mi 'gal bar sbyar nas gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:2066: sgra mi 'gal ba zhes pa'i tshig thung 'di sbyar dgos par sems te /
NK067(ju)004:2067: 'gal ba'i gtan tshigs mtshan nyid pa yin min la
NK067(ju)004:2068: byed na tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs bzhag
NK067(ju)004:2072: sgra mthun don spags kyi gtan tshigs so //
NK067(ju)004:2074: rgyud gzhung gis dngos bstan ltar 'chad pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:2078: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs dang bzhi /
NK067(ju)004:2080: rgyud kyi le'u bcu gcig par /
NK067(ju)004:2081: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK067(ju)004:2082: byin gyis brlabsa dang mngon sum pa //
NK067(ju)004:2083: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK067(ju)004:2084: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK067(ju)004:2086: de la tha mal pa'i gnas dang longs spyod la sogs pa snang ba sna tshogs dang /
NK067(ju)004:2087: de rnams la bzang ngan dang spang blang sogs su
NK067(ju)004:2088: zhen tshul sna tshogs can gyi sems ni kun nyon
NK067(ju)004:2090: de dag brgal ba'i pha rol ye shes kyi snang
NK067(ju)004:2091: ba rnams ni rnam byang myang 'das kyi phyogs te
NK067(ju)004:2092: / de dag gang yang sems kyi gnyug ma'i gnas lugs kyi khams sam dbyings la ma grub ste /
NK067(ju)004:2093: dbyings de gcig pu de dag thams cad kyi rgyu'am snang gzhi yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2094: dbyings de'i ngos nas 'khor ba'i snang sems grub na
NK067(ju)004:2095: dbyings 'khor ba'i phyogs su chad pas snang sems de
NK067(ju)004:2096: dag sbyang du mi rung la /
NK067(ju)004:2097: rnam byang gi snang ba de'i ngos nas grub na
NK067(ju)004:2098: dbyings de rnam byang gi phyogs su lhung bas 'khor
NK067(ju)004:2099: ba'i snang gzhir mi rung ngo //
NK067(ju)004:2100: snang sems rang rgyud pa'am rang dbang bar grub na
NK067(ju)004:2101: snang gzhi mthar thug gi khams la med pa mi
NK067(ju)004:2102: 'thad pas / grub tshul de khegs dgos te /
NK067(ju)004:2103: de'i phyir spyan 'grel las mtha' bzhi'i skye 'gog dang
NK067(ju)004:2104: gcig du bral gyi rig pa rgyas par bshad do
NK067(ju)004:2105: // de ltar na dbyings kyi bzhugs tshul mthar thug
NK067(ju)004:2106: la gnyis snang gi spros pa phra rab tsam yang
NK067(ju)004:2108: 'di yang ma yin dgag gi stong nyid las brtsams te dpyad pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:2109: tshul de ltar rtogs pa ni rgyu gcig par rtogs pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:2110: mdor bsdus nas sbyor ba 'god tshe /
NK067(ju)004:2114: mtshan nyid blo bral bzhi bsgrub byar bzung nas rgyu
NK067(ju)004:2115: gcig pa sogs bzhi po gtan tshigs su 'god par
NK067(ju)004:2117: 'khor 'das kyi snang ba gnyis chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2118: dbyings kyi rang bzhin la skye ba med de /
NK067(ju)004:2119: khyod gnyis ka'i snang gzhi mthar thug dbyings gcig po de las med pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2121: gsang bdag dgongs rgyan du bkod tshul ni der shes par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:2122: de ltar snang cha dbyings kyi ngos nas ma grub kyang /
NK067(ju)004:2123: dbyings la ye shes 'bral mi srid cing /
NK067(ju)004:2124: ye shes la snang cha lhun grub tu yod de /
NK067(ju)004:2125: thag khra med na sbrul du 'khrul ba'i gzhi med
NK067(ju)004:2126: pa bzhin sems kyi gnyug ma'i gnas tshul la snang
NK067(ju)004:2127: ba gtan med na 'khrul snang gtan med pas khyab
NK067(ju)004:2128: ces sgyu 'phrul la mkhas pa rnams gsungs te rdo
NK067(ju)004:2129: rje'i tshig go // de'ang gong smos ltar rtsa ba'i
NK067(ju)004:2130: dbyings gang du yang phyogs lhung med pa'i gnad kyis
NK067(ju)004:2131: ris med kyi snang ba sgyu ma lta bur rang
NK067(ju)004:2132: rje'i tshig go // shar te / ris med kyi don ni /
NK067(ju)004:2133: bye brag mtha' yas pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2134: chu lta bu'i dngos po gcig kyang las dang rig
NK067(ju)004:2135: sngags dang bsam gtan la sogs pa'i rkyen las cir
NK067(ju)004:2137: mdor na phyogs rer ma chad pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:2138: rgyud 'dir dngos po thams cad ming tsam du zad par yang yang gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:2139: snang ba ris med kyi rgyu mtshan dpyis phyin pa yin la /
NK067(ju)004:2140: de yang dbyings la snang ba ma grub pa'i rgyu mtshan der thug go //
NK067(ju)004:2141: ye shes kyi snang ba la phyogs ris med kyang sems kyis phyogs ris su zhen par ma zad /
NK067(ju)004:2142: rdzogs rim pas stong gzugs mthong tshe ris med kun
NK067(ju)004:2143: khyab kyi 'char tshul rtsal ma rdzogs pa'ang rtog sgrib
NK067(ju)004:2144: glo bur ba de'i shan zhugs pa yin gyi /
NK067(ju)004:2145: snang ba rang gi gnyug ma'i 'dug tshul mthar thug gi cha ma yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2146: glo bur bas bslad pa med na rdo rje sems
NK067(ju)004:2147: dpa'i ye shes las mi gzhan pa'i rang snang bkod
NK067(ju)004:2148: pa'i 'khor lo rnam pa thams cad pa /
NK067(ju)004:2149: chos kyi dbyings ltar tshad yongs su ma chad pa kho na'o //
NK067(ju)004:2150: de 'dra ba de la dag pa rab 'byams kyi snang ba zhes bya zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2151: de nyid yongs su dag pa'i lha'i ngo bo nyid kyang yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2152: dag pa'i rten dang brten pa thams cad de bzhin
NK067(ju)004:2153: gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid yin par yongs su grags
NK067(ju)004:2154: so // 'di la yig 'bru'i tshul dang snang ba lhar sgrub pa zhes bya ste /
NK067(ju)004:2157: sems nyid skye med kyi gdangs chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2158: rol pa 'gags med lha'i sku gsung thugs su rang snang ba yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2159: mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid mtshon byed
NK067(ju)004:2160: yi ge du mar ma 'gags par snang bas mtshon
NK067(ju)004:2163: dbyings la spros pa med pa ni a yig la yi ge mang po med pa dang 'dra /
NK067(ju)004:2164: 'on kyang snang ba sna tshogs dbyings de'i cho 'phrul
NK067(ju)004:2165: du shar ba ni a de gnas lnga'i byed rtsol
NK067(ju)004:2166: tha dad kyis bsgyur bas dbyangs gsal gyi tshogs 'byung
NK067(ju)004:2167: ba dang 'dra / rang bzhin dag pa'i dbyings de
NK067(ju)004:2168: las shar ba la mthar gtugs na dag pa'i lha
NK067(ju)004:2169: las gzhan med pa ni dbyangs gsal gyi yi ge
NK067(ju)004:2170: la a'i gdangs kyis ma khyab pa med pa dang
NK067(ju)004:2171: ba dang 'dra / 'dra'o // grol lam cig char ba'i thad na rgya mtsho las /
NK067(ju)004:2172: sku gsung thugs su snang ba yis //
NK067(ju)004:2173: ma lus gsung gi rgyan du rtogs //
NK067(ju)004:2174: zhes pa ltar lhag pa'i bden gnyis dbyer med yi
NK067(ju)004:2175: ge a u ma gsum mo yig la gcig tu
NK067(ju)004:2176: 'dus pas mtshon nas rtogs par byed pa la yig
NK067(ju)004:2177: 'bru'i tshul du gsungs pa'ang yod do //
NK067(ju)004:2178: dper na ras dkar po btsod kyis kha bsgyur na
NK067(ju)004:2179: dmar po yin pa ltar gang dang ji ltar snang
NK067(ju)004:2180: ba'i chos thams cad rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i
NK067(ju)004:2181: tshul gyi phyogs nas bltas na lhag pa'i bden gnyis
NK067(ju)004:2182: dbyer med kyi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor nyag gcig tu
NK067(ju)004:2183: 'char bas snang spyod thams cad tshul de gnyis kyis
NK067(ju)004:2184: sangs rgyas su byin gyis brlabsa pa zhes bshad na
NK067(ju)004:2186: skabs 'di'i byin gyis brlabsa pa'i gtan tshigs la'ang sbyar rung bar mngon no //
NK067(ju)004:2188: lhag pa'i bden gnyis chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2189: ngo bo dbyer med yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2190: khyod gnyis rang bzhin dang rol par gtan la phab
NK067(ju)004:2191: pa'i byin rlabs sam shugs las de ltar thon pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2192: phyir / zhes bkod na go bade'am snyam mo //
NK067(ju)004:2194: 'di ltar snang ba'i dngos po chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2195: lhag pa'i bden gnyis dbyer med dam zung 'jug gi
NK067(ju)004:2196: rang bzhin du ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te
NK067(ju)004:2197: / rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul du rtogs
NK067(ju)004:2198: pa gnyis kyi stobs sam byin rlabs las de ltar
NK067(ju)004:2199: / mthong ba'i phyir / zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:2200: de ltar chos thams cad bden pa dbyer med du
NK067(ju)004:2201: sangs rgyas pa de shes pa gang gis gsal bar
NK067(ju)004:2202: 'grub ce na / de ni sgrin po'i blo can
NK067(ju)004:2203: rnams kyis ring du brtag kyang lha mi'i spyod yul
NK067(ju)004:2204: tha dad ltar sems kyi spyod yul ma yin pas
NK067(ju)004:2205: mngon sum du blta bar mi nus kyi /
NK067(ju)004:2206: sems las 'das pa'i ye shes rang gsal g.yo med
NK067(ju)004:2207: kyi dgongs pa shar ba na gdod gzhon nu ma'i
NK067(ju)004:2208: bde ba ltar nyams su myong bzhin brjod mi shes
NK067(ju)004:2209: shing / yid ches yod kyang phyogs 'dzin dang ma
NK067(ju)004:2210: 'dres pa'i tshul du rang nyid kyis mthong bar 'gyur
NK067(ju)004:2212: bden pa dbyer med chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2213: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2214: rang rig mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2216: mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK067(ju)004:2217: dbyings dang ye shes dang sems zhes smos pa rnams su sngar bshad pa rnams dran par bya'i /
NK067(ju)004:2218: gzhung spyi skad dang bsre bar mi bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:2221: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK067(ju)004:2223: 'di la snang ba phyi nang gi chos rnams chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2224: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2225: dag pa gsum dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK067(ju)004:2227: snod bcud rgyud gsum chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2228: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2229: rim bzhin de bzhin gshegs pa yum lnga dang yab lnga dang ye shes lngar dag pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2231: de'ang da lta phyi nang gi dngos po'i bye brag
NK067(ju)004:2232: ji snyed pa de snyed du tha mal pa'i snang
NK067(ju)004:2233: zhen rgyas shing / de ji ltar rgyas pa ltar
NK067(ju)004:2234: dag pa'i gnas tshul las gol bar 'gyur ba bzhin
NK067(ju)004:2235: zhen rgyas shing / du / dmigs pa de dag
NK067(ju)004:2236: thams cad gdod nas rnam dag gi ngo bor shes
NK067(ju)004:2237: pa'i lta ba ci tsam rtsal sbyangs ba de tsam
NK067(ju)004:2238: du log pa'i zhen snang gcod tshabs che la /
NK067(ju)004:2239: zhen snang gi dmigs pa mtha' yas kyang 'dir snod bcud rgyud gsum du bsdus nas bstan te /
NK067(ju)004:2240: phung po gcig la mtshon na /
NK067(ju)004:2241: gzugs phung tsam yang tshor ba sogs phung po thams
NK067(ju)004:2242: cad kyi bdag nyid du gnas pa ro mnyam rdo
NK067(ju)004:2244: de'i cha shas res kyang brtan g.yo mtha' dag khyab
NK067(ju)004:2245: pa rtag khyab chen po'i gzugs phung ni dag pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2246: gzugs phung gi don yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2247: don de dag kyang rang snang ris med ces pa'i don mthar thug yin la /
NK067(ju)004:2248: sems can gyi gzugs phung yang rang snang ris med du gdod nas dag par bshad zin te /
NK067(ju)004:2249: tshul de lta bus snod kyi 'jig rten sogs gsum
NK067(ju)004:2250: po rnam par dag pa ni dag pa rnam pa
NK067(ju)004:2254: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK067(ju)004:2256: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad chos can //
NK067(ju)004:2257: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2258: mnyam pa bzhis mnyam par gnas pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2260: phyi nang gi dngos po rnams sems la dag ma
NK067(ju)004:2261: dag tu snang ba'i tshul gnyis su byung ba la
NK067(ju)004:2262: bzang ngan dang blang dor du bden par blta zhing
NK067(ju)004:2264: chos de rnams kyi gnas lugs la rnam grangs yin
NK067(ju)004:2265: min gyi don dam gnyis yod kyang yul can gyi
NK067(ju)004:2266: khyad par la ltos nas phye ba ma gtogs skye
NK067(ju)004:2267: med mtha' bral du mnyam zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2268: yang log gi kun rdzob gnyis po gang gi dbang
NK067(ju)004:2269: du byas kyang bden stong sgyu ma lta bur mnyam
NK067(ju)004:2270: ste / de gnyis ni mdo sngags thun mong gi srid zhi mnyam nyid 'jog lugs so //
NK067(ju)004:2271: 'di dag 'og ma kha drang ba'i ched tsam min gyi /
NK067(ju)004:2272: lam 'di'i rnal 'byor pas tshul de dag gis kyang
NK067(ju)004:2273: 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du blta dgos pa yin te
NK067(ju)004:2274: / 'di gnyis la thun mong gi mnyam pa zhes grags pas shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:2275: stong nyid med dgag dang ma yin dgag gi rnam
NK067(ju)004:2276: gzhag ci tsam byas kyang glo bur pa'i sems kyis
NK067(ju)004:2277: sgro btags pa'i dgag sgrub kyi tshul la brten nas
NK067(ju)004:2279: sems las 'das pa'i lhag pa don dam gyi ngos
NK067(ju)004:2280: nas bltas na ni dgag pa gnyis ka'i tha snyad
NK067(ju)004:2282: de bzhin du da lta rags pa'i sems kyis ma
NK067(ju)004:2283: dag pa'i snang zhen bkag nas bsgoms pas dag par
NK067(ju)004:2284: shar yang de 'dra'i dag ma dag gnyis la glo
NK067(ju)004:2285: bur ba'i sems kyi snang ba yin min khyad med
NK067(ju)004:2286: cing / dag par snang ba de ma dag pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2287: dngos po'i gnas tshul du sgrub mi nus pas nyi
NK067(ju)004:2289: lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa dngos kyi steng
NK067(ju)004:2290: nas gzhal na ni gser gling du sa rdo phal
NK067(ju)004:2291: pa mi rnyed pa ltar spang len med par de
NK067(ju)004:2292: 'dra'i las snang dang bcos ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK067(ju)004:2293: snang ba thams cad ye shes rang snang gi 'khor
NK067(ju)004:2294: lo 'ba' zhig tu mnyam ste lhag pa'i mnyam pa
NK067(ju)004:2295: gnyis so // rang byung ye shes 'khor lo tha
NK067(ju)004:2296: ma nas bsnan par 'chad tshe lhag pa'i mnyam pa'am
NK067(ju)004:2297: thun mongs ma yin pa'i mnyam pa zhes 'dod rung
NK067(ju)004:2298: mi rung dpyad rgyu che yang /
NK067(ju)004:2299: de ltar bstan pa'i mdo rnams dmigs bsal du byas nas /
NK067(ju)004:2300: mdo phyogs spyi btang la ltos te thun min du 'jog pa'am /
NK067(ju)004:2301: yang na bde gshegs snying po don dam dkor bdun gyi ldog pa nas bstan pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2302: de la brten nas snang srid dag mnyam du blta
NK067(ju)004:2303: ba mdo sde'i phyogs la med pas de'i cha nas
NK067(ju)004:2304: thun min du bzhag ces bya ste /
NK067(ju)004:2305: phyi ma drag par sems so //
NK067(ju)004:2306: le'u bcu gcig pa'i dgongs rgyan sogs dang bstun nas gong ltar bshad kyi /
NK067(ju)004:2307: go bde ba ni chos thams cad don dam par ma skyes pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2308: kun rdzob tu sgyu mar mnyam pa gnyis thun mong ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:2309: don dam par dkor bdun du dang /
NK067(ju)004:2310: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes su mnyam pa gnyis lhag pa zhes gzhan nas 'byung ba ltar ro //
NK067(ju)004:2312: lam rnam bkod dang bstun na le'u dgu pa'i /
NK067(ju)004:2313: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK067(ju)004:2314: zhes pa drang rung ba 'dra yang dpyad dgos //
NK067(ju)004:2317: snang lugs du mar snang yang yin lugs la de ltar ma grub ste /
NK067(ju)004:2318: sems nyid skye med rang byung gi ye shes gcig gi bdag nyid du ye nas gnas pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2320: 'di pha mes kyi lo chus bsnyan pas rigs brgyud gang yin shes pa'i dpes mtshon par gsungs pas /
NK067(ju)004:2321: mdor na chos thams cad sems nyid 'od gsal gyi gdung rigs su bstan pa yin no //
NK067(ju)004:2322: de'ang dag mnyam gyi lta ba'i gnad spyir gtan la 'bebs pa rtogs pas bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:2323: dag tshul bye brag tu phye nas ston pa dag pa gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:2324: mnyam tshul bye brag tu phye ba mnyam pa bzhi /
NK067(ju)004:2325: dag mnyam gyi gnad thams cad mthar thug rang byung
NK067(ju)004:2326: ye shes su la zlo ba bdag nyid chen po
NK067(ju)004:2327: zhes bshad na nyang t+aika pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2328: smin lo chen po dgongs par yang 'grigs so //
NK067(ju)004:2329: gnyis pa sgra mthun don spags la /
NK067(ju)004:2333: mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs dang bzhi /
NK067(ju)004:2335: nyon mongs dug lnga chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2336: spang byar yang dag par ma grub ste /
NK067(ju)004:2337: rang spyi'i mtshan nyid gnyis char du ngo bo nyid kyis stong pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2339: dug lnga la rang spyi'i mtshan nyid gnyis 'jog pa 'og ma dang mthun yang /
NK067(ju)004:2342: de dag spyi'i mtshan nyid sems rab tu ma zhi ba'i rnam pa /
NK067(ju)004:2344: gti mug kun tu rmongs pa /
NK067(ju)004:2345: zhe sdang kun nas mnar sems pa /
NK067(ju)004:2348: phrag dog gzhan gyi phun tshogs mi bzod pa'i rnam pa yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2349: 'dir nyon mongs spyi'i mtshan nyid rig pa spros bral dang /
NK067(ju)004:2350: so so'i mtshan nyid rig pa sgyub ma'i rtsal tha
NK067(ju)004:2351: dad du snang bar 'dod pas 'phags zhes gsungs te
NK067(ju)004:2352: / phyi ma'i mtshan nyid ni don ldog la mi byed kyi /
NK067(ju)004:2353: rang bzhin nam de nyid la bya zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2354: nyon mongs pa'i de nyid rig pa ye shes yin
NK067(ju)004:2355: lugs la sngar gzhi rgyud kyi skabs su bshad pa
NK067(ju)004:2356: dran par bya'o // bshad tshul snga ma yang 'dir
NK067(ju)004:2357: mi bzhed pa min yang nyon mongs lam byed kyi
NK067(ju)004:2358: skabs don gtso bo phyi ma yin la /
NK067(ju)004:2359: de 'og ma dang ma mthun pa'i 'phags chos yin no //
NK067(ju)004:2361: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs chos can /
NK067(ju)004:2362: khyod la mtha'i spros pa ci yang ma grub ste /
NK067(ju)004:2363: yang dag par gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2365: thun mong du stong nyid la yod med rtag chad
NK067(ju)004:2366: sogs kyi mtha' gang yang med pa dang sgra mthun
NK067(ju)004:2367: yang / 'dir sems dang ye shes phye nas mtha'i
NK067(ju)004:2368: rtog pa gang yang ye shes kyi dbyings la mi
NK067(ju)004:2369: rgyu bar ston pas spags so //
NK067(ju)004:2373: dbyibs dang kha dog sogs chos du ma dang ldan pas brtags na dben pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2376: 'byung chen rags par snang ba rnams snang ba ltar
NK067(ju)004:2377: bden par grub pa cha shas phye na mi rnyed
NK067(ju)004:2378: pa'i rig pas 'gog pa dang sgra mthun yang /
NK067(ju)004:2379: 'dir rgyu mtshan des chos de dag m+aum gyi de
NK067(ju)004:2380: nyid 'od gsal gyi dbyings su bstim par byed pas
NK067(ju)004:2383: ngo bo nyid cir yang ma grub ste /
NK067(ju)004:2384: gzung du med pa'i phyir te /
NK067(ju)004:2386: zhes pa lta bur gzhung spyi'i dpe don sbyor tshul dang sgra mthun yang /
NK067(ju)004:2387: 'dir nam mkha'i brda thabs kyis chos nyid mtshon pa
NK067(ju)004:2388: tsam las rtags kyi tshul gsum sgrub pa'i ched ma
NK067(ju)004:2389: yin pas spags zhes zer ram dpyad rgyu cung zad
NK067(ju)004:2390: snang ngo // gnyis pa tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)004:2391: sems can tha mal pa la dngos su snang ba'i
NK067(ju)004:2392: dngos po 'di dag nyid lhag pa'i bden gnyis dbyer
NK067(ju)004:2393: med du gdod nas sangs rgyas kyang de ltar mi
NK067(ju)004:2395: lhag pa'i bden gnyis kyi gnad gsang mthar gtug na
NK067(ju)004:2396: sems nyid kyi dbyings ci yang ma yin pa ste
NK067(ju)004:2397: cir yang ma grub pa la thug cing /
NK067(ju)004:2398: snang ba'i dngos po ni sna tshogs cir yang 'char
NK067(ju)004:2399: ba mig 'phrul gyi grong khyer lta bur yod pas
NK067(ju)004:2400: des mgo rmongs nas dbyings kyi bzhugs tshul las phyin
NK067(ju)004:2401: ci log tu 'khrul pa yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2402: lta ba ngo sprod tshe snang phyogs cing yar 'char
NK067(ju)004:2403: ba nyid dbyings ci yang ma yin pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK067(ju)004:2404: du bkod pa rmad du byung ba'i thabs mkhas kyis
NK067(ju)004:2405: du ma dang ro gcig phyogs rer zhen pa'i mdud
NK067(ju)004:2406: pa 'grol ba la yin min gyi phyogs 'dzin gzhig
NK067(ju)004:2407: pa zhes lam rnam bkod las gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:2408: de lta bu'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)004:2410: yang dag par ci yang ma yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2411: snang tshul du ma 'gags par rang snang bas ci yang yin pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)004:2413: ji ltar brtags shing bsam pa ltar 'gyur bas na
NK067(ju)004:2414: chos kun gyi ngo bor chos nyid rang snang ba'i
NK067(ju)004:2416: sgra mthun don spags dang tshig don mi mthun pa'i mthun mi mthun brtsi ba'i gzhi mi gcig ste /
NK067(ju)004:2417: snga ma ni theg pa 'og ma'i bshad tshul dang sgra mthun pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2418: phyi ma rtags chos gnyis kyi tshig don mi mthun pa la bzhag pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:2419: phyi ma 'di'i mi mthun pa'i mtshams ni ci yang ma yin pa dang yin pa gnyis tsam mo //
NK067(ju)004:2420: de'ang rtogs pa bzhi sogs rgyud gzhung gi dngos bstan
NK067(ju)004:2421: bzhi po'i khongs su lta ba ngo sprod tshul gtan
NK067(ju)004:2422: la phab ba des theg pa 'og ma'i gsung rab
NK067(ju)004:2423: rnams su rang spyi dang mtha' bral gyi tha snyad
NK067(ju)004:2424: sogs gsungs pa'i mthar thug gi dgongs gzhi sbas te
NK067(ju)004:2425: ma bstan pa rnams gsal bar bkrol nas sde snod
NK067(ju)004:2426: gzhan rnams 'dir gzhol bar ston pa la sgra mthun
NK067(ju)004:2427: don spags dang / yang bzhi po der mi mkhas
NK067(ju)004:2428: pa la ches 'gal ba ltar snang ba'am phan tshun
NK067(ju)004:2429: grogs su khyer nas gol sgrib kyi g.yang sar mi
NK067(ju)004:2430: 'chug pa'i gnad kyi gzer bu ngo mtshar can yod
NK067(ju)004:2431: pa zur du phyung ste ngo sprod pa la mi
NK067(ju)004:2432: mthun pa'i gtan tshigs byung bar bdag cag smra'o //
NK067(ju)004:2434: de ltar gtan la phab pa las cir 'gyur zhe na /
NK067(ju)004:2435: shes pa'i mtshan nyid kyi lta ba dngos rnyed par 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)004:2436: de'i ngo bo ni lam rim las /
NK067(ju)004:2437: rgya mtsho dwangs pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK067(ju)004:2438: sgra rten yid la byed min par //
NK067(ju)004:2439: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral ba //
NK067(ju)004:2440: rang gsal gsum bral mi bsgul bar //
NK067(ju)004:2441: nges par gdengs su gang byas pa //
NK067(ju)004:2442: thos bsam brtan pa'i lta mthar phyin //
NK067(ju)004:2444: gnas lugs lhag pa'i bden gnyis dbyer med rang rig
NK067(ju)004:2445: mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal du rjen par
NK067(ju)004:2446: rtogs pa ste / mngon sum 'di dang rtogs pa bzhi'i skabs kyi mngon sum pa don 'dra'o //
NK067(ju)004:2447: gsal bar bshad na 'od gsal gyi rtogs pa dngos
NK067(ju)004:2448: su rnyed nas de'i char gyur ba'i shes rab skyes
NK067(ju)004:2450: lhun grub ye shes sgron ma nyid //
NK067(ju)004:2451: rang bzhin gsal ba spyan gyi mchog /
NK067(ju)004:2453: 'di la rang rig mngon sum zhes bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)004:2454: rang gnas kyi ye shes go yul du ma lus
NK067(ju)004:2455: par mngon sum du rtogs pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis yin
NK067(ju)004:2456: la / lam gyi 'od gsal mngon sum du shar
NK067(ju)004:2457: na chos nyid kyi dbyings mngon sum du mthong bas
NK067(ju)004:2458: la / ma khyab pas / rje sgrol g.yung rnam
NK067(ju)004:2459: gnyis 'dir chos nyid don spyi'i sgo nas mthong bar
NK067(ju)004:2460: bzhed pa dang yang mi 'gal te /
NK067(ju)004:2461: ji srid gnyis snang phra mos kyang bar ma chod
NK067(ju)004:2462: pa'i tshul gyis 'od gsal gyi dbyings la 'jug mi
NK067(ju)004:2463: nus pa de srid du chos nyid rjen par mthong
NK067(ju)004:2465: des mthong tshod tsam de rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2466: dbyings mtshan nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'ang ma yin no
NK067(ju)004:2467: // 'dir 'od gsal rjen par rtogs pa'i grol lam
NK067(ju)004:2468: rim gyis pa yod na slar stong pa chen po'i
NK067(ju)004:2469: rnal 'byor la nyams lnga mthar chags kyi sgo nas
NK067(ju)004:2470: 'jug dgos pa mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK067(ju)004:2472: 'od gsal sprin sbubs kyi nyi ma lta bu yud
NK067(ju)004:2473: tsam rer rtogs kyang da dung rnam rtog gi gzhan
NK067(ju)004:2474: dbang can yin pas brtan pa rim gyis 'thob dgos
NK067(ju)004:2475: pa'i phyir te / kun mkhyen chen pos /
NK067(ju)004:2476: rang ngo 'phrod kyang goms 'dris ma byas na //
NK067(ju)004:2477: rnam rtog dgras 'khyer g.yul ngo'i bu chung 'dra //
NK067(ju)004:2479: 'od gsal kyi dgongs pa dngos la ma reg kyang
NK067(ju)004:2480: lhag pa'i bden gnyis la bsam byung gi nges pa
NK067(ju)004:2481: rnyed na shes pa'i mtshan nyid phal pa tsam du
NK067(ju)004:2482: 'dod dgos so // shes pa'i mtshan nyid bshad zin to //
NK067(ju)004:2483: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud la gsum du 'byed skabs /
NK067(ju)004:2484: gsang 'dus sogs pha rgyud rnams su gsal stong rlung gi rdzogs rim dang /
NK067(ju)004:2485: bde mchog sogs ma rgyud du bde stong thig le'i rdzogs rim dang /
NK067(ju)004:2486: gsang snying sogs gnyis med rgyud las 'od gsal ye
NK067(ju)004:2487: shes chen po'i rdzogs rim gtso bor ston zhes 'byung
NK067(ju)004:2488: ba'i rdzogs rim phyi ma yang grol lam la byed
NK067(ju)004:2489: par mngon zhing / sngar bshad pa ltar thabs lam
NK067(ju)004:2490: du rdzogs rim gyis ye shes skyes nas 'phel gsung
NK067(ju)004:2491: thams cad shas cher rtsa rlung thig le'i rnal 'byor
NK067(ju)004:2492: gyis byed pa'i dod phal cher lam 'dir lta ba
NK067(ju)004:2493: lam byed kyi steng nas 'gro bar snang ba dang
NK067(ju)004:2494: thabs lam la'ang med du mi rung bas rgyas par
NK067(ju)004:2495: par mngon zhing / bshad do // gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid la /
NK067(ju)004:2497: srid pa rim par smin tshul gyis //
NK067(ju)004:2498: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bzhag /
NK067(ju)004:2499: gang dag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK067(ju)004:2500: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK067(ju)004:2501: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK067(ju)004:2502: skyes pa'i rim gsum gnyis med don //
NK067(ju)004:2504: tha mal pa'i skye 'chi bar do gsum gyi snang
NK067(ju)004:2505: zhen sbyangs nas 'chi ba'i 'od gsal chos skur lam
NK067(ju)004:2506: du 'khyer ba don dam stong pa chen po'i rnal
NK067(ju)004:2507: 'byor / bar do'i rlung sems longs skur 'khyer ba kun rdzob snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor /
NK067(ju)004:2508: skye srid rags pa 'khor bcas sprul skur sbyong byed
NK067(ju)004:2509: kyi rnal 'byor rim pa gsum ste ting nge 'dzin
NK067(ju)004:2510: lnga'o // phyi ma'i rim pa gsum ni dri za
NK067(ju)004:2511: mngal du zhugs pa nas phyir btsas ba'i bar dang
NK067(ju)004:2512: mthun pa phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2513: btsas nas bu tsha 'khor 'dabs rgyas pa'i bar dang mthun pa phyag rgya spros bcas /
NK067(ju)004:2514: nar son nas bcad ris dang khe drag sgrub pa dang mthun pa tshom bu tshogs sgrub rnams te /
NK067(ju)004:2515: de ltar rim drug las bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:2517: rdo rje'i cho ga gsum bskyed dang sbyar na /
NK067(ju)004:2518: bar do'i rlung sems pha ma'i khu rdul gyi dbus su dang por zhugs pa ltar gsung yig 'bru /
NK067(ju)004:2519: mer nur ltar 'khrang gi gnas skabs ltar thugs phyag mtshan dang /
NK067(ju)004:2520: gong nya rus sbal nas lus rdzogs te btsas pa
NK067(ju)004:2521: ltar sku rdzogs pa zhes he ru ka galpo drangs
NK067(ju)004:2522: nas lo chen gyis gsungs so //
NK067(ju)004:2523: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbye sgo gzhan yang bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:2524: 'di nyid kyi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK067(ju)004:2525: lha yi rnam pa'i spyor ba yi //
NK067(ju)004:2526: zla ba rdo rje la sogs rim //
NK067(ju)004:2527: bskyed pa'i rim pa zhes su bshad //
NK067(ju)004:2528: rang bzhin grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK067(ju)004:2529: rdzogs pa'i rim pa zhes byar brjod //
NK067(ju)004:2530: ces gsungs pa ltar 'khor ba'i skye 'chi bar do gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:2531: thun mong ma yin pa'i sku gsum ste gzhi 'bras
NK067(ju)004:2532: de gnyis char dang rnam pa mthun par byas nas
NK067(ju)004:2533: rdzogs rim gyi smin byed du sgom pa'i dag rdzogs
NK067(ju)004:2534: smin gsum gyi gnad tshang ba'i bcos ma'i rnal 'byor
NK067(ju)004:2536: skye 'chi bar do sku gsum du dngos su sgyur
NK067(ju)004:2537: ba'i lam gyi rigs su gnas pa'i ma bcos pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2538: rnal 'byor ni rdzogs rim yin la /
NK067(ju)004:2539: de'i phyir gong ma kha cig kun btags bskyed rim
NK067(ju)004:2540: dang yongs grub rdzogs rim gyi rnal 'byor zhes gsungs
NK067(ju)004:2541: pa yang dgongs pa zab bo //
NK067(ju)004:2543: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob kyang mos
NK067(ju)004:2544: mno tsam gyis thun re'i nang du srung 'khor nas
NK067(ju)004:2545: go bgo lus srung bar gyi sgrub thabs tshang ba
NK067(ju)004:2546: re nyams su len pa mos sgom dang /
NK067(ju)004:2547: stong chen sogs lnga po snga ma snga ma la
NK067(ju)004:2548: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin gyi nyams lnga rdzogs
NK067(ju)004:2549: pa na gdod phyi ma phyi ma la 'jug pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2550: tshul gyis mthar chags su slob pa nges rdzogs te
NK067(ju)004:2551: lam rim las de ltar bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:2552: mos sgom du bshad pa'i tshul 'di nyid thun bzhir
NK067(ju)004:2553: sgom pa'i sbyor bas bskyed rim mthar phyin pa'ang yod
NK067(ju)004:2554: mod kyi / bka' srol 'di las cher mi 'byung la /
NK067(ju)004:2555: thun rer sgrub thabs kyi yan lag tshang bar sgom
NK067(ju)004:2556: pa la mos nges gnyis su phye ba'i mos sgom
NK067(ju)004:2557: gyis khyab pa ni 'dir yang mi bzhed de /
NK067(ju)004:2558: nges rdzogs kyi tshogs sgrub skabs su yang de ltar sgom par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:2559: mos sgom 'di la bskyed rim gyis khyab cing /
NK067(ju)004:2560: der thun re'i nang du tshang bar sgom rgyu'i ting
NK067(ju)004:2561: nge 'dzin ni rgya spros man chad kyi bzhi po
NK067(ju)004:2562: tsam yin yang / sems brtan pa'i mtshan ma ma
NK067(ju)004:2563: mthong pa'i sgrub pa po mang pos tshogs sgrub byed
NK067(ju)004:2564: pa'ang mos sgom du bzhag dgos pas spyir mos sgom
NK067(ju)004:2566: nges rdzogs la bskyed rdzogs kyi cha gnyis dang /
NK067(ju)004:2567: de la slob tshul yang gang zag gi khyad par gyis mi 'dra ba gnyis yod par gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:2568: dang po nas bskyed rdzogs zung 'brel du slob tshul dang /
NK067(ju)004:2569: bskyed rim mthar phyin nas rdzogs rim la 'jug pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:2571: thog mar stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor rtogs pas
NK067(ju)004:2572: g.yo ba'i nyams ri gzar gyi 'bab chu lta bu
NK067(ju)004:2573: dang / thob pa'i nyams rong khung dog pa'i 'bab chu lta bu /
NK067(ju)004:2574: goms pa'i nyams byang thang gi dal 'bab lta bu /
NK067(ju)004:2575: brtan pa'i nyams mtsho chung ser bus bskyod pa lta bu /
NK067(ju)004:2576: mthar phyin gyi nyams rgya mtsho rlab dang bral ba
NK067(ju)004:2577: lta bu ste nyams lnga rdzogs rdzogs su bsgoms pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2578: khog nas rdzogs rim pa'i 'od gsal gyi nyams myong
NK067(ju)004:2579: la 'dris cha thon pa na snying rje sgyu ma
NK067(ju)004:2580: bcos nas sgom / de rdzogs rim ma bcos pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2581: snying rje sgyu mar song ste nyams lnga rdzogs phan
NK067(ju)004:2582: phyag rgya gcig pa phra rags la dmigs pa'i bskyed
NK067(ju)004:2583: rim sbyang bas rkyen byas te rdzogs rim gyi lha
NK067(ju)004:2585: de la gsal brtan gyi nus pa rnyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2586: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi rnal 'byor yang dang por
NK067(ju)004:2587: bskyed rim dang rim gyis rdzogs rim du go 'pho
NK067(ju)004:2588: zhing / spros bcas mthar phyin nas tshogs sgrub kyi
NK067(ju)004:2589: spyod pa'i nye rgyus mtshams sbyar bas 'phags lam 'grub
NK067(ju)004:2590: zhing / pa ste / 'di'i rgya gcig gi bskyed
NK067(ju)004:2591: rim lta bu ni rdzogs rim thob la ma nyams
NK067(ju)004:2592: pa'i rgyud kyi bcos ma'i rnal 'byor yin pas /
NK067(ju)004:2594: bskyed pa'i rdzogs pa zhes gsungs pa lta bur 'gyur ro //
NK067(ju)004:2596: dang por bskyed rim gyi stong chen brtan pa thob thob tu sgom /
NK067(ju)004:2597: de nas snying rje sgyu ma de ltar sgom /
NK067(ju)004:2598: de lta bu'i rim pas spros bcas kyi bskyed rim
NK067(ju)004:2599: mthar son pa na tshogs sgrub kyis 'dod gzugs gang
NK067(ju)004:2600: rung gi rig 'dzin bsgrubs te mkha' spyod kyi zhing
NK067(ju)004:2601: sogs nyul zhing dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang lhan
NK067(ju)004:2602: cig tu rdzogs rim la brten nas lam lnga mthar
NK067(ju)004:2603: dbyung ba ste / de ltar gnyis yod kyang grol
NK067(ju)004:2604: lam rim gyis pa gtso bo rnams kyi sgom tshul
NK067(ju)004:2605: dngos snga ma yin par gsungs so //
NK067(ju)004:2606: de ltar spyi'i rnam bzhag la dpyad pa'i sa bon
NK067(ju)004:2607: tsam smos nas ting 'dzin lnga so so'i ngos 'dzin
NK067(ju)004:2609: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs cir yang mi dmigs
NK067(ju)004:2610: pa 'od gsal stong nyid kyi dbyings su mnyam par
NK067(ju)004:2611: 'jog cing chos sku'i ngo bor blta ba stong pa
NK067(ju)004:2613: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i sems
NK067(ju)004:2614: can la dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje longs sku'i
NK067(ju)004:2615: rang bzhin du shes nas sgom pa snying rje sgyu
NK067(ju)004:2616: ma'i rnal 'byor / stong nyid snying rje dbyer med
NK067(ju)004:2617: pa'i rang sems a dkar por bsgoms nas yi ge
NK067(ju)004:2618: spro bsdu la dmigs pa phra ba yig 'bru dang
NK067(ju)004:2619: ma'i rnal 'byor / / de las bskyed chog rgyas
NK067(ju)004:2620: bsdus ci rigs kyis rtsa ba'i lha yab yum zung
NK067(ju)004:2621: gcig byin rlabs kyi lha gsum dang dbu rgyan gyi
NK067(ju)004:2622: lha lnga thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' ste yan
NK067(ju)004:2623: lag gi lha dgu dang bcas par sgom pa rags
NK067(ju)004:2624: pa lha sku la bslab pa ste phyag rgya gcig
NK067(ju)004:2626: gnyal sangs rgyas grags kyi bzhed pa ltar rigs tha
NK067(ju)004:2627: dad kyi gtso bo gcig tu gyur pas rab tu
NK067(ju)004:2629: rigs tha mi dad kyi gtso bo so sos byed pas rab tu phye ba tshom bur bshad de /
NK067(ju)004:2630: de 'dra'i dkyil 'khor dang tshom bu spro ba gnyis
NK067(ju)004:2631: dang grangs dang zhal phyag rgya spro ba ste phyag
NK067(ju)004:2632: rgya spros bcas kyi dbye ba bzhi /
NK067(ju)004:2633: de la dkyil 'khor spro ba ni /
NK067(ju)004:2634: zhi dkyil 'bring po lha zhe gnyis ma /
NK067(ju)004:2635: rgyas pa de'i steng du rig chung gi sems dpa'
NK067(ju)004:2636: yab yum bzhi bcu bsnan pas brgyad cu rtsa gnyis
NK067(ju)004:2637: pa / bsdus pa rigs lnga dang sgo ba yab yum bco brgyad /
NK067(ju)004:2638: khro dkyil 'bring po yongs grags nga brgyad la khro bcu yab yum bsnan pas don brgyad /
NK067(ju)004:2639: rgyas pa de la rigs chung bsnan pas brgya dang bco brgyad /
NK067(ju)004:2640: bsdus pa lnga bcu rtsa brgyad pa rnams so //
NK067(ju)004:2642: mi bskyod pa yab yum rdo rje'i rigs chung zung bzhi /
NK067(ju)004:2643: sgo ba yab yum ste bco brgyad pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2644: sku gsung thugs kyi rigs gsum gyi gtso bo rigs
NK067(ju)004:2645: chung dang bcas pa la khro bo bcu las steng
NK067(ju)004:2646: 'og gi khro bo spangs pa'i yab yum zung brgyad
NK067(ju)004:2647: bsnan pas zhe drug ma dang /
NK067(ju)004:2648: rigs lnga rigs chung khro bcu yab yum ste bdun
NK067(ju)004:2649: cu pa rnams rim bzhin tshom bu gcig gsum lnga
NK067(ju)004:2651: gnas yul sgo skyong dbang mo rnams yod mnyam la /
NK067(ju)004:2652: rdo rje'i rigs kyi gtso 'khor bcu dang khro bcu yab yum bsnan pa'i don brgyad ma dang /
NK067(ju)004:2653: bud+d+ha dang pad+ma'i gtso 'khor yang bsnan pa'i go brgyad ma dang /
NK067(ju)004:2654: rigs lhag ma gnyis kyang bsnan pa'i brgya bco brgyad pa rnams snga ma bzhin no //
NK067(ju)004:2656: le'u brgyad pa ltar sangs rgyas stong dang /
NK067(ju)004:2658: bsam yas lhun grub tu spro ba dang gsum /
NK067(ju)004:2659: de'i rigs pa khro bo la'ang sbyar bas lha grangs stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2660: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2661: bsam yas lhun grub ste spro ba gsum mo //
NK067(ju)004:2662: bsam yas lhun grub spro ba la 'phags lam pa
NK067(ju)004:2663: dgos zhes gsungs pa yod kyang de tshun chad la
NK067(ju)004:2664: de ltar dngos su spro mi nus pa yin gyi
NK067(ju)004:2665: sgom mi nus pa min no //
NK067(ju)004:2667: zhi ba rgyas pa thub drug dang yum rnams ma gtogs thams cad zhal gsum phyag drug pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2668: 'bring po rgyal ba rigs drug tsam zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK067(ju)004:2669: bsdus pa thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis la /
NK067(ju)004:2670: khro bo la gtso bo dbu phyag grangs med dang dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa /
NK067(ju)004:2671: 'khor gyi ma mo rnams kyang zhal gsum phyag drug
NK067(ju)004:2672: pa sogs rgyud nas bshad kyang brgyud pa'i phyag bzhes
NK067(ju)004:2673: su rgyas pa la rigs lnga dang /
NK067(ju)004:2674: 'bring po la gtso bo tsam zhal gsum phyag drug pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2675: bsdus pa thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:2676: de ltar ting nge 'dzin bzhi po so sor sgrub cing rtsal thon nas /
NK067(ju)004:2677: slar de rnams thun re'i nang du tshang bar bsgom
NK067(ju)004:2678: ste bogs 'don pa'am khyad par du 'gro bar byed
NK067(ju)004:2679: pa ni tshom bu tshogs sgrub yin te /
NK067(ju)004:2681: phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi bzung ba /
NK067(ju)004:2682: bsnyen sgrub yan ga lag bzhis gzhung bsrang ba /
NK067(ju)004:2683: 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bstan pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:2685: bdag dbang bar chad med cing yid du 'ong ba'i sar g.yos sbyor byed pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2687: gsang spyod la 'jug pa'i khang pa rim gsum brtsigs pa gnas phun tshogs dang /
NK067(ju)004:2688: gza' skar sbyor byed tshes grangs sogs legs pa'i dus phun tshogs /
NK067(ju)004:2692: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad rnams tshang bar 'du byas pa yo byad phun tshogs /
NK067(ju)004:2693: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK067(ju)004:2694: zhes sogs ltar rang bzhin brgyad ldan gyi slob dpon dang /
NK067(ju)004:2695: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal /
NK067(ju)004:2696: sogs yon tan drug ldan gyi 'khor te ston 'khor
NK067(ju)004:2697: de gnyis sgrub pa po phun tshogs zhes gcig tu
NK067(ju)004:2698: bsdus te / de lta bu'i 'dus pa chung 'bring chen po ji ltar tshogs pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2699: bsnyen sgrub rnam pa bzhi'i srol du tshud pa sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa ste lnga'o //
NK067(ju)004:2701: sgrub dus kyi bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i dang po bsnyen pa la'ang sngon du bya ba'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:2702: bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:2704: sngar spros bcas man chad kyi ting 'dzin bzhi mthar phyin par bslabs pa de nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:2710: dkyil 'khor bri zhing rgyan bkod pa rnams sngon du btang ste /
NK067(ju)004:2711: gral tshul gyi phyag nas rtags gdab par bya /
NK067(ju)004:2714: las rim gyi ting nge 'dzin lnga po bsgom la
NK067(ju)004:2715: 'dzab kha phye nas gsal ba gsum ldan gyi 'dzab
NK067(ju)004:2716: bzla / dkyil 'khor phye ba de rang la bstim
NK067(ju)004:2717: zhing tshogs mchod sogs byed pa nub dang po'i bsnyen
NK067(ju)004:2718: pa ste bsnyen pa'i yan lag /
NK067(ju)004:2719: las rim de dang mthun pas 'dab kyi tsha 'od
NK067(ju)004:2720: zer dkar po'i spro bsdus dngos grub kyi snod rung
NK067(ju)004:2721: du bya ba la ci tsam sgrub pa'i dus kyi
NK067(ju)004:2722: phyed tshun chad brtson pa nye bsnyen gyi yan lag
NK067(ju)004:2723: / phyed phyi mar 'od zer dmar po'i spro bsdus
NK067(ju)004:2724: dngos grub dbang du bya ba sgrub pa'i yan lag
NK067(ju)004:2725: / / dngos grub kyi mtshan ma yin ches pa
NK067(ju)004:2726: byung ba na 'od zer mthing khas dngos grub bsdu
NK067(ju)004:2727: zhing lha dang rdzas dang yum gyi mkha' rnams las
NK067(ju)004:2728: dngos grub blang ba sgrub chen gyi yan lag go
NK067(ju)004:2729: / / // rgyud nyid las tshogs sgrub ston pa
NK067(ju)004:2730: na zhen med kyi ngang nas 'dod yon gyi yo
NK067(ju)004:2731: byad lnga la longs spyod tshul 'ba' zhig rtsal du
NK067(ju)004:2732: bton nas gsungs pas tshogs sgrub kyi don po ni
NK067(ju)004:2733: bde chen gyi ye shes rgyas pa'i sgo nas de
NK067(ju)004:2734: kho na nyid kyi rtogs pa 'bar zhing brtan pa
NK067(ju)004:2736: de'i mthus ting nge 'dzin snga ma bzhi'i rgyun yang
NK067(ju)004:2737: shin tu khyad zhugs par 'gyur bas bogs 'don du
NK067(ju)004:2738: 'gro lugs dang / dngos grub myur du 'grub pa'i rgyu mtshan gnyis ka de yin no //
NK067(ju)004:2740: khyad par zhu bde lam byed la rdzogs rim gyi ma khyab pa ni grags che bas ma phye'o //
NK067(ju)004:2741: 'grel pa rnams su dngos grub blang ba'i skabs ma
NK067(ju)004:2742: gtogs par a li ka li'i yo byad la spyod
NK067(ju)004:2743: tshul gsal bar ma smos kyang /
NK067(ju)004:2745: sgrub thabs kyi mchod pa'i nang du /
NK067(ju)004:2746: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK067(ju)004:2747: zhes sogs 'byung ba las shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:2749: brtson 'grus drag pos bsgrubs pas zla drug la sogs
NK067(ju)004:2750: pa'i dus nges pa can na phra yang sogs kyi
NK067(ju)004:2751: yon tan dang ldan pa'i rig 'dzin gyi lus 'dod
NK067(ju)004:2752: gzugs gang rung gi lha dang rjes su mthun par
NK067(ju)004:2753: thob ste / 'dod gzugs kyi rig 'dzin gnyis gang
NK067(ju)004:2754: 'thob ni las dang ye shes kyi phyag rgya'i khyad
NK067(ju)004:2755: par gyis yin zhes gsung ngo //
NK067(ju)004:2756: 'di lta bu'i rig 'dzin ni thun mong gi dngos grub chen po'o //
NK067(ju)004:2757: lam rim las zhi ba'i tshogs sgrub kyis rab zla ba drug dang /
NK067(ju)004:2758: tha mas lo gcig zla ba bzhin dang /
NK067(ju)004:2759: khro bos rab zla ba gnyis dang /
NK067(ju)004:2760: tha mas drug na 'grub pa sogs kyi khyad gsungs
NK067(ju)004:2761: pa la 'dzab 'thor 'dril gyi khyad du bzhed pa'ang
NK067(ju)004:2762: yod mod kyi / phal cher snang ston gyi bzhed pa ltar khro bo bar chad 'dul ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:2763: drag cing myur pa'i phrin las kyi lhar bzhengs pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis yin byas na bde zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2764: dngos grub kyi pho nya'i dbang gis kyang khyad cung zad zhugs sam snyam mo //
NK067(ju)004:2765: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud gzhan las tshogs spyod kyi
NK067(ju)004:2766: mthar thun mong gi grub pa chen po sgrub pa
NK067(ju)004:2767: la da dung sbyin sreg dang 'khrul 'khor sogs par
NK067(ju)004:2768: du brgyud dgos par gsungs shing /
NK067(ju)004:2769: 'dir de dag la mi ltos par tshogs sgrub kyi
NK067(ju)004:2770: dus nyid du rig 'dzin 'grub par gsungs pa ni
NK067(ju)004:2771: / snga ma bskyed rim cung zad brtan pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:2772: phyi ma cher brtan pa'i dbang du byas par bzhed
NK067(ju)004:2773: pa yod kyang phra mo'i rnal 'byor mtha' phyin pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2774: tshogs spyod pas kyang snga ma ltar byed par bshad
NK067(ju)004:2775: pas sgrub lugs kyi khyad lta bu'i 'byed dgos sam
NK067(ju)004:2776: brtag par bya'o // phyag rgya'i ting nge 'dzin gong
NK067(ju)004:2777: 'og 'di dag thams cad du lta ba'i skabs su
NK067(ju)004:2778: bshad pa'i rang snang ris med kyi go don srog
NK067(ju)004:2780: slob dpon ye shes zhabs kyi gzhung las bskyed rim
NK067(ju)004:2781: gyis yul dus tshad can 'joms par gsungs pa'ang 'di
NK067(ju)004:2783: rang snang ris med kyi dkyil 'khor la grangs tshad
NK067(ju)004:2784: dang zhal phyag sogs gcig tu nges pa med kyang
NK067(ju)004:2785: sgrub thabs su nges pa ltar ma bstan na don
NK067(ju)004:2786: de la rnam pa gsal ba dang nga rgyal brtan
NK067(ju)004:2787: pa sogs kyi ting nge 'dzin skyed mi nus pas
NK067(ju)004:2788: de ltar bstan ces bde shegs 'dus pa las gsungs
NK067(ju)004:2789: so // de 'dra ba'i ting nge 'dzin lnga ni
NK067(ju)004:2790: bskyed rim kho na'i dbang du byas pa yin la
NK067(ju)004:2791: so // / rdzogs rim gyi ting nge 'dzin lnga ni /
NK067(ju)004:2792: dang por chos dang chos min gyi bya ba gzhan btang ste /
NK067(ju)004:2793: lus gnad rnam snang gi chos bdun dang ldan pas 'dug la /
NK067(ju)004:2794: sems kyi gnad bzhag thabs gnyis gang rung la gnas par bya ste /
NK067(ju)004:2796: blo che ba shes rab kyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:2797: blo chung gdams ngag gi stobs kyis 'jog pa gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:2799: spros bral gyi chos nyid la sems 'jog go snyam
NK067(ju)004:2800: pa dran tsam gyis rig pa yul med du sal
NK067(ju)004:2801: ler 'jog pa rig pa spyi blugs su dang /
NK067(ju)004:2802: sngar gtan la phabs pa'i lta ba dran par byas
NK067(ju)004:2803: nas de'i ngang la gsal ba so ma shor tsam
NK067(ju)004:2804: du 'jog pa mthong ba'i rjes la 'jog pa gnyis
NK067(ju)004:2805: yod cing / phyi ma ni nang du rang sems
NK067(ju)004:2806: kyi ngo bo la bltas pa na cir yang mi
NK067(ju)004:2807: mthong zhing de'i ngang la ma bcos par 'jog pa
NK067(ju)004:2808: yod cing / ste / gsum ka sems kyi de
NK067(ju)004:2809: nyid la 'jog par khyad med kyang 'jog byed kyi
NK067(ju)004:2810: thabs sam sgo mi 'dra ba las dabye'o //
NK067(ju)004:2811: gang lta yang rtse gcig tu dang /
NK067(ju)004:2812: bar ma chad par bslab pas gzung 'dzin rags pa
NK067(ju)004:2813: dang bral ba'i 'od gsal nam mkha' lta bu mngon
NK067(ju)004:2814: du gyur nas stong gzugs zhes stong pa 'od gsal
NK067(ju)004:2815: gyi char gyur pa'i gzugs snang ngam stong pa 'od
NK067(ju)004:2816: gsal gyi gzugs brnyan lta bu'i snang ba sgyu ma'i
NK067(ju)004:2817: grong khyer ltar dbyibs dang kha dog gi rnam pa
NK067(ju)004:2819: goms pa yun bsring bas 'od gsal je 'thug tu 'gro zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2820: ji tsam 'thug pa'i rim pa ltar stong gzugs de
NK067(ju)004:2821: dag je dwangs je gsal dang cher mched par 'gyur
NK067(ju)004:2822: ro // de lta bu'i 'od gsal de la 'khrul
NK067(ju)004:2823: pa'i kun rtog gis stong pas stong pa chen po'i
NK067(ju)004:2825: 'di'i tshe stong gzugs shar ba de la gtso bor
NK067(ju)004:2826: mi byed par 'od gsal rang gi bzhugs tshul mi
NK067(ju)004:2827: rtog pa'i dbyings la bsre ba rtsal 'don byed par
NK067(ju)004:2828: mngon no // de byang bar goms pa na 'od
NK067(ju)004:2829: gsal rgya bskyed de snang ba de rnams la bsres
NK067(ju)004:2830: nas rtse gcig tu bzhag pas ris med kyi snang
NK067(ju)004:2831: ba sngar las kyang cher mched cing /
NK067(ju)004:2832: de thams cad thun mong ma yin pa'i dmigs med
NK067(ju)004:2833: kyi snying rje'am mi dmigs pa'i bde ba'i yo lang
NK067(ju)004:2835: de brtan pa'i tshe stong gzugs la las rung gi yon tan khyad par can thob pas /
NK067(ju)004:2836: rkyen cung zad tsam gyi rdzogs rim pa'i lha sku phyag rgya gcig tu sgyur nus pa yin no //
NK067(ju)004:2837: mnyam bzhag tu de ltar rtsal 'byongs pas de las
NK067(ju)004:2838: lang ba na'ang 'gro ba thams cad stong gzugs bzhin
NK067(ju)004:2839: du bde chen snying rje'i rol ba sgyu ma lta
NK067(ju)004:2840: bur 'char te snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor ro
NK067(ju)004:2841: // de nas bskyed rdzogs zung 'brel byed tshe kun
NK067(ju)004:2842: bzang yab yum lta bu'i bskyed rim gyi ting nge
NK067(ju)004:2843: // 'dzin dang / gang ltar yang 'phen pa'i rkyen
NK067(ju)004:2844: la brten nas stong gzugs de thams cad lha sku
NK067(ju)004:2845: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnam par sad pa ni rgya
