NK067(ju)004:2847: stong gzugs kyi lha sku ji snyed shar yang kun
NK067(ju)004:2848: bzang yab yum lta bu gcig gi rnam pa can
NK067(ju)004:2849: du mtshungs pas de ltar brjod kyi /
NK067(ju)004:2850: stong gzugs kyi sku gcig las mi 'char ba ni min pa 'dra'o //
NK067(ju)004:2851: bka' srol 'di las rgya gcig gi 'go brtsams pa
NK067(ju)004:2852: nas zung 'jug gi lha sku yin zhes 'byung ba
NK067(ju)004:2853: ni ting nge 'dzin dang po'i stong pa dang gnyis
NK067(ju)004:2854: pa'i snying rje zung 'jug tu song ba tsam la
NK067(ju)004:2855: dgongs kyi / zung 'jug gi sku dngos min no //
NK067(ju)004:2856: de nas dkyil 'khor dang tshom bu'i 'khor lo spro
NK067(ju)004:2857: ba'i bskyed rim gyi rkyen cung zad las stong gzugs
NK067(ju)004:2858: kyi lha gtso 'khor dang tshom bu'i rnam pa mtha'
NK067(ju)004:2859: yas pa dang / de dag re re la'ang grangs
NK067(ju)004:2860: spro ba'i skabs ltar grangs med pa ma 'dres yongs
NK067(ju)004:2861: rdzogs su 'char ba nas bzung mthar phyin pa'i bar
NK067(ju)004:2862: ni phyag rgya spros bcas te /
NK067(ju)004:2863: de ltar ting nge 'dzin snga ma bzhi'o //
NK067(ju)004:2864: phyag rgya spro ba'i bskyed rim gyi skabs 'dir /
NK067(ju)004:2865: phung khams sogs rtogs tshogs thams cad lhar sbyong ba'i
NK067(ju)004:2866: ched du sangs rgyas zhe gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor sgom
NK067(ju)004:2867: pa dang / phung sogs kyi cha re re yang
NK067(ju)004:2868: rnam dag gi yon tan thams cad par sgrub pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2869: ched du lha de dag re re zhing yang dkyil
NK067(ju)004:2870: 'khor gyi lha thams cad tshang bar sgom pa dang
NK067(ju)004:2871: pa dang / / de ltar dag pa gcig kyang
NK067(ju)004:2872: dag pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid du 'gyur ba'i
NK067(ju)004:2873: tshul de'ang rtogs tshogs thams cad mi shigs pa'i srog
NK067(ju)004:2874: dang ldan pa rgyu mtshan du bzung ba'i steng nas
NK067(ju)004:2875: sgom pa'i ched du lus la bkod pa'i lha thams
NK067(ju)004:2876: cad so sor ye shes sems dpa' dang ldan par
NK067(ju)004:2878: lha rtog dbyer med du shes pa ni bskyed rdzogs kyi lam gnad gces shos zhig tu snang ngo //
NK067(ju)004:2879: de dag sgom pa'i rjes thob kyi skabs rnams su'ang
NK067(ju)004:2880: mnyam bzhag gi rnal 'byor gang yin des snang spyod
NK067(ju)004:2881: thams cad rgyas btab nas rnal 'byor de dang mi
NK067(ju)004:2882: mthun pa'i rnam rtog sdom pa'am gnad gcig ste 'di
NK067(ju)004:2883: ni la dor ba spyod pa'i thad na gsal lo
NK067(ju)004:2884: // de bzhin du nyin mo ting nge 'dzin gang
NK067(ju)004:2885: la slob pa de nyid mtshan mo'i rnal 'byor du
NK067(ju)004:2886: 'khyer tshul yang rgyud 'grel las stong chen gyi skabs
NK067(ju)004:2887: su sad pa'i dus kyi 'od gsal dang mtshan mo'i
NK067(ju)004:2888: gnyid 'thug gi 'od gsal gnyis sbrel te nyams su
NK067(ju)004:2889: // len pa dang / snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs
NK067(ju)004:2890: su nyin snang dang rmi lam gyi snang ba thams
NK067(ju)004:2891: cad sgyu mar mthong zhes 'byung bas rnal 'byor dang
NK067(ju)004:2892: po gnyis kyis gnyid dang rmi lam sbyong tshul gsal
NK067(ju)004:2893: // len pa dang / bar bstan cing / tshul
NK067(ju)004:2894: des rmi lam gyi snying rje sgyu ma phyag rgya
NK067(ju)004:2895: gcig spros su bsgyur nas sgom pa'ang go nus la
NK067(ju)004:2896: // len pa dang / bar bstan cing / / sngar lam rim drangs par /
NK067(ju)004:2897: 'chi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK067(ju)004:2898: sogs kyis 'chi ba dang stong chen bsre ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:2899: bar do snying rje sgyu ma dang bsre ba sogs
NK067(ju)004:2900: kyang legs par thon pas bsre ba'i man ngag ces
NK067(ju)004:2901: pa'i ming ma btags kyang don tshang ba yin no
NK067(ju)004:2902: // 'on kyang 'dir rmi lam dang bar do'i phyag
NK067(ju)004:2903: rgya gcig spros sad pa dang skye ba sbyong byed
NK067(ju)004:2904: kyang yin pas gzhan dang mi 'dra'o //
NK067(ju)004:2905: de'ang lta ba'i skabs su gtan tshigs rnams la brten
NK067(ju)004:2906: nas sems dang ye shes thun mong gi snang ba
NK067(ju)004:2907: rags pa rnams la ye shes kyi rang snang kho
NK067(ju)004:2908: na'i phyogs bzung ste bltas pas grub mtha' 'od gsal
NK067(ju)004:2909: mngon sum du sad pa ni ye shes kyi snang
NK067(ju)004:2910: ba thun min dngos su skul ba'i sgo dang po
NK067(ju)004:2911: yin te / 'dir ye shes kyi snang ba thun min ni stong gzugs la bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:2912: de 'dra'i snang ba de ting nge 'dzin dang por mthong nas /
NK067(ju)004:2913: gnyis par ji ltar mthong ba de la dbang sgyur bsgrub /
NK067(ju)004:2914: gsum pa nas lha skur bsgyur te rtsa la sbyang
NK067(ju)004:2915: bas gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi'i steng na
NK067(ju)004:2916: shin tu phra ba'i snang ba rnam pa thams cad
NK067(ju)004:2917: pa spro ba'i nus pa yod pa de ye shes
NK067(ju)004:2918: kyi rlung gis bskul nas gsal bar sad cing /
NK067(ju)004:2919: gzhi'i yon tan dang shes 'jug gi lam ma bu
NK067(ju)004:2920: 'phrod de gcig grogs gcig gis byas nas ye shes
NK067(ju)004:2921: rang snang gi rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor dngos
NK067(ju)004:2922: gnas pa 'grub pa'i nus pa bde blag tu rdzogs
NK067(ju)004:2923: par 'gyur ba ni sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam gnad
NK067(ju)004:2924: chen po ste / thabs grol gnyis ka'i skabs su
NK067(ju)004:2925: rtogs daka'i mdud pa 'di las 'grol dka' ba med
NK067(ju)004:2926: pas rtsal ci yod phyung nas sems pa gces so
NK067(ju)004:2927: chen po ste / // rgya spros mthar phyin nas
NK067(ju)004:2928: rnal 'byor pa'i 'byor pa dang dbang po'i rim pa
NK067(ju)004:2929: bzhin du 'dus pa che 'bring chung du ci rigs
NK067(ju)004:2930: kyi tshogs sgrub bam yang na stong gzugs kyi lha
NK067(ju)004:2931: mo 'ba' zhig la brten nas mi 'gyur ba'i bde
NK067(ju)004:2932: ba bsgrubs te zag med kyi lam la sbyor ba
NK067(ju)004:2933: ni tshogs sgrub kyi ting nge 'dzin dang bar chad
NK067(ju)004:2934: med pa'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:2935: tshogs sgrub kyi skabs su'ang rgya spros kyi ting nge 'dzin phul du byung ba yod mod kyi /
NK067(ju)004:2936: ting nge 'dzin lngar phye ba'i bzhi pa ni ma yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:2937: des stong chen sogs gzhan la'ang shes par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:2938: le'u dgu pa rtsa 'grel gyi tshig zin la 'bras
NK067(ju)004:2939: bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bstan pa 'byung ba
NK067(ju)004:2940: ni rdzogs rim gyi tshogs sgrub 'di nyid kyi dbang
NK067(ju)004:2942: der tshogs sgrub kyi dus su lha tshom bu gcig
NK067(ju)004:2943: pa dang gsum pa sogs gang bsgom gyi khyad par
NK067(ju)004:2944: las 'bras bu dman mchog gi khyad 'jug par bshad
NK067(ju)004:2945: pa ni rgya gcig dang tshogs sgrub kyi bar du
NK067(ju)004:2946: spros bcas bor ba'i thod rgal ba yod par bshad
NK067(ju)004:2947: pas de lta bu la sbyar dgos sam dpyad do
NK067(ju)004:2948: // shes 'jug gi mtshan nyid de dag la tshogs
NK067(ju)004:2949: sbyor gyi lam gnyis kyi rnam bzhag bya ba'i tshul
NK067(ju)004:2950: // ni / sdom t+aika snye mar bskyed rim pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2951: tshogs sgrub kyis 'dod gzugs kyi rig 'dzin grub pa'i
NK067(ju)004:2953: rdzogs rim la zhugs pa nas sbyor lam du 'jog
NK067(ju)004:2954: par bshad pa sngar brjod pa'i rim gnyis la slob
NK067(ju)004:2956: yongs grags kyi bshad sgros dang yang mthun par bzung bde mod /
NK067(ju)004:2957: bskyed rdzogs sbrag nas sgom pa'i phyogs la rnam bzhag
NK067(ju)004:2958: gzhan dgos pas sgyu 'phrul rang gi bshad sgros su
NK067(ju)004:2959: / tshogs rdzogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:2960: sbyor lam tshogs sgrub ces grags che ba ltar dgos so //
NK067(ju)004:2961: sngags bla med kyi tshogs lam la bsgom stobs kyis
NK067(ju)004:2962: rlung sems dbu mar tshud pa las byung ba'i rdzogs
NK067(ju)004:2963: rim gyi rnal 'byor du ma zhig yod par yid
NK067(ju)004:2964: bzhin mdzod rtsa 'grel sogs mang po las ches gsal
NK067(ju)004:2965: bar gsungs pa'ang phyogs 'di la 'thad do //
NK067(ju)004:2966: de'ang ji srid bcos shing brtags pa'i rnal 'byor la
NK067(ju)004:2967: ltos pa de srid du tshogs lam pa yin la
NK067(ju)004:2968: / rang bzhin grub pa'i rnal 'byor ram ma bcos
NK067(ju)004:2969: pa'i rnal 'byor 'ba' zhig tu song ba na sbyor
NK067(ju)004:2971: tshogs lam du 'jog pa bcos ma'i rnal 'byor gyi cha nas yin kyang /
NK067(ju)004:2972: tshogs lam pa'i rgyud kyi ma bcos pa'i rnal 'byor rnams tshogs lam du 'jog pa mi 'gal lo //
NK067(ju)004:2973: 'dis rdzogs rim la dang por 'jug pa'i sngon du
NK067(ju)004:2974: bskyed rim mthar phyin pa ma song ba'i gnad kyis
NK067(ju)004:2975: rdzogs rim pa'i rgya spros grub pa'i 'og tu'ang bskyed
NK067(ju)004:2976: rim la brten nas spro bsdu'i rtsal sbyang dgos pas
NK067(ju)004:2977: rnal 'byor snga ma bzhi ka tshogs lam du 'jog
NK067(ju)004:2978: pa'i rgyu mtshan de yin no //
NK067(ju)004:2979: rgya spros las bsam yas lhun grub spro ba'i thad 'dir zhib cha cung zad dgos so //
NK067(ju)004:2980: de ltar byas na bskyed rdzogs sbrag ma'i lugs 'dir
NK067(ju)004:2981: so skye'i sa'i rdzogs rim gyi yon tan phal cher
NK067(ju)004:2982: tshogs lam nyid du rdzogs par 'dod dgos shing /
NK067(ju)004:2983: sbyor lam la drod sogs bzhi'i dbye ba byas pa'ang
NK067(ju)004:2984: ma mthong bas bla med kyi rgyud sde'i lam gyi
NK067(ju)004:2985: 'gros gzhan dang mi 'dra ba ches che ba zhig
NK067(ju)004:2987: da dung mkhas pa rnams kyis zhib tu brtag dpyad mdzad par zhu'o //
NK067(ju)004:2988: rgya gcig man chad tshogs lam dang /
NK067(ju)004:2989: spros bcas nas sbyor lam dang lo tshod bstun par
NK067(ju)004:2990: 'dod pa sogs kyang yod de 'dir ma brjod do
NK067(ju)004:2991: // gsum pa lam gyur gyi 'bras bu ni /
NK067(ju)004:2992: lam dang gang zag gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:2993: lam la mthong sgom mthar lam gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:2994: de rgyud ldan gyi gang zag la /
NK067(ju)004:2995: rnam smin tshe dbang phyag rgya lhun gyi grub //
NK067(ju)004:2996: ces pa ltar rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'o /
NK067(ju)004:2997: dang po rnam smin rig 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)004:2998: rnam smin gyi lus rten rags pa dang ma bral ba /
NK067(ju)004:2999: sems yi dam gyi lha skur smin pa /
NK067(ju)004:3000: lus rgya dang bral ma thag phyag chen rig 'dzin
NK067(ju)004:3001: la sbyor nges pa ste chos gsum ldan gyi mthong
NK067(ju)004:3002: lam pa'o // de thob pa na mngon shes la
NK067(ju)004:3003: brten nas gleng gzhi'i 'jig rten tsam du 'gro ba'i
NK067(ju)004:3004: don spyod nus pa sogs yon tan gzhan mang po
NK067(ju)004:3005: lam pa'o // yang 'thob bo // 'di la rnam smin gyi lus rgyas bcing ba'i cha nas dang /
NK067(ju)004:3006: sems lha skur rnam par smin pa'i cha nas rnam
NK067(ju)004:3007: smin rig 'dzin zhes sgra bshad tshul gnyis yod gsung
NK067(ju)004:3009: lus zag med du gyur pa /
NK067(ju)004:3010: 'khor sgyur dang 'dod gzugs kyi lha'i gtso bo cha byad can gyi mthong lam pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:3011: rdzogs rim gyi lag rjes su gyur pa'i dbang shes nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK067(ju)004:3012: spyir grags pa'i mngon shes drug gis gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgyar sems can gyi don byed pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:3013: 'dir zag med ces pa'i zag pa ni bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)004:3014: zhen pa phyin ci log gi sgro 'dogs nyon mongs pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:3015: lus rang dbang med par 'dor ba lus kyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3016: khams bde mi bde rang dbang med par 'byung ba khams kyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3017: las kyis rang dbang med par lus len pa skye
NK067(ju)004:3018: gnas kyi zag pa ste dang po rtsa ba dang
NK067(ju)004:3019: lhag ma gsum yan lag go //
NK067(ju)004:3020: de la rig 'dzin de gnyis ka'ang don gyi 'od gsal mtshan nyid pa thob pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3021: rtsa ba'i zag pa zad pa'i spangs rtogs kyi cha
NK067(ju)004:3022: la khyad med kyang dbang po rno rtul gyi dbang
NK067(ju)004:3023: gis rags lus ye shes kyi mes sbyang nus ma
NK067(ju)004:3024: nus sam yan lag gi zag pa gsum zad ma
NK067(ju)004:3025: zad kyi khyad par las phye bar lam chung las
NK067(ju)004:3026: / nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK067(ju)004:3027: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK067(ju)004:3028: zhes pa drang nas bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:3029: des na gang zag gcig gis rig 'dzin 'di gnyis ka bgrod pa ni mi srid de /
NK067(ju)004:3030: mthong lam lan gnyis su 'thob pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:3032: rtsa ba'i lus rten yi dam gyi lha'i rnam pa can mtshan dpes brgyan pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3033: sprul pa'i lus rngon ba dang smad 'tshong sogs sna tshogs pa'i gzugs su ston cing /
NK067(ju)004:3034: tshe dbang las kyang gsal brtan dag gsum gyi khyad
NK067(ju)004:3035: par 'phags pa'i mngon shes kyis longs sku'i zhing dang
NK067(ju)004:3036: mnyam par 'gro ba'i don byed pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:3037: 'di la sgom lam sa dgu'i dbye bas de snyed dang /
NK067(ju)004:3038: dgu po de la rigs lnga'i gnas skabs kyis lngar mdzad pa'ang yod do //
NK067(ju)004:3040: mthar lam pa zhes sa bcu pa'i khyad par lam la gnas pa /
NK067(ju)004:3041: sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs sku dang rjes su mthun pa'i lus can /
NK067(ju)004:3042: rtogs pa dang phrin las sangs rgyas nyid dang phyogs mtshungs pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:3043: rig 'dzin phyi ma gnyis su lhan cig gnas pa
NK067(ju)004:3044: dang bag la nyal gyi dri ma phra mo spang
NK067(ju)004:3045: bar gsungs pa'i dri ma rnams ni shes sgrib kho
NK067(ju)004:3046: na yin te / nyon sgrib kun brtags lhan skyes
NK067(ju)004:3047: ma phye bar mthong lam nas spang bar bshad pa'i
NK067(ju)004:3048: na yin te / phyir ro // slob lam du
NK067(ju)004:3049: rig 'dzin gcig las ma bgrod par sangs rgyas thob
NK067(ju)004:3051: shin tu blo che ba 'ga' zhig tshe dbang nas rgya chen dang lhun grub gnyis bor nas dang /
NK067(ju)004:3052: rgya chen tsam bor nas dang /
NK067(ju)004:3053: rgya chen nas lhun grub bor te 'tshang rgya ba'i thod rgal ba bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)004:3054: de dag gi dka' ba'i gnas la dpyod pa'i sgo cung zad btod na /
NK067(ju)004:3055: 'di dang dus 'khor ba'i lugs gnyis la spyir mi
NK067(ju)004:3056: 'dra ba'i khyad par che yang stong gzugs kyi phyag
NK067(ju)004:3057: rgya la brten nas mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba sgrub
NK067(ju)004:3058: pa dang / des phung khams rags pa sbyong tshul
NK067(ju)004:3059: dgongs pa mthun par rgyal ba g.yung sogs bzhed la
NK067(ju)004:3060: pa dang / / de ltar kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po'ang bzhed de /
NK067(ju)004:3062: sa dang sa yi yon tan rnams //
NK067(ju)004:3063: rtsa rnams kyi ni skye 'bri las //
NK067(ju)004:3064: rlung dang bde chen las 'dod de //
NK067(ju)004:3067: rnam bzhi'am gsum mam lnga 'khor lo //
NK067(ju)004:3068: gnyis gnyis kyi ni gcig ma rdzogs //
NK067(ju)004:3069: sa bcu tha mas ye shes sa //
NK067(ju)004:3070: bzhi pas steng dang 'og tu grags //
NK067(ju)004:3071: zhes gsungs pa la brten nas yid bzhin mdzod kyi /
NK067(ju)004:3072: 'khor lo bzhi yi rlung sems las rung tshe /
NK067(ju)004:3073: lam bzhi'i yon tan rim bzhin 'char ba ste //
NK067(ju)004:3074: dbu ma'i rtsa mdud gnyis gnyis grol ba las //
NK067(ju)004:3075: sa bcu'i yon tan nang nas 'char bar bzhed //
NK067(ju)004:3076: ces pa rtsa 'grel du 'byung ba rnams 'gyur med
NK067(ju)004:3077: kyi bde bas rags lus za tshul bshad pa rnams
NK067(ju)004:3078: dang rags bshad zhib bshad kyi khyad par ma gtogs
NK067(ju)004:3079: dgongs pa gcig ces mkhas grub gong ma 'gas gsungs
NK067(ju)004:3080: so // de ltar byas na 'dir 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)004:3081: phyag rgya gcig spros su stong gzugs kyi sku thob
NK067(ju)004:3082: nas de 'dra ba'i phyag rgya'i stobs kyis bde chen
NK067(ju)004:3083: 'dren pa'i ched du tshogs spyod byed pa yin zhing
NK067(ju)004:3084: / nam mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba skad cig dang
NK067(ju)004:3085: po thob pa nas lus kyi bem po'i cha dag
NK067(ju)004:3086: pa'i mgo rtsom pa yin pas rags lus dwangs mar
NK067(ju)004:3087: song ba'i tshe dbang rig 'dzin du 'jog chog go
NK067(ju)004:3088: / // dbang rtul ni phyag rgya chen po grub
NK067(ju)004:3089: nas de la tshogs kyi spyod pas rjes chags brtsams
NK067(ju)004:3090: kyang mchog bde 'dren mi nus pas 'phags lam thob
NK067(ju)004:3091: kyang snyigs ma'i lus dag ma dag nyis su byung
NK067(ju)004:3093: 'di bas mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba thob nas tshe de la 'tshang rgya bas khyab kyang /
NK067(ju)004:3094: stong gzugs kyi sku mtshan nyid thob pa tsam la de 'dra'i sems med par bzhed de /
NK067(ju)004:3095: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi bshad pas shes so //
NK067(ju)004:3096: rnam smin pas bar dor rgya chen 'grub lugs ni /
NK067(ju)004:3097: de'i 'chi dus kyi shin tu phra ba'i rlung de
NK067(ju)004:3098: don gyi 'od gsal mtshan nyid pas gser sbyang ltar
NK067(ju)004:3099: dag cing dri med kyi khams su sbyangs pa dang
NK067(ju)004:3100: / sngar nas snying rje sgyu ma sogs kyis rmi
NK067(ju)004:3101: lam dang srid pa bar do'i snang zhen sku dang
NK067(ju)004:3102: ye shes su sbyangs stobs kyi thob pa'i stong gzugs
NK067(ju)004:3103: kyi sku la gsal brtan rdzogs pa'i rten 'brel gyis
NK067(ju)004:3104: 'od gsal las ldang ba na zung 'jug sgyu ma'i
NK067(ju)004:3105: sku mtshan dpes brgyan par bzhengs pa la tshegs med
NK067(ju)004:3106: / par mngon te / tshe dbang las rgya chen
NK067(ju)004:3107: du 'phos tshe rags lus lha'i skur 'grub pa la'ang
NK067(ju)004:3108: sgrub tshul zur pa med do //
NK067(ju)004:3109: tshe dbang dang des thob pa'i rgya chen lta bur
NK067(ju)004:3110: stong gzugs sku yang gsal brtan dag gsum phul du
NK067(ju)004:3112: stong gzugs mnyam bzhag kho na dang 'brel bas stong gzugs kyi rten la 'tshang rgya zhes mi bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:3113: bar do'i rgya chen thob na sgyu lus kyi rten dang /
NK067(ju)004:3114: tshe 'dir thob na rags lus dwangs mar gyur pa'i rten la 'tshang rgya zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:3115: sgom lam bar nas bor te mthong lam nas mi
NK067(ju)004:3116: slob lam du 'gro ba'i lam thod rgal ba ni
NK067(ju)004:3118: phyag chen dang lhun grub bor te tshe dbang nas
NK067(ju)004:3119: 'tshang rgya ba yod par bshad pa sogs ni rdo
NK067(ju)004:3120: rje'i lus tha mal pa'i cha byad can sogs rig
NK067(ju)004:3121: 'dzin gyi lus rten mi 'dra ba gsum gyi steng
NK067(ju)004:3123: shin tu dbang rno kha cig 'gyur med kyi bde
NK067(ju)004:3124: ba'i skad cig ma thams cad dkyus thog gcig la
NK067(ju)004:3125: rdzogs pa lta bur 'dod dam gang yin dpyad par
NK067(ju)004:3126: bya'o // zhar byung kun mkhyen chos rje'i bzhed pa'ang bstan par bya ste /
NK067(ju)004:3127: rnam smin rig 'dzin ni sems yi dam gyi phyag rgyar smin pa'i mos spyod pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3129: rgya chen tsam ni 'phags lam gyi rtogs pa dang por thob pa nas dang /
NK067(ju)004:3131: lhun grub mi slob lam pa ste sems kyi rtogs pa la ltos nas bzhag pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3132: rnam smin gyi lus rten khyad par can sogs rig
NK067(ju)004:3133: 'dzin gyi lus la ltos nas 'jog pa'i tshul gnyis
NK067(ju)004:3134: te / tshe rgya gnyis lus dwangs mar gyur pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3135: sems 'phags lam thob pa'i cha nas rim bzhin 'jog
NK067(ju)004:3136: pas ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad du
NK067(ju)004:3137: gsungs pa dang / gnyis pa tshe dbang /
NK067(ju)004:3138: gsum pa phyag chen zhes pa mi 'gal tshul yang de'i steng nas go sla'o //
NK067(ju)004:3139: rnam smin pa la 'dir chos mchog thob nas tshe dbang la sbyor ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3140: chos mchog ma thob par shi nas bar dor phyag chen gyi sku 'thob pa gnyis te /
NK067(ju)004:3141: snga mas rig 'dzin bzhi ka 'thob cing /
NK067(ju)004:3142: phyi ma la gsum las mi 'thob bo //
NK067(ju)004:3143: de ltar gnyis yod pa bzhin du de dag gis thob pa'i mthong lam gnyis kyang khyad che bas /
NK067(ju)004:3144: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK067(ju)004:3145: sogs kyi lung don yang gnas so //
NK067(ju)004:3146: phyi ma 'dis thob pa'i mthong lam ni sems la
NK067(ju)004:3147: ltos te rgya chen rig 'dzin du rung yang lus
NK067(ju)004:3148: la ltos te rig 'dzin bzhi'i gang yang min no
NK067(ju)004:3149: // chos mchog ma thob par shi na bar dor
NK067(ju)004:3150: rgya chen grub pa'i rnam smin pa ni rdzogs rim
NK067(ju)004:3151: gyi rtogs pa cher byang ba dgos kyi /
NK067(ju)004:3152: bskyed rim brtan pa tsam min par sems te /
NK067(ju)004:3153: rnam smin rig 'dzin la mthong lam pa'i sgra sbyor
NK067(ju)004:3154: ba'ang rdzogs rim gyi lhag mthong rnyed pa yan chad
NK067(ju)004:3155: cig las gzhan la 'grigs dka' bas /
NK067(ju)004:3156: bskyed rim pa'i rnam smin 'jog na phal pa tsam du 'dod par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:3158: lus kyi rgya mdud grol gyur nas //
NK067(ju)004:3159: phyag rgya'i sku nyid gsal gyur pa //
NK067(ju)004:3160: rnam par smin zhes de la brjod //
NK067(ju)004:3161: ces sogs bshad pa rnams kyis kyang rnam smin rig
NK067(ju)004:3162: 'dzin shi nas bar dor phyag chen la sbyor ba
NK067(ju)004:3163: zhig ston yang / rnam smin rig 'dzin yin na
NK067(ju)004:3164: ma shi bar du phyag chen mi 'grub pas khyab
NK067(ju)004:3165: ces bstan par mi bzhed do //
NK067(ju)004:3166: tshe 'dir chos mchog thob ma thob ces pa ni
NK067(ju)004:3167: tshogs spyod byas ma byas la rig 'dzin 'jigs med
NK067(ju)004:3169: chos mchog nas tshe dbang rig 'dzin la sbyor tshul
NK067(ju)004:3170: mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba'i steng nas 'gro ba kun
NK067(ju)004:3171: mkhyen gyi bzhed par yang gnas pa ni sngar bshad
NK067(ju)004:3172: zin la / mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba'i ma mtha'i
NK067(ju)004:3173: mtshams la mos spyod mthon po nas 'jog pa sogs
NK067(ju)004:3174: bzhed pa mi 'dra ba yod kyang /
NK067(ju)004:3175: bde ba de'i skad cig dang po thob pa dang
NK067(ju)004:3176: 'phags lam gyi dang po brnyes pa dus mnyam pa'i
NK067(ju)004:3177: phyogs de kun mkhyen gyi dgongs par gnas te /
NK067(ju)004:3178: de'i rgyu mtshan dang lugs 'di kho na bzhin du
NK067(ju)004:3179: ma byas na lung rigs kyi gnod byed yod tshul
NK067(ju)004:3181: nges don shing rta chen po sogs las 'gyur med
NK067(ju)004:3182: kyi bde ba'i skad cig rnams kyi d+h+au ti'i rtsa
NK067(ju)004:3183: mdud 'jig par bshad pa'i don ni rtsa mdud dang
NK067(ju)004:3184: de 'jig tshul gzhan nas bshad pa dang mi 'dra
NK067(ju)004:3185: bar rtsa 'od du dengs pa la byed de /
NK067(ju)004:3186: de'i tshul yang ma spros so //
NK067(ju)004:3187: spyir sgyu 'phrul mkhan po snga rabs pa kha cig
NK067(ju)004:3188: rnam smin rig 'dzin lus 'di dang bral nas phyag
NK067(ju)004:3189: chen rig 'dzin du ma sleb pa'i skad cig de
NK067(ju)004:3191: de la nye ston chos seng gis /
NK067(ju)004:3193: zhes pa'i lung dang 'gal ba la sogs pa'i skyon brjod mdzad kyang /
NK067(ju)004:3194: 'chi ba'i snga rol du mthong lam thob pa la
NK067(ju)004:3195: rnam smin par 'jog pa rnams las 'di nyid zur
NK067(ju)004:3196: lugs gzhir bzhag la'ang bzang bar sems te /
NK067(ju)004:3197: snga ma ltar na de 'dra'i rnam smin pa des
NK067(ju)004:3198: slar mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba thob nas rgya chen
NK067(ju)004:3199: tshe 'dir 'grub pa'ang med par sgrub mi nus la
NK067(ju)004:3200: / de yod na ni rags lus 'di rgya chen
NK067(ju)004:3201: du 'khyer ba med pas rnam smin dang des thob
NK067(ju)004:3202: pa'i rgya chen sogs lhag med myang 'das dang /
NK067(ju)004:3203: tshe dbang dang des thob pa'i rgya chen sogs de
NK067(ju)004:3204: las ldog pas lhag bcas myang 'das su zur lugs
NK067(ju)004:3205: par rang gis bshad pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK067(ju)004:3206: stong gzugs ye shes kyi sku sngon nas grub cing
NK067(ju)004:3207: don gyi 'od gsal thob nas nyon sgrib zad par
NK067(ju)004:3208: spangs pa'i 'phags pa las kyis 'chi ba'i gzhan dbang
NK067(ju)004:3209: du 'gro ba sogs kyang khas len bzang bar ma
NK067(ju)004:3210: mthong la / lugs phyi ma 'di lta na /
NK067(ju)004:3211: sbyor lam tshogs sgrub pa la phyag rgya chen po'i
NK067(ju)004:3212: stobs kyis mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba grub nas mthong
NK067(ju)004:3214: de ma grub kyang 'chi ba'i stobs kyis 'thug po'i
NK067(ju)004:3215: 'od gsal gnyis snang gi spros pas mi shigs pa
NK067(ju)004:3216: thob ste mthong lam par 'gyur ba gnyis las snga
NK067(ju)004:3217: mas thob pa'i mthong lam pa de tshe dbang dang
NK067(ju)004:3218: / gnyis pa rnam smin rig 'dzin zhes bshad par 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)004:3219: de ltar byas tshe mthong lam pa phyi ma de
NK067(ju)004:3220: rnam shes lus las bsdus zin pas lugs dang bral
NK067(ju)004:3221: ba zhes gong du smos pa ltar yin yang bar
NK067(ju)004:3222: do la ma sleb bar du rnam smin gyi lus
NK067(ju)004:3223: la gnas shing lus las phyir ma thon pas rgya
NK067(ju)004:3224: chen la sgrib pa'i snyigs ma'i lus dang ma bral
NK067(ju)004:3225: ba zhes kyang brjod pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3226: sngar nas sems lha skur smin pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3227: gdon mi za bar bar do'i rten la rgya chen
NK067(ju)004:3228: 'thob pa ste sngar smos pa'i chos gsum tshang bar
NK067(ju)004:3229: ldan la / zag pa gsum ma zad pa'i don
NK067(ju)004:3230: ni lus rten snga ma'i 'byung ba snyigs ma'i cha
NK067(ju)004:3231: rnams ma dag par lus pa tsam la bya yi
NK067(ju)004:3232: ldan la / / da dung khams bde mi bde sogs dbang med du 'byung mi dgos te /
NK067(ju)004:3233: rnam smin rig 'dzin tshe 'dir thob par 'dod pa rnams kyi ltar na'ang /
NK067(ju)004:3234: de skye gnas kyi zag pa ma zad kyang bar
NK067(ju)004:3235: dor rgya chen du sbyor ba nges pas dbang med
NK067(ju)004:3236: du skye ba mi len pas khyab par bzhed pa
NK067(ju)004:3237: bzhin no // 'dis mthong lam brnyes kyang tha mal
NK067(ju)004:3238: pa'i rnam smin gyi lus rgya'i sbubs las ma 'phags
NK067(ju)004:3239: pas sgra bshad kyang mi 'jig go //
NK067(ju)004:3240: ci ste rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi 'jog tshul de ltar byed na ni /
NK067(ju)004:3242: lha yi rnal 'byor las rdzogs smin //
NK067(ju)004:3243: lus kyi dra bas bsgribs gyur pa //
NK067(ju)004:3244: zhes lus kyis bsgribs par bshad pa dang 'gal te /
NK067(ju)004:3245: 'chi ba'i 'od gsal la gnas pa yin na phung
NK067(ju)004:3246: khams rags pa'i d+r+wa bas ma bsgribs par 'dod rigs
NK067(ju)004:3247: pa'i phyir dang / dpag tshad gling khams yul la spyod //
NK067(ju)004:3248: ces mngon shes kyi yul don bshad pas kyang gnod cing /
NK067(ju)004:3249: smin pas phrin las rdzogs byed pas //
NK067(ju)004:3251: zhes phrin las bzhis gzhan don spyod pa mi 'dor
NK067(ju)004:3252: bar bshad pa'ang 'gog rigs par thal lo zhe na
NK067(ju)004:3254: dang po ni 'od gsal la bsgribs pa'i don min
NK067(ju)004:3255: zhing phung po phra rags kyi 'brel ba gtan chad
NK067(ju)004:3256: pa na gegs byas pa'i don dngos mi gnas kyang
NK067(ju)004:3257: rnam smin gyi lus snga ma las ma phyung bar
NK067(ju)004:3258: du sgyu ma'i skur mngon du mi 'gyur ba la
NK067(ju)004:3259: des sku de bsgribs par tha snyad byas pa yin
NK067(ju)004:3260: par / yid kyis lha yi gzugs bzung zhing //
NK067(ju)004:3261: lus kyi rgya mdud grol gyur nas //
NK067(ju)004:3262: phyag rgya'i sku nyid gsal gyur pa //
NK067(ju)004:3264: rgya mig rgya sa ji lta bar //
NK067(ju)004:3265: phyag rgya thob la ma rag pa'i //
NK067(ju)004:3267: gnyis pa mngon shes kyi nus pa thob tshul tsam la sbyar bas chog pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3268: gsum pa sems lha'i skur smin pas gzhan phan phrin
NK067(ju)004:3269: las kyi nus pa cher lhag pa'i sgo nas rnam
NK067(ju)004:3270: smin pa'i mnyam bzhag ye shes de zab gsal gnyis
NK067(ju)004:3271: med dang srid zhi'i mtha' gnyis 'gog pa'i rnal 'byor
NK067(ju)004:3272: du 'gro lugs ston pa tsam yin pa'i phyir te
NK067(ju)004:3273: / phyi ma 'di gnad shin tu che'o //
NK067(ju)004:3274: 'di lta bu'i tshul gyi bshad na zur lugs dang
NK067(ju)004:3275: kun mkhyen chos rje'i bzhed pa gnyis kyang rnam smin
NK067(ju)004:3276: rig 'dzin gyi mtshan gzhi ngos 'dzin la mi mthun
NK067(ju)004:3277: pa tsam dang / rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling pas
NK067(ju)004:3278: kun mkhyen gyi dgongs pa blangs pa dang bsgrigs tshe
NK067(ju)004:3279: phyag rgya gcig spros pas tshe 'dir tshe dbang rig
NK067(ju)004:3280: 'dzin mi 'thob pa'i rgyu mtshan tshogs spyod ma byas
NK067(ju)004:3281: pa tsam dang / pa dang / byas kyang dgos
NK067(ju)004:3282: pa ma grub pa la bzhed pa'i khyad par yang
NK067(ju)004:3283: pa tsam dang / pa dang / yod de /
NK067(ju)004:3284: de tsam ma gtos gnad kyi 'gangs gcig par snang
NK067(ju)004:3285: pa tsam dang / pa dang / yod de /
NK067(ju)004:3286: la / tshe 'dir mthong lam thob cig bar dor
NK067(ju)004:3287: rgya chen 'grub pa'i rnam smin rig 'dzin khas len
NK067(ju)004:3288: pa ltar na gnad mi mthun pa'i khyad par chen
NK067(ju)004:3289: pa tsam dang / pa dang / yod de /
NK067(ju)004:3290: la / po yod do // de la zur lugs
NK067(ju)004:3291: pa rnams ni rig 'dzin bzhi po 'di mtshan nyid
NK067(ju)004:3292: gsum las 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid du gsungs pas so
NK067(ju)004:3293: skye'i sar bzhag tu mi btub par dgongs te rnam
NK067(ju)004:3294: smin rig 'dzin yang 'phags lam pa kho nar 'jog
NK067(ju)004:3295: gi gnyug sems lha'i skur rdzogs pa tsam gyis 'jog
NK067(ju)004:3297: kun mkhyen ni rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub ces pa
NK067(ju)004:3298: phal cher gtso bor lus kyi dngos grub khyad par
NK067(ju)004:3299: can gyi steng nas 'jog pa rgyud sde gong 'og
NK067(ju)004:3301: sems lha skur smin pa zhes rdzogs rim gyi lha
NK067(ju)004:3302: sku thob pa nas rnam smin gyi lus gnas ma
NK067(ju)004:3303: gyur yang mchog gi dngos grub kyi phyogs su gtogs
NK067(ju)004:3304: pa'i rig 'dzin gyi sku brnyes pa yin pas rig
NK067(ju)004:3305: 'dzin bzhi'i dang por 'thad snyam du dgongs nas mos
NK067(ju)004:3306: spyod kyi sar gnas dang rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi
NK067(ju)004:3307: gzhi mthun zhal gyis bzhes pa yin ces bshad na
NK067(ju)004:3308: so so'i lugs la nges pa phrig tsam rnyed par
NK067(ju)004:3309: 'gyur ro // sems lha skur smin pa zhes pa'i sku 'di res sems kyi phyogs dang /
NK067(ju)004:3310: res lus kyi phyogs su bshad kyang 'gal ba med par shes par bya ste cung zad go sla'o //
NK067(ju)004:3311: gsum pa gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud ni /
NK067(ju)004:3312: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi'i steng gi sbyang
NK067(ju)004:3313: bya glo bur gyi dri ma rnams lam gyis bsal
NK067(ju)004:3314: bas gzhi ji lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur pa
NK067(ju)004:3317: grub pa mthar phyin 'bras bur brjod //
NK067(ju)004:3318: ces pa ltar bla na med pa'i go 'phang don
NK067(ju)004:3319: du gnyer ba rnams kyi bsam pa yongs su rdzogs
NK067(ju)004:3321: nam yang rgyun mi 'chad pas na rgyud ces bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:3322: theg chen pha rol tu phyin pa'i sde snod nas
NK067(ju)004:3323: kyang byang chub chen po'i 'bras bu rgyas par bstan
NK067(ju)004:3324: mod de / de dang sngags bla med nas bshad
NK067(ju)004:3325: pa'i sangs rgyas gnyis smon lam dang tshogs gnyis kyi
NK067(ju)004:3327: rang bzhin gzhi rgyud kyi gnas tshod ji lta ba bzhin mngon du mdzad pa'i khyad che zhing /
NK067(ju)004:3328: gsang sngags thun min gyi lam la ma brten par
NK067(ju)004:3329: de'i thun min gyi 'bras bu 'grub pa mi 'thad
NK067(ju)004:3330: pas mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin tsam la sangs
NK067(ju)004:3331: rgyas su btags pa yin gyi /
NK067(ju)004:3332: sngags lam gyi sangs rgyas dngos ni de'i phyi nas
NK067(ju)004:3333: 'thob dgos so zhes dpal ldan zur ba'i srol 'dzin
NK067(ju)004:3335: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po yang mdo phyogs nas
NK067(ju)004:3336: bshad pa'i sangs rgyas dang rgyud 'di'i lhun grub rig
NK067(ju)004:3338: lhun grub mthar thug gi sa la mdzad pas dgongs pa mi gcig ste /
NK067(ju)004:3340: chos thams cad rnam pa thams cad du mngon par
NK067(ju)004:3341: byang chub pa'i sangs rgyas mdo phyogs nas kyang shin
NK067(ju)004:3343: de ltar mngon par byang chub pa ni glo bur
NK067(ju)004:3344: ba'i sems kyis bsgrub gzhi byas pa la mi srid
NK067(ju)004:3345: pas bla med kyi lam la nges par brten dgos
NK067(ju)004:3346: te / de'i phyir theg pa gnyis kyi thob bya'i
NK067(ju)004:3347: sangs rgyas gcig yin kyang mdo lam rkyang pas 'thob
NK067(ju)004:3349: yi ges 'jigs pas rgya ma bskyed do //
NK067(ju)004:3351: spyir grags pa'i stobs bcu mi 'jigs sogs dang /
NK067(ju)004:3352: bla med kho na la grags pa'i kha sbyor yan
NK067(ju)004:3353: lag bdun sogs mang du yod kyang rgyud gzhung 'di
NK067(ju)004:3354: nyid kyi dbang du byas na 'bras chos nyer lnga
NK067(ju)004:3355: ste / dang po sku lnga ni /
NK067(ju)004:3356: dbyings la rig pa phyogs med du grol ba chos sku dang /
NK067(ju)004:3357: de las ma g.yos bzhin du byang sems 'phags pa
NK067(ju)004:3358: rnams la theg pa mchog gi chos kyi longs spyod
NK067(ju)004:3359: rdzog par ston pa longs sku /
NK067(ju)004:3360: gdul bya dag ma dag thun mong gi snang ngor
NK067(ju)004:3361: bzo dang skye ba mchog gi gzugs su ston pa
NK067(ju)004:3362: sprul sku / de gsum dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje'i sku /
NK067(ju)004:3363: sku gsum snang cha ma 'dres pa mngon byang gi sku'o //
NK067(ju)004:3365: bsam brjod dang bral ba'i dbyings la rtag tu mnyam
NK067(ju)004:3366: par bzhag pa'i ye shes nyid brjod pa thams cad
NK067(ju)004:3367: kyi gzhir gyur pa'i cha nas chos sku skye med
NK067(ju)004:3368: don gyi gsung / mthong ba tsam gyis 'khor rnams
NK067(ju)004:3369: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas la 'jug
NK067(ju)004:3370: pa'i cha nas longs sku'i sku de dgongs pa brda'i
NK067(ju)004:3371: don gyi gsung / gsung / skad cig rer yang
NK067(ju)004:3372: gdul bya so so'i skad du chos tshad med pa
NK067(ju)004:3373: ston pa sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung /
NK067(ju)004:3374: ji tsam gsung yang gzhom med ye shes kyi rang
NK067(ju)004:3375: sgra las gzhan du mi 'gyur ba dbyer med rdo
NK067(ju)004:3376: rje'i gsung / ye shes gcig nyid sgra dbyangs kyi
NK067(ju)004:3377: rnam pa thams cad du 'char ba mngon byang rig
NK067(ju)004:3378: pa byin rlabs kyi gsung ste phyi ma gnyis po'i
NK067(ju)004:3379: rje'i gsung / khyad ni / du ma gcig tu 'du ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3380: gcig nyid du mar 'char ba'i ldog cha nas so //
NK067(ju)004:3381: dgongs brgyud kho na la sbyar na sngar sngon byung
NK067(ju)004:3382: dngos lnga'i thad du bshad pa ltar yang rung mod
NK067(ju)004:3383: de / le'u bdun pa rtsa 'grel gyi dngos bstan ni bshad ma thag pa nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:3385: chos dbyings ye shes chos sku rnam par mi rtog pa'i thugs /
NK067(ju)004:3386: mnyam nyid ye shes longs sku mnyam pa chen po'i thugs /
NK067(ju)004:3387: bya grub ye shes sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thugs /
NK067(ju)004:3388: sor rtog ye shes mi phyed rdo rje'i thugs /
NK067(ju)004:3389: me long ye shes mngon byang cir yang gsal ba'i thugs so //
NK067(ju)004:3391: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams /
NK067(ju)004:3392: rgya tshad bral ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK067(ju)004:3395: dgyes dgur spyod pa'i longs spyod rnams so //
NK067(ju)004:3397: tshe 'di phyi'i sdug bsngal rgyur bcas zhi ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3399: sa gsum gyi gdul bya dbang du mdzad pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3400: shin tu gdul dka' rnams drag pos tshar bcad pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3401: de dag thams cad dus dang gdul ba'i dbang bzhin
NK067(ju)004:3402: rtsol med du 'byung ba lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin
NK067(ju)004:3405: mdzad pa phrin las kyi rnam bzhag rnams kyang de dag tu 'dus so /
NK067(ju)004:3406: don gnyis pa lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bcu bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)004:3407: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsang chen rgyud sde'i rnam grangs
NK067(ju)004:3408: ji snyed cig bstan pa thams cad ston pa rang
NK067(ju)004:3409: nyid lam gang nas gshegs pa de nyid nas gdul
NK067(ju)004:3410: bya mchog rnams 'khrid pa'i ched kho na yin pas
NK067(ju)004:3411: rgyud kyi brjod bya'i gtso bo lam rgyud yin la
NK067(ju)004:3412: / de nyid lam gyi khog dbub tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3413: de'i cha rkyen du dgos pa'i rgyud don gyi dngos
NK067(ju)004:3414: po bye brag tu phye nas bstan pa gnyis kyis
NK067(ju)004:3416: dang po thabs grol gyi lam sngar brjod pa rnams yin zhing /
NK067(ju)004:3422: phrin las te gzhi lnga dang /
NK067(ju)004:3426: mchod pa dang yan lag bzhi ste shes bya la
NK067(ju)004:3427: mkhas bya'i rgyud don gyi dngos po dgur lo ts+aa
NK067(ju)004:3428: ba chen po rong zom gsungs la /
NK067(ju)004:3429: spar khab las gzhi lnga po de'i steng du lta
NK067(ju)004:3430: spyod gnyis bsnan nas dngos po bdun du bshad kyang
NK067(ju)004:3431: / 'dir de kho na nyid lta ba /
NK067(ju)004:3437: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa /
NK067(ju)004:3439: gnas su stobs pa mchod pa /
NK067(ju)004:3440: 'ching zlos sngags dang phyag rgya ste bcur 'chad par mdzad de /
NK067(ju)004:3441: de'ang lam gyi khog sngar bshad pa de la dbang dang dam tshig sogs kha bskang nas dang /
NK067(ju)004:3442: ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pa sogs gsal bar phye ba'i tshul gyis 'chad par shes par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:3443: 'di dag la nyams su len byed lam gyi rim pa bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3444: blang bya rgyud kyi dngos po bshad pa zhes kyang 'byung ngo //
NK067(ju)004:3446: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam gong 'og thams cad la
NK067(ju)004:3447: lta ba khyab byed du 'jug pas lam gyi rim
NK067(ju)004:3448: pa la ltos nas lta ba'i grangs dgur dbye ste
NK067(ju)004:3450: mnyam nyid ngang la mi skrag pas //
NK067(ju)004:3451: mngon byas nges pa'i shes rab dang //
NK067(ju)004:3452: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK067(ju)004:3453: rang rig ye shes snying rjes gzigs //
NK067(ju)004:3454: phyag rgya gcig sku 'bras bur blta //
NK067(ju)004:3455: thams cad gsal ba'i lta ba dang //
NK067(ju)004:3456: bar chad med pa'i tshogs chen mthong //
NK067(ju)004:3457: dbang bsgyur mnyam nyid mi g.yo ba //
NK067(ju)004:3458: ye shes kun mkhyen lta ba dgu //
NK067(ju)004:3460: gzhan yang rgyud kyi dngos po rnams la lta ba
NK067(ju)004:3461: khyab byed dam zin byed du 'jug pa la ltos
NK067(ju)004:3462: nas lta ba'i grangs dgu dang /
NK067(ju)004:3463: tshogs drug gi spyod yul thams cad lta ba'i rgyas 'debs pa la ltos nas drug dang /
NK067(ju)004:3464: dbang po rab 'bring tha ma'i rtogs tshul la ltos nas gsum du dbye ba sogs yod cing /
NK067(ju)004:3465: gtan la 'bebs tshul rgyas par sngar bshad zin to //
NK067(ju)004:3467: spyir spyod pa la mnyam rjes gnyis ka yod kyang
NK067(ju)004:3468: 'dir spyi ming phyogs gcig la btags nas mnyam bzhag
NK067(ju)004:3469: gi rtogs pa'i grogs su gyur pa'i sgo gsum gyi
NK067(ju)004:3470: spyod pa rjes thob kyis bsdus pa gtso bor gyur
NK067(ju)004:3471: pa ste / de la spyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3474: las dang po pa'i dus su dge sbyong gzhon nu
NK067(ju)004:3475: ltar bag dang ldan par spyod pa zhes lam sgrub
NK067(ju)004:3476: pa'i 'gal rkyen 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad sogs las
NK067(ju)004:3478: yi ge 'bri mchod sbyin pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:3479: nyan dang klog dang 'dzin pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:3480: 'chad dang kha ton byed pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:3481: don sems pa dang sgom pa ste //
NK067(ju)004:3482: spyod pa 'di bcu'i bdag nyid ni //
NK067(ju)004:3483: bsod nams phung po dpag tu med //
NK067(ju)004:3484: ces pa'i chos spyod bcu la mang du gnas pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3485: de nas cung zad goms pa na rtogs pa rkyen
NK067(ju)004:3486: thub tu rtsal sbyong ba ro snyoms smyon pa'i brtul
NK067(ju)004:3487: zhugs dang / shin tu goms nas rkyen bzang ngan
NK067(ju)004:3488: gang gis kyang rtogs pa bri gang med pa na
NK067(ju)004:3489: rang babs su gzhan phan byed pa rgyal po sa
NK067(ju)004:3490: 'dzin gyi spyod pa lta bu ste spyir bshad pa'o
NK067(ju)004:3493: thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa gnyis /
NK067(ju)004:3494: dang po la rim gyis pa dang cig char ba'i spyod pa gnyis /
NK067(ju)004:3496: dang po dad brtson gyi spyod pa zhes shes pa'i mtshan nyid tshol dus kyi spyod pa 'di la /
NK067(ju)004:3497: gzhi dam tshig gis bzung ba /
NK067(ju)004:3500: phul du mkhas pas dbyung ba /
NK067(ju)004:3502: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba /
NK067(ju)004:3504: rim pa dbang gis bgrod pa /
NK067(ju)004:3505: don man ngag gi sgrub pa /
NK067(ju)004:3506: mdo don gcig tu bsdu ba la bslab pa ste bslab pa'i mtha' bcu'o //
NK067(ju)004:3507: de'ang lta ba thog mar 'tshol dus nas lam yongs
NK067(ju)004:3508: rdzogs dmigs 'og tu bcug nas skabs don la gtso
NK067(ju)004:3509: bor byed pa yin pas de ltar gsungs kyi /
NK067(ju)004:3510: skabs don gtso bo'i dbang du btang na rgyud thos pas dgrol ba sogs bzhi po nyid do //
NK067(ju)004:3511: gnyis pa shes rab dang mthun pa zhes stong chen
NK067(ju)004:3512: gyi dus su thun mtshams kyi bya ba thams cad
NK067(ju)004:3513: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyi rtsal sbyong du 'khyer
NK067(ju)004:3514: ba dang / gsum pa thabs dang mthun pa zhes
NK067(ju)004:3515: snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs su snang spyod ye shes
NK067(ju)004:3516: sgyu ma'i yo lang du blta ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3517: bzhi pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i dus su phyogs gcig pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3518: lnga pa spros bcas kyi tshe spros bcas kyi spyod
NK067(ju)004:3519: pa zhes mnyam bzhag tu gang bsgom gyi lha'i ting
NK067(ju)004:3520: nge 'dzin des snang ba thams cad la rgyas btab
NK067(ju)004:3521: ste log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba zil gyis gnon
NK067(ju)004:3522: pa dang / drug pa tshogs kyi spyod pa zhes
NK067(ju)004:3523: tshogs sgrub kyi dus su dag mnyam bde ba chen
NK067(ju)004:3524: po'i rnal 'byor khor yug tu skyong ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3525: bdun pa zag med rig 'dzin thob nas rdzu 'phrul
NK067(ju)004:3526: gyi spyod pa zhes nus mthu thogs pa med pa'i
NK067(ju)004:3527: phrin las kyis gzhan don rlabs po che spyod cing
NK067(ju)004:3528: rang rgyud kyi rtogs pa gong du spor ba'o //
NK067(ju)004:3530: rjes thob tu yang snang sems gang shar thams cad
NK067(ju)004:3531: la brten nas lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med kyi
NK067(ju)004:3532: dgongs pa'i rtsal phyogs med du sbyong ba'o //
NK067(ju)004:3534: skrag pa dang dogs pa dang ngo tsha ba la
NK067(ju)004:3535: sogs pa'i rnam rtog thams cad bshig nas sha lnga
NK067(ju)004:3536: dang bdud rtsi lnga dang bud med la sogs pa'i
NK067(ju)004:3537: yul thams cad la bde ba chen po'i man ngag
NK067(ju)004:3538: gi gding dang ldan pas ci dgar longs spyod pa'o
NK067(ju)004:3539: // phyi ma 'dir yul gang la spyod kyang rang
NK067(ju)004:3540: bzhin dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin las skad cig kyang
NK067(ju)004:3541: mi g.yo ba gnad du bzung dgos pas bla na
NK067(ju)004:3542: med pa'i bag yod kyi spyod pa yin yang chags
NK067(ju)004:3543: yul dang skyug bro ba'i gnas sogs gang la'ang 'dzem
NK067(ju)004:3544: pa spangs pa 'di lta bu grol lam gyi dus
NK067(ju)004:3545: su rtsal 'don mi byed pas brtul zhugs kyi dang
NK067(ju)004:3546: bag yod kyi spyod pa zhes so sor sbyar ro
NK067(ju)004:3548: bkod pa lha'i 'khor lo rdzogs par snang ba la bshad de thugs thig las so //
NK067(ju)004:3549: de la chos don las rang bzhin dang /
NK067(ju)004:3551: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:3552: rgyud phyi ma las sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:3553: 'grel chung las dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis su bshad pa
NK067(ju)004:3554: sogs yod kyang brgyud pa'i bka' srol du rgyas pa
NK067(ju)004:3555: las / 'dis ni rang bzhin dkyil 'khor dang //
NK067(ju)004:3556: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK067(ju)004:3558: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK067(ju)004:3559: zhes gsungs pa ltar dkyil 'khor bdun du 'chad par mdzad de /
NK067(ju)004:3560: de la dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK067(ju)004:3561: khog gzhung las gsum du gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:3562: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas rnam par dag pa'i dbyings rang bzhin nyid kyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3563: rtog tshogs thams cad kyi snang gzhi ye shes lha'i
NK067(ju)004:3564: dkyil 'khor du gnas pa rang bzhin lhun grub kyi
NK067(ju)004:3565: dang / rtogs pa mngon du gyur te 'og min
NK067(ju)004:3566: du sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med par bzhugs
NK067(ju)004:3567: pa rang bzhin 'bras bu thar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)004:3568: dang / ro // gnyis pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)004:3569: don dam pa'i gzugs brnyan kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor rtog pa phra rags kyi rnam par shar ba'o //
NK067(ju)004:3570: gsum pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan ni /
NK067(ju)004:3571: dgos pa la ltos nas dbang gi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3574: phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor dang bzhi ste gang yang
NK067(ju)004:3575: rdul tshon sogs las dkyil 'khor gyi gzugs su bzhengs
NK067(ju)004:3576: pa'o // de'ang dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga'i las rim
NK067(ju)004:3577: mang pos lhag pas na lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi
NK067(ju)004:3581: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK067(ju)004:3582: tshon dang bri dang rnam pa dang //
NK067(ju)004:3583: rab gnas sbyin sreg dkyil 'khor du //
NK067(ju)004:3584: 'jug dang zhugs pa'i yon tan no //
NK067(ju)004:3592: sa gzung ba dang bdun sa gzhi mnyam pa zhes gcig tu bgrang ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3593: dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus pa gang byed kyi tshad nges pa can du bya ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3600: nyes spang dang bdun la thig chog ces gcig tu byas pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3605: nyes spang ste tshon gyi cho ga lnga dang /
NK067(ju)004:3606: rten gyi dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus pa gang rung
NK067(ju)004:3607: du 'bri ba dang lha'i mtshan ma sku dang yig
NK067(ju)004:3608: 'bru phyag mtshan ci rigs kyi rnam pa dgod pa
NK067(ju)004:3609: dang / bum pa dang slob ma dkyil 'khor gsum rab tu gnas pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3611: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing slob ma gzhug pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3612: zhugs pa'i yon tan rnams te /
NK067(ju)004:3613: de dag kyang slob ma la dbang bskur ba'i ched
NK067(ju)004:3614: du yin na lam mos sgom gyi tshul gyis grangs
NK067(ju)004:3615: dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa gang rung rdzogs pa dang
NK067(ju)004:3616: / tshogs sgrub kyi ched yin na nges rdzogs kyi
NK067(ju)004:3617: spros bcas man chad brtan pa'i slob dpon gyis bya
NK067(ju)004:3618: / ba yin no // bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)004:3619: dngos snang thams cad mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su bsdus
NK067(ju)004:3620: te rig pa ma bcos pa'i ngang la rtse gcig
NK067(ju)004:3622: lnga pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)004:3623: mtshan bcas lha sku sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK067(ju)004:3624: bskyed chog gi bya ba mang pos lhag pas lhag pa zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:3627: bdud 'dul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi ting nge 'dzin gnyis yod /
NK067(ju)004:3628: 'di dag gi las rim yang zur tsam brjod na /
NK067(ju)004:3629: sngon 'gro dngos gzhi rjes kyi rim pa dang gsum /
NK067(ju)004:3637: mchod pa byin brlab ste las bdun no //
NK067(ju)004:3639: khyad par gyi sems bskyed pas mtshams sbyar nas bskyed chog dngos la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)004:3640: 'di ni lhag ting gi sgom don gtso bo yin pas cung zad bshad par bya ste /
NK067(ju)004:3644: las rim gyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK067(ju)004:3646: de bzhin nyid stong pa chen po dang /
NK067(ju)004:3647: kun snang snying rje sgyu ma dang /
NK067(ju)004:3648: rgyu'i ting 'dzin rtsa ba'i a dang de las a
NK067(ju)004:3649: sogs yi ge phra mo'i spro bsdu la dmigs pa
NK067(ju)004:3652: brten pa sgom pa gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK067(ju)004:3655: gdan bskyed pa rnams te sgrub thabs bzhin no //
NK067(ju)004:3659: dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:3661: spyir lugs gsum las rgyud 'grel nyi seng ma ltar na /
NK067(ju)004:3663: yud tsam gyis kun tu bzang por bsgoms nas 'og
NK067(ju)004:3664: gi phyogs su ye shes kyi sa gzhi nas bzung
NK067(ju)004:3665: gzhal yas khang gdan bcas bskyed /
NK067(ju)004:3666: de las nyi zla'i gdan la sems skyil gyis 'dug
NK067(ju)004:3667: par mos la byang chub kyi sems ye shes su
NK067(ju)004:3668: bskyed pa'i don gyis stong nyid ye shes /
NK067(ju)004:3669: de'i ngang las rang sems a'i ngo bor bsgoms nas
NK067(ju)004:3670: spro bsdus a las zla ba la mtshan gyi sa
NK067(ju)004:3672: +aa ring las nyi ma la dpe byad kyi sa
NK067(ju)004:3673: bon ka li nyis rim du 'god pa me long
NK067(ju)004:3674: ye shes / de dag 'od kyi gong bu gcig tu 'dril ba mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK067(ju)004:3675: 'od kyi gong bu de las h'u du gyur nas
NK067(ju)004:3676: de'i rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu rdo rjer byin gyis
NK067(ju)004:3677: rlob pa sor rtog ye shes /
NK067(ju)004:3678: de yongs su gyur pa las kun tu bzang po'i
NK067(ju)004:3679: skur bskyed pa bya grub ye shes te cho ga
NK067(ju)004:3680: lnga'o // de nas yum bskyed de byang chub sems
NK067(ju)004:3681: sprin las lha so so'i sku bskyed pa rang rang
NK067(ju)004:3682: gi sngags kyis phyir phyung nas dkyil 'khor du 'god
NK067(ju)004:3683: lnga'o // par mdzad do // bi ma la'i lha
NK067(ju)004:3684: sku sgom pa'i man ngag ltar na gong du bshad
NK067(ju)004:3685: pa'i rgyu'i yi ge las yi ge zhe gnyis spros
NK067(ju)004:3686: te so so'i gdan la bkod nas rgyu'i a nyid
NK067(ju)004:3687: de rnams la bstim zhing spro bsdu bya ba yig
NK067(ju)004:3688: lnga'o // par mdzad do // 'bru'i cho ga /
NK067(ju)004:3689: yi ge rnams zhu ba rdo rje dang 'khor lo
NK067(ju)004:3690: sogs phyag mtshan zhe gnyis su gyur pa las spro
NK067(ju)004:3691: bsdu bya ba phyag mtshan gyi cho ga /
NK067(ju)004:3692: phyag mtshan rnams yongs su gyur pa las dang so
NK067(ju)004:3693: so'i bskyed sngags brjod pa las rgyal ba bzhi bcu
NK067(ju)004:3694: rtsa gnyis kyi skur bskyed pa sku rdzogs pa'i cho
NK067(ju)004:3695: ga ste rdo rje gsum gyi cho gas bskyed pa
NK067(ju)004:3696: da lta'i phyag bzhes su ji ltar 'byung ba bzhin
NK067(ju)004:3697: no // d+r+wa ba che chung gi lugs ni sras gnyis kyi cho gas bskyed pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:3698: de la bdag sras ni cho ga gsum gyis lha zhe gnyis bskyed pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:3700: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas bdag nyid 'khor ba'i lus
NK067(ju)004:3701: 'dzin pa zhig shar sgor thon nas gsol ba btab
NK067(ju)004:3702: pas lha rnams kyi sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems
NK067(ju)004:3703: kyi 'od zer 'phros te bdag gi lus rtog sbyangs
NK067(ju)004:3704: pas 'od kyi gong bur gyur pa la slar yang
NK067(ju)004:3705: rdo rje gsum gyi 'od zer bstims pas yi ge
NK067(ju)004:3706: gsum dang de yang h'u du bsgyur /
NK067(ju)004:3707: de nyid zla ba'i steng du bzhag pa rlung dkyil
NK067(ju)004:3708: gyis btegs nas lha tshogs rnams la bskor ba lan
NK067(ju)004:3709: gsum byas te gtso bo'i thugs kar thim /
NK067(ju)004:3710: yab yum rol pa'i rjes chags kyis byang sems su zhu ba sku'i dbyibs brgyud /
NK067(ju)004:3711: yum mkhar ba babs pa'i rkyen gyis gtso bo yab yum 'od du zhu /
NK067(ju)004:3712: 'khor rnams kyang bde ba chen por zhu ste dbus
NK067(ju)004:3713: kyi thig ler thim pas 'od kyi gong bu gcig
NK067(ju)004:3714: tu gyur / de nyid kyang h'u m+aum du gyur
NK067(ju)004:3715: pa las cho ga gsum gyis rdor sems yab yum
NK067(ju)004:3716: tu gyur / bskyed / snyoms par zhugs nas yum mkhar spro ba gsum gyi dang pos thig gdab /
NK067(ju)004:3717: gnyis pas gzhal yas khang gdan bcas su rlob /
NK067(ju)004:3718: gsum pas sa bon gyi yi ge bskyed cing de
NK067(ju)004:3719: dag rang rang gi sngags kyis lhar bskyed nas mdun
NK067(ju)004:3720: mkhar bton / yi ge gsum gyis sku brtas par bya /
NK067(ju)004:3721: spro bsdus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrub ste mi bskyod pa gtso bo la bstim /
NK067(ju)004:3722: gzhan rnams rang rang gi gnas su dgod par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:3725: rang byung dngos dang mi 'gal zhing //
NK067(ju)004:3726: 'bras bu nyid la lam shes pas //
NK067(ju)004:3727: ma lus dkyil 'khor thig le rnams //
NK067(ju)004:3728: bdag gi sras su bsgom par bya //
NK067(ju)004:3730: gang gis gang la gsol btab pas //
NK067(ju)004:3731: thugs rjes byin brlabsa sbyangs byas nas //
NK067(ju)004:3732: thugs zhugs 'dres nas dbyer med pa //
NK067(ju)004:3733: sras gyur dgongs pa gcig la gnas //
NK067(ju)004:3735: lam dang 'bras bu'i khyad par las //
NK067(ju)004:3736: rtog pa'i ye shes 'od las byung //
NK067(ju)004:3738: bde bar gshegs pa'i sras tshogs bsgom //
NK067(ju)004:3740: de'ang bdag sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir bdag
NK067(ju)004:3741: gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya ba dang
NK067(ju)004:3742: / rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya
NK067(ju)004:3743: ba'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya
NK067(ju)004:3744: ba zhes chen po rnams gsungs pa ltar shes par
NK067(ju)004:3745: / bya'o // de'i don yang sems kyi gnyug ma'i gnas tshul ni sangs rgyas yin la /
NK067(ju)004:3746: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gang bsgom kyang de nyid gzhir bzung ste sgom pa las ma 'das shing /
NK067(ju)004:3747: de ltar bsgoms pas gnyug ma las gnyis med gnyis
NK067(ju)004:3748: ltar snang ba'i glo bur gyi phung po'i cha rnams
NK067(ju)004:3749: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du bstims nas
NK067(ju)004:3750: slar shin tu rnam dag gi phung khams kyi cha
NK067(ju)004:3751: las mi bskyod pa sogs rgyal ba sras dang btsun
NK067(ju)004:3752: mor bcas pa rang 'char ba ni lam rim pa
NK067(ju)004:3753: gnyis ka'i khog sdom yin la /
NK067(ju)004:3754: de ltar 'bras bu'i sangs rgyas lam du gang byed
NK067(ju)004:3755: gzhir gnas gdod ma'i sangs rgyas kyi gdung rigs las
NK067(ju)004:3757: dri bcas gnas lugs kyi gzhi de 'bras bu lam
NK067(ju)004:3758: byed kyi gdung sras su bzung bas byang chub kyi
NK067(ju)004:3759: 'bras bu 'grub pa'i rgyu mtshan 'di'i phyir bdag gi
NK067(ju)004:3760: sras su sangs rgyas dang sangs rgyas kyi sras bdag
NK067(ju)004:3761: byed pa yin te rgya mtsho'i lung don yang 'dis
NK067(ju)004:3762: shes so // dam pa rgyan las sras kyi cho
NK067(ju)004:3763: ga khro bo'i bskyed chog tu sbyar nas bshad pa'ang
NK067(ju)004:3764: khog 'di nyid yin te yi ges 'jigs nas ma
NK067(ju)004:3765: shes so // bkod do // gnyis pa ni /
NK067(ju)004:3771: 'od zer sogs te le'u drug pa bzhin no //
NK067(ju)004:3773: byin rlabs dang dbang bskur gyi sngags dang ting nge
NK067(ju)004:3774: 'dzin le'u bdun pa rtsa 'grel las 'byung ba bzhin
NK067(ju)004:3776: ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drang zhing bstims nas mchod pa dbul ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3786: spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)004:3788: snang srid thams cad gdod nas dag pa lha'i rang
NK067(ju)004:3789: bzhin du gnas pa la spyi dmigs nas sgom pa
NK067(ju)004:3791: rang gis mngon par 'dod pa'i dkyil 'khor gang yin
NK067(ju)004:3792: la bye brag tu dmigs nas sgom pa lhag ting
NK067(ju)004:3794: 'dis ni lhag pa zhes pa gtso bor ram khyad
NK067(ju)004:3795: par du zhes pa'i steng nas 'chad par mngon no
NK067(ju)004:3796: // drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)004:3798: rdo rje'i lus la rtsa dbu rkyang ro gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:3799: dbu ma las gyes pa'i spyo bo bde chen /
NK067(ju)004:3802: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rnams dang /
NK067(ju)004:3804: gshang kha rlung gi 'khor lo rnams dang /
NK067(ju)004:3806: yan lag gi rlung lnga dang /
NK067(ju)004:3807: de dag gi 'pho ba bcu drug la sogs pa'i rnam bzhag sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho dang /
NK067(ju)004:3808: gsang ba'i snying po khro bo stobs kyi rgyud dang /
NK067(ju)004:3809: dbang gi galpo la sogs pa las gsungs par bshad la /
NK067(ju)004:3810: rgyud 'di'i sgos chos su che long tsam 'byung ba ni /
NK067(ju)004:3811: snying ga'i 'khor lor chos nyid kyi rtsa gsum /
NK067(ju)004:3814: yon tan gyi rtsa gcig rnams 'od bzhi dbyibs bzhir bcas pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3815: de dag gi dbus na dwangs ma lnga'i thig le dang /
NK067(ju)004:3818: spyi bo na bdud rtsi'i thig le /
NK067(ju)004:3819: dbyings phyug lnga'i thig le sogs kyi ming can yod
NK067(ju)004:3820: tshul thal rgyud dbang gis galpo dang gsang thig sogs
NK067(ju)004:3822: bdun pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK067(ju)004:3826: dgyes ldan lha'i tshogs gsum tshig zin dang /
NK067(ju)004:3827: sogs sgras bstan pa tshogs chen po ste bzhir bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:3829: rnal 'byor mchog dang ldan pa'i skye bo pho mo tshogs shing 'dus pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:3831: skye bo mdza' ba kun tshogs pa //
NK067(ju)004:3835: khyad par gyi yo byad lnga la sogs pa tshogs pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:3837: rnal 'byor yo byad tshang bas ni //
NK067(ju)004:3838: bde ba longs spyod tshogs su bshad //
NK067(ju)004:3842: lha dang dam can kun 'dus pa //
NK067(ju)004:3843: 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs su bshad //
NK067(ju)004:3845: tshogs 'di dngos ni ye shes lha'i dkyil 'khor sprul pa phyag brnyan dang bcas pa yin la /
NK067(ju)004:3846: btags pa dngos grub kyi rten du de dag gi gzugs brnyan bkod pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3847: sems kyis btags nas bsgom pa'ang yin no //
NK067(ju)004:3849: bdag dang tshogs kyi longs spyod thams cad ye shes
NK067(ju)004:3850: kyi rol par shes nas spyad pas bsod nams dang
NK067(ju)004:3851: / sbyong bzhin du mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyis
NK067(ju)004:3852: zin pas ye shes kyi tshogs gong nas gong du
NK067(ju)004:3853: / rdzogs pa ste / de nyid las /
NK067(ju)004:3854: thams cad spyod la mi 'dzin pa //
NK067(ju)004:3855: tshogs gnyis rgyud du rdzogs byed pas //
NK067(ju)004:3856: tshogs chen por ni nges par bshad //
NK067(ju)004:3858: tshogs dkyil zhes pa'i tshogs kyi rnam grangs de ltar yod kyang tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dngos ni /
NK067(ju)004:3859: dkyil 'khor gyi khang par rten gyi dkyil 'khor tshul bzhin du bris te /
NK067(ju)004:3860: der lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i tshogs sgrub kyi rnal
NK067(ju)004:3861: 'byor pa rnams lha'i chas su zhugs te gtso bo'i
NK067(ju)004:3862: lha gnas su rdo rje slob dpon yab yum dang
NK067(ju)004:3863: 'khor gyi lha gnas su 'khor gyi rnal 'byor pho
NK067(ju)004:3864: mo brang sprad du 'dug pa'am 'dug par mos pa
NK067(ju)004:3866: de la'ang rnam 'byor pa so so'i lha so sor nga rgyal bzhag nas sgrub pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3867: rnal 'byor pa re re zhing gtso bo'i nga rgyal
NK067(ju)004:3868: la gnas te sgrub pa'i tshul gnyis yod par gsungs
NK067(ju)004:3869: so // de la rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang
NK067(ju)004:3870: po gnyis ni lhag pa don dam pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)004:3871: so // dang / phyi ma gcig ni de bsgrub
NK067(ju)004:3872: gzhi mthar thug tu bzung ste 'bras bu lam byed
NK067(ju)004:3874: gzugs brnyan ni lhag pa kun rdzob kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)004:3875: lhag pa gzug brnyan ni gang du zhugs na kun
NK067(ju)004:3876: rdzob ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor der zhugs par 'gyur
NK067(ju)004:3878: ting nge 'dzin ni stong phyogs kyi dkyil 'khor sgom pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK067(ju)004:3879: lhag ting ni snang phyogs kyi dkyil 'khor sgom pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK067(ju)004:3880: byang sems ni rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)004:3881: la dngos su 'jug pa'i phyir gnas du bsnun pa'i
NK067(ju)004:3882: yul dang / tshogs dkyil ni dngos grub mchog gi
NK067(ju)004:3883: don du sgrub pa po ya gyal nyung ngu'i nus
NK067(ju)004:3884: pa la mang po tshogs pa'i nus pas stongs gdab
NK067(ju)004:3885: pa'am gtso bor bde chen gyi kun spyod gcig pa'i
NK067(ju)004:3886: grogs mang po la brten nas ye shes phyogs med
NK067(ju)004:3890: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhis yan lag bsnyad //
NK067(ju)004:3891: drug la gnas pa'i thob bya de //
NK067(ju)004:3892: ngo bo nyid ces rnam par bshad //
NK067(ju)004:3894: rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi tshogs pa la brten nas
NK067(ju)004:3895: go 'phang gi chos rgyud la 'jog pa'i las kyis
NK067(ju)004:3896: ye shes dngos su skyes pa'am skye nges kyi nus
NK067(ju)004:3899: rtsa rgyud du phan nus zab mo'i dbang gsum gsungs
NK067(ju)004:3900: pa bshad rgyud rdo rje las lngar phye nas gsungs
NK067(ju)004:3901: te / dang po sa bon 'jog pa ste //
NK067(ju)004:3902: gnyis pa nus pa bskyed pa yin //
NK067(ju)004:3903: gsum pa nyams myong skyed pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:3904: bzhi pas de nyid brtan par byed //
NK067(ju)004:3905: lnga pas brtan pa nyams lon pas //
NK067(ju)004:3909: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang /
NK067(ju)004:3910: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK067(ju)004:3911: zhes phan nus gnyis slob dpon gyi dbang zhes gcig tu bgrang nas bzhir gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:3912: slob dpon gyi dbang gtso bo dang gzhan rnams de'i 'khor yin pa la dgongs nas so //
NK067(ju)004:3913: de la phan dbang ni bcu ste /
NK067(ju)004:3914: snying po lnga dang dbu rgyan dang //
NK067(ju)004:3915: bum pa cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK067(ju)004:3916: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs phyag rgya //
NK067(ju)004:3917: bza' btung dbang rnams rim bzhin bskur //
NK067(ju)004:3918: zhes brgyud kyi dngos bstan zhi ba'i phan dbang yin la /
NK067(ju)004:3920: gdan dang lha dbang phyag mtshan dang //
NK067(ju)004:3921: chas bcu sgrub rdzas bco lnga ste //
NK067(ju)004:3922: zhes nyer brgyad du bshad do //
NK067(ju)004:3923: phan dbang bcu po de dag phal cher 'jig rten
NK067(ju)004:3924: na rgyal po chen po'i bu rgyal sar dbang skur
NK067(ju)004:3925: ba na steng du gdugs dang g.yas g.yon du rgyal
NK067(ju)004:3926: mtshan bsgreng / bum chus spyi bo nas blugs dbu
NK067(ju)004:3927: rgyan dang cod pan sogs byin nas byed pa dang
NK067(ju)004:3928: tshul mthun par bzhag pa dper na dus 'khor nas
NK067(ju)004:3929: byis pa ltar 'jug pa'i dbang bdun zhes gsungs pa
NK067(ju)004:3930: lta bur mngon nam snyam yang snga ma rnams kyis
NK067(ju)004:3931: bshad pa ma mthong bas kha tshon mi chod do
NK067(ju)004:3935: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang dang lnga ste /
NK067(ju)004:3936: phyi ma gsum po 'di las gzhan rnams slob dpon
NK067(ju)004:3937: gyi dbang ma yin yang dbang bzhi'i ya gyal gyi
NK067(ju)004:3938: slob dpon dbang yin par brjod zin la /
NK067(ju)004:3939: gsum po'i yang rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang gtso bo dang 'chad phrin de'i 'khor du bshad de /
NK067(ju)004:3940: des na rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang gi 'khor la slob dpon gyi dbang yin min gnyis yod do //
NK067(ju)004:3941: zab dbang gsum ni gsang sher tshig dbang gsum ste /
NK067(ju)004:3942: sher dbang la 'dir ye shes rang gnas dang /
NK067(ju)004:3943: dbang bzhi pa la dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang zhes kyang gsungs so //
NK067(ju)004:3944: dbang de dag thams cad la rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi re yod pa'i dang po rgyu gnyis las /
NK067(ju)004:3946: slob bu'i rgyud la dang po nas dbang so so'i
NK067(ju)004:3947: rjes su mthun pa'i chos re yod pa de yin
NK067(ju)004:3948: te / phan dbang dang sbyar na /
NK067(ju)004:3949: gong du smos ba'i go rim ltar nang gi bdud rtsi lnga dang /
NK067(ju)004:3951: rtsa gnas thig les gang ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:3953: d+h+au ti'i nang na thig le so gnyis gnas pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3954: lus rtsa'i d+r+wa bas khebs pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3957: rtog tshogs lha'i ngo bor gnas pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:3958: longs spyod 'khor lo'i thig le rnams su thal ba las gsungs shing /
NK067(ju)004:3959: nus dbang gi mtshungs ldan ni rim bzhin /
NK067(ju)004:3960: rna ba'i 'dom rtsa'i sgra nyan byed kyi thig le dang /
NK067(ju)004:3961: snying gi dran byed kyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3962: lag pa'i skyod byed kyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3964: yan lag lnga'i skyod byed reg shes kyi thig le rnams dang /
NK067(ju)004:3966: snying ga gtso bor gyur pa'i lus gnas bde ba'i rten gyi thig le dang /
NK067(ju)004:3967: 'od gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK067(ju)004:3968: bden pa dbyer med kyi ye shes gdod nas rang chas su bzhugs pa rnams go rim bzhin no //
NK067(ju)004:3969: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK067(ju)004:3970: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:3971: dbu rgyan dang phreng ba'i rin 'byung gi /
NK067(ju)004:3972: cod pan mtha' yas dang rdor sems kyi /
NK067(ju)004:3974: rgyal mtshan dang gdugs mi bskyod pa'i phyag rgya ni
NK067(ju)004:3975: kun mkhyen chen po rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan la bzhed
NK067(ju)004:3976: kyang 'dir dkyil 'khor ba'i sku gzugs te lha rang
NK067(ju)004:3977: rang gi / bum chu rigs lnga ka'i /
NK067(ju)004:3979: snying po lnga ni kun mkhyen bdud rtsi lnga la
NK067(ju)004:3980: bzhed kyang 'dir rigs lnga'i sa bon te gang ltar
NK067(ju)004:3981: yang rigs lnga so sos rab gnas can no //
NK067(ju)004:3982: de dag kyang sngon rab gnas byas pa tsam gyis mi chog gi /
NK067(ju)004:3983: dus der gang la dbang bskur ba de'i ched du rab gnas byas pa dgos so //
NK067(ju)004:3984: dbang rdzas gang du 'god pa'i mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)004:3985: yang lhan cig byed rgyur 'jog pa'am yang na bdag
NK067(ju)004:3986: rkyen gyi phyogs su bzhag par bya ste brtag go
NK067(ju)004:3987: // de bzhin du nus dbang gi dbang rdzas kyang /
NK067(ju)004:3989: phreng ba yi dam gang yin gyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3990: rgya gram don grub kyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3991: 'khor lo dung sogs mtha' yas kyi dang /
NK067(ju)004:3992: rdor dril rigs lnga spyi 'dus kyi rab gnas can rnams dang /
NK067(ju)004:3993: gsang dbang la rdo rje slob dpon gyi lhan skyes
NK067(ju)004:3994: kyi bde bas lhag par gnas pa'i bdud rtsi dang
NK067(ju)004:3995: / gong ma gnyis la byin gyis brlabsa pa'i phyag rgya ma'o //
NK067(ju)004:3996: rkyen bzhi'i dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni khog gzhung las /
NK067(ju)004:3997: dad dang brtson 'grus gsum ldan dang /
NK067(ju)004:3998: brtul zhugs gsum ldan sloob ma la //
NK067(ju)004:3999: zhes pa ltar dbang gi snod du rung ba'i slob ma ste /
NK067(ju)004:4000: phan dbang gi snod dad pa can dang /
NK067(ju)004:4001: nus dbang las nyan sgom gyi snod bdag don nus pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:4002: 'chad phrin gyi gzhan don nus pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:4003: rdo rje'i rgyal po'i gnyis ka'i don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can gsum dang /
NK067(ju)004:4004: gsang dbang gi spyod pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:4005: sher dbang gi rig pa'i dang /
NK067(ju)004:4006: dbang bzhi pa'i snod mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can te gsum rnams so //
NK067(ju)004:4007: 'dir bstan dad pa can ni sngags kyi theg pa la yid ches pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:4008: de'i rten du tshe 'adi'am snga mar theg chen spyi'i lam la blo sbyang ba'ang dgos so //
NK067(ju)004:4009: nus dbang gi snod la de'i steng du rgyud nyan
NK067(ju)004:4010: sgom sogs la dngos su 'jug pa'i brtson 'grus sam
NK067(ju)004:4012: zab dbang la de gnyis ka'i steng du brtul zhugs
NK067(ju)004:4013: gsum dang yang ldan pa snod du dgos zhes pa
NK067(ju)004:4014: yin gyi / phan dbang ma gtogs pa'i snod la dad pa can mi dgos pa sogs min no //
NK067(ju)004:4015: brtul zhugs gsum ni rim bzhin /
NK067(ju)004:4016: bde ba chen po'i lam mos pa brtan pas bdud
NK067(ju)004:4017: rtsi lnga la gtsang dme'i rtog pa zil gyis mnan
NK067(ju)004:4018: nas dngos su spyod nus pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:4019: chags rtog rang dga' ba zil gyis mnan nas rig ma'i bde ba lam du byed nus pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:4020: de'i sgo nas bden gnyis dbyer med mnyam pa chen
NK067(ju)004:4021: po'i don la dngos su 'jug nus pa gsum la
NK067(ju)004:4023: gtso bor dngos dbang gi snod la dgongs so //
NK067(ju)004:4024: gnyis pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK067(ju)004:4026: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK067(ju)004:4027: ces pa'i skabs ltar bsnyen pa tshad du 'khyol ba
NK067(ju)004:4028: sogs mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i slob dpon te de
NK067(ju)004:4029: las gzhan gyis dbang bskur lo byas kyang slob ma'i
NK067(ju)004:4030: rgyud smin mi nus shing bdag nyid rnam par sun
NK067(ju)004:4033: dbang rdzas dang sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gsum tshogs pa'i nus pa khyad par can te /
NK067(ju)004:4035: slob ma lhar gsal ba'i gnas lngar snying po lnga
NK067(ju)004:4036: bkod pa rigs lngar bskyed de byin gyis brlabsa pas
NK067(ju)004:4037: khams lnga rigs lngar dag pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:4038: dbu rgyan gyis tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag par dang /
NK067(ju)004:4039: bum pas rigs lnga'i chu rgyun gyi nyon mongs pa'i
NK067(ju)004:4040: dri ma dag nas ye shes lnga'i dbang thob par
NK067(ju)004:4041: dang / cod pan gyis yon tan rdzogs shing gdug pa 'dul ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:4042: phreng bas gzungs ting sogs 'bras chos rdzogs par dang /
NK067(ju)004:4043: go chas rgol bas mi tshugs par dang /
NK067(ju)004:4044: rgyal mtshan gyis log lta can zil gyis gnon par dang /
NK067(ju)004:4045: gdugs kyis nyon mongs pa'i tsha gdung las skyob par dang /
NK067(ju)004:4046: phyag rgyas rtogs pa lha'i ngo bor dag par dang /
NK067(ju)004:4047: bza' btung gis 'dod yon ye shes su rol ba'i
NK067(ju)004:4048: mthu thob bar bsam pa rnams phan dbang gi dgongs
NK067(ju)004:4049: pa yin la / der ma zad dkyil 'khor pa'i
NK067(ju)004:4050: lha rnams kyang de ltar dgongs pa mdzad par dmigs
NK067(ju)004:4051: pa yin la / dgos te / phan dbang lhag
NK067(ju)004:4052: pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor las thob par bshad
NK067(ju)004:4053: pa'i go don yang de'i steng nas shes par bya
NK067(ju)004:4055: de la dgongs nas phan dbang gi mtshams sbyor du
NK067(ju)004:4056: yang slob dpon gyis dkyil 'khor bskor zhing bstod nas
NK067(ju)004:4057: dbang bskur ba'i don du dgongs shing byin gyis rlob
NK067(ju)004:4058: par gsol ba 'debs tshul 'byung ba yin no //
NK067(ju)004:4059: nus dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)004:4060: sloob bu'i mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu rnams kyi gnas su
NK067(ju)004:4061: dbang rdzas rab gnas la bshad pa'i rigs gang yin
NK067(ju)004:4062: gyi tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor gsal spro bstims nas slob
NK067(ju)004:4063: ma rigs bzhi'i gtso bo dang kun tu bzang por
NK067(ju)004:4066: gsang dbang la nyi zla byang chub kyi sems rdo
NK067(ju)004:4067: rje sems dpa'i sku phra mo til gang phye ba
NK067(ju)004:4068: lta bur gyur pa snying ga'i 'khor lo la bstims
NK067(ju)004:4069: pas de na gnas pa'i rigs drug gi sa bon
NK067(ju)004:4070: gnyid dang bcas pa sbyangs nas sems nyid 'od gsal
NK067(ju)004:4071: gyi dkyil 'khor du bsgyur ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:4072: sher dbang la phyag rgya'i thabs kyis mtshon pa'i dpe'i ye shes rtogs pa dang /
NK067(ju)004:4073: dbang bzhi par mas brtan gyi dga' ba'i mtha'i lhan
NK067(ju)004:4074: skyes la brten nas bden gnyis zung 'jug gi dkyil
NK067(ju)004:4075: 'khor mthar thug ngo sprod pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK067(ju)004:4076: sgyu 'phrul thal ba las dbang bzhi pa bskur dus
NK067(ju)004:4077: dga' bzhi mtshan dpe dang mngon shes drug ldan du
NK067(ju)004:4079: de 'dra de bla ma bsu skyel sogs dang rnam
NK067(ju)004:4080: gnas yid byed kyis mtshan dpe dang mngon shes sgrub
NK067(ju)004:4081: pa'i phyogs dang thun mong ma yin par kun mkhyen
NK067(ju)004:4083: mdor na sngar thabs grol du bshad pa'i ye shes
NK067(ju)004:4084: kyi sku dang mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba'i thugs gnyis
NK067(ju)004:4085: ngo bo gcig tu gyur ba'i zung 'jug gi go
NK067(ju)004:4087: de ltar ngo sprod byed kyi dga' bzhi dngos ni
NK067(ju)004:4088: gleng bslang gi thad dang bsgrigs na mas brtan la
NK067(ju)004:4090: de'i steng nas ngo sprod tshul ni /
NK067(ju)004:4091: da lta dbang dus su skyes pa'i dga' bzhi 'di
NK067(ju)004:4092: dag gi rgyun goms pa las yas babs kyi dga'
NK067(ju)004:4093: ba bzhi gnas skabs bcu drug dang /
NK067(ju)004:4094: rten gyi dbye ba sum cu rtsa gnyis ye shes
NK067(ju)004:4095: kyi ro nyams brgyad cu mtshan dpe'i rgyu tshogs kyi
NK067(ju)004:4096: nus pa thams cad pa las byung ba'i mas brtan
NK067(ju)004:4097: gyi ye shes mtshan dpe dang mngon shes kyi yon
NK067(ju)004:4098: tan thams cad dang ldan par 'gyur ba yin zhes
NK067(ju)004:4100: da dung rdo rje las rim las /
NK067(ju)004:4101: pha rol phyin dang sa mtshan nyid //
NK067(ju)004:4102: mtshungs phyir rdzogs par bshad pa yin //
NK067(ju)004:4103: zhes sogs ltar mang du spro bar bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:4104: bzhi pa de ma thag rkyen ni /
NK067(ju)004:4105: dbang de dag go rim 'chol bar bskur du med kyi /
NK067(ju)004:4106: snga ma snga mas go phye nas gdod phyi ma
NK067(ju)004:4107: phyi ma bskur dgos pas zab dbang gi de ma
NK067(ju)004:4109: nus dbang gi de ma thag rkyen phan dbang yin pa sogs te /
NK067(ju)004:4110: dkyil 'khor du ma bcug pa la dbang bskur mi
NK067(ju)004:4111: rung ba 'di'i yang lugs yin pas phan dbang dang
NK067(ju)004:4112: po'i de ma thag rkyen dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa
NK067(ju)004:4113: la bzhag dgos pa sogs kyang 'dod chogs gam snyam
NK067(ju)004:4114: mo // de ltar na dbang bskur yul khams drug
NK067(ju)004:4115: ldan gyi rten can min na mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu
NK067(ju)004:4116: mo // ma tshang / dbang rdzas ma tshogs pa'am
NK067(ju)004:4117: tshogs kyang lhag gnas ma byas na lhan cig byed
NK067(ju)004:4118: mo // ma tshang / rgyu ma tshang / sngon
NK067(ju)004:4119: du slob bu'i rgyud sbyangs shing smin pa ma song
NK067(ju)004:4121: slob dpon gyis sngon du bsnyen pa sogs ma song
NK067(ju)004:4122: na dkyil 'khor gyi las la mi dbang bas bdag
NK067(ju)004:4123: po dang / yul rten de dag 'dzom yang slob
NK067(ju)004:4124: dpon gyis rdzas sngags ting 'dzin tshang bar 'du ma
NK067(ju)004:4125: po dang / byas pa dang / byas kyang slob
NK067(ju)004:4126: bus de la yid gtad nas mos pa ma bsgom
NK067(ju)004:4127: dmigs rkyen dang dmigs rkyen du 'gro ba'i yan lag
NK067(ju)004:4128: po dang / byas pa dang / dang / dbang
NK067(ju)004:4129: gi go rim 'khrugs shing bar du 'ga' zhig chad
NK067(ju)004:4130: na de ma thag rkyen ma tshang bar 'gyur la
NK067(ju)004:4131: po dang / byas pa dang / dang / /
NK067(ju)004:4132: shing rta 'phang lo nyams pa ltar rgyu tshogs kyi
NK067(ju)004:4133: yan lag ma tshang na dgos pa byed mi nus
NK067(ju)004:4134: pas thams cad tshang ba gces so //
NK067(ju)004:4135: de ltar tshang ba las lag rjes kyi khyad par gang dang gang 'byung ba ni /
NK067(ju)004:4136: phan dbang gis spyir gsang sngags kyi rigs su nges
NK067(ju)004:4137: par byed cing phyi dkyil drang don gyi bskyed rim
NK067(ju)004:4138: tsam mnyan pa la dbang ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:4139: nyan sgom gyi dbang gis nang lus la lha tshogs
NK067(ju)004:4140: rgyas par bkod pa'i snang byed kyi bskyed rim sogs
NK067(ju)004:4141: nyan sgom la dbang bar byed /
NK067(ju)004:4142: nus dbang lhag ma gsum gyi slob dpon gyi go
NK067(ju)004:4143: 'phang sbyin par mtshungs kyang 'chad phrin gnyis kyis rgyud
NK067(ju)004:4144: 'chad pa dang / las phra mo sgrub pa tsam la dbang bar byed la /
NK067(ju)004:4145: de tsam gyis dkyil 'khor chen po'i rdo rje slob dpon du gyur pa min zhing /
NK067(ju)004:4146: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang gis dkyil 'khor gyi las rab 'byams la dbang bar byed pas mi 'dra'o //
NK067(ju)004:4147: gsang dbang gis steng sgo'i rdzogs rim mam rang lus la gnad du bsnun pa la dang /
NK067(ju)004:4148: sher dbang gis 'og sgo'i lam mam gzhan lus pho nya'i rnal 'byor la dbang bsgrub par gsungs te /
NK067(ju)004:4150: gsang dbang gi lam rdzogs rim pa'i stong chen sogs ting nge 'dzin dang po bzhi dang /
NK067(ju)004:4151: sher dbang gi lam tshogs sgrub nas 'jog pa 'dra zhing /
NK067(ju)004:4152: gang ltar yang dbang bzhi pas gsang sher gyi lam
NK067(ju)004:4153: du thob pa'i ye shes de dag 'gyur med kyi
NK067(ju)004:4154: bde bar song ba'i go nas shin tu brtan par
NK067(ju)004:4155: byed de / dbang bzhi'i lam gyi rtogs pa 'di
NK067(ju)004:4156: dag thog mar skye ba la go rim gyi nges
NK067(ju)004:4157: byed de / pa yod kyang / gsang dbang gi
NK067(ju)004:4158: lam pa dang bum dbang ga lam pa 'gal ba
NK067(ju)004:4159: sogs mi bzhed dam snyam du sems mod kyi zab
NK067(ju)004:4160: mo'i gnas la kha tshon mi chod pas gzur gnas
NK067(ju)004:4161: mkhas pa rnams kyis zhib tu dpyad par bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:4162: dbang de rnams ma smin pa smin byed kyi dbang du bskur na rgyu'i dbang zhes bya la /
NK067(ju)004:4163: smin zin gyi nus pa gong 'phel du bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK067(ju)004:4164: rtsa ltung byung nas sngags sdom slar gso ba'i ched
NK067(ju)004:4165: du bla ma las nod pa'am rang nyid len pa
NK067(ju)004:4167: mthar lam pas rigs bdag drug pa dngos las nod pa ni 'bras bu'i dbang zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)004:4169: ston pa rdo rje 'chang gis khrims su bcas shing
NK067(ju)004:4170: sngags pa rnams kyis bsrung byar gyur pa'i bslab gzhi
NK067(ju)004:4171: khyad par can las mi 'da' ba'i sems pa sa
NK067(ju)004:4174: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK067(ju)004:4175: rmi lam du yang dam tshig brjod //
NK067(ju)004:4176: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK067(ju)004:4177: ces gsungs pa ltar rdo rje gsum gyi brtul zhugs la gnas pa'i cha nas dam tshig dang /
NK067(ju)004:4178: rgyud mi mthun phyogs las sdom pa'i cha nas sdom pa'ang yin no //
NK067(ju)004:4179: de srung ba la dang por bla ma las sngags sdom thob pa med du mi rung zhing /
NK067(ju)004:4180: de la thob pa'i dus mtshams shes nas thob blo skye ba gal che ste /
NK067(ju)004:4181: dus mtshams ni sngon gyi sgyu 'phrul mkhan po rnams
NK067(ju)004:4182: dbang gi snga rol du dang por thun mong gi
NK067(ju)004:4183: sdom bzung dang / de nas khyad par gyi sdom
NK067(ju)004:4184: bzung lan gsum re brjod pa'i mtha' la skye bar
NK067(ju)004:4185: sdom bzung dang / bzhed kyang / lugs 'dir rdo rje las rim las /
NK067(ju)004:4186: rang bzhin 'bru gsum sku gsung thugs //
NK067(ju)004:4187: gzi byin ldan par byin brlabsa la //
NK067(ju)004:4188: dam tshig sdom pa mchog ces bshad //
NK067(ju)004:4189: ces pa ltar dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i skabs su
NK067(ju)004:4190: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig byin pa nyid sdom
NK067(ju)004:4191: bzung du bzhed pas de'i mthar skye ba yin no
NK067(ju)004:4192: // de la dam pa kha cig ni /
NK067(ju)004:4193: sdom bzung gi dus su sngags sdom thob kyang sngags
NK067(ju)004:4194: sdom mtha' dag der bzung ba ni ma yin te
NK067(ju)004:4195: / da dung dbang so so'i ngo skal gyi sdom
NK067(ju)004:4196: pa mi 'dra ba mang po bzung dgos pa'i phyir
NK067(ju)004:4197: / zhes gsungs la / kha cig ni /
NK067(ju)004:4198: sngags sdom la ris mi 'dra ba mang po med kyi gcig tu zad la /
NK067(ju)004:4199: de khas blang gis bzung ba'i mthar thob kyang dbang
NK067(ju)004:4200: bskur dang ma 'brel ba'i khas blang gi brjod pa
NK067(ju)004:4201: lan gsum tsam gyis 'thob pa min zhing /
NK067(ju)004:4202: khas blang gis thob pa'i 'og tu dbang rnams bskur
NK067(ju)004:4203: bas sdom rgyun gong 'phel du 'gro ba yin zhes
NK067(ju)004:4204: gsungs ngo // thun mong byang chub sems dpa'i sdom
NK067(ju)004:4205: pa ni lus dbul gsum gyi skabs su skye bar
NK067(ju)004:4206: bshad kyang dam tshig gsum bkod dang bstun na rung
NK067(ju)004:4207: tsam snang yang 'di'i skor du de ltar bshad pa
NK067(ju)004:4208: gsungs ngo // ma mthong ngo // spyir dam tshig
NK067(ju)004:4209: gi rnam grangs mtha' yas kyang bsdu na rtsa ba
NK067(ju)004:4210: dang yan lag gnyis su 'du la /
NK067(ju)004:4211: de'ang rgyud gzhung 'di nyid las grags pa ltar na /
NK067(ju)004:4212: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK067(ju)004:4213: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu'o //
NK067(ju)004:4216: bla med mi spang bla ma bkur //
NK067(ju)004:4217: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyud mi bcad //
NK067(ju)004:4218: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK067(ju)004:4219: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK067(ju)004:4220: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te //
NK067(ju)004:4221: sgrub dang srung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK067(ju)004:4225: sngags rgya rgyun mi gcod pa /
NK067(ju)004:4227: gsang ba mi smra ba ste lnga las /
NK067(ju)004:4229: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi rang bzhin gyi
NK067(ju)004:4230: sems bskyed pa'am byang chub chen por 'bras bu lam
NK067(ju)004:4231: byed kyi tshul du sems bskyed pa mi spong ba
NK067(ju)004:4232: ste / sems kyi rang bzhin byang chub tu rtogs
NK067(ju)004:4233: pa'i lta ba gzhir bzung ste ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK067(ju)004:4234: rgyun du goms par byed pa las mi 'da' ba'o
NK067(ju)004:4235: ste / // de la sems nyid spros bral gyi
NK067(ju)004:4236: ngang la mnyam par 'jog pa don dam sems bskyed
NK067(ju)004:4237: ste / // dang / cir snang sems nyid kyi
NK067(ju)004:4238: rnam rol rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor nyag gcig tu shes
NK067(ju)004:4239: pa kun rdzob sems bskyed gnyis yod de /
NK067(ju)004:4240: rim bzhin zab pa dang rgya che ba'i sems gnyis so //
NK067(ju)004:4241: sems de gnyis mthar phyin par gdul byas myur du
NK067(ju)004:4242: 'grub pa'i ched du sangs rgyas rnams kyis shin tu
NK067(ju)004:4243: rnam dag gi bden gnyis zung 'jug lha'i rnam par
NK067(ju)004:4244: byin gyis brlabsa pa la de ltar shes nas bsgom
NK067(ju)004:4245: na bla med byang chub kyi sems gnyis ka der
NK067(ju)004:4246: 'du bar sngon gyi mkhas grub dag gis gsungs te
NK067(ju)004:4247: / 'dir kun rdzob byang sems gtso bor sgom pa'i
NK067(ju)004:4248: tshe yang snang ba rang rgyud pa ma yin par
NK067(ju)004:4249: lhag pa kun rdzob ces ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil
NK067(ju)004:4250: 'khor du sgom pas don dam sems bskyed kyi snying
NK067(ju)004:4252: don dam sems bskyed la mnyam par 'jog pa na
NK067(ju)004:4253: yang tha mal pa'i dngos snang gi rang bzhin stong
NK067(ju)004:4254: par sgom pa dang mi 'dra bar dag pa'i dkyil
NK067(ju)004:4255: 'khor thams cad don dam 'od gsal gyi thig le
NK067(ju)004:4256: gcig tu bsdus nas sgom pa yin pas kun rdzob
NK067(ju)004:4257: sems bskyed kyi snying po can te /
NK067(ju)004:4258: tshul de lta bus byang chub kyi sems gnyis skad
NK067(ju)004:4259: cig tsam yang ya bral du ma song ba'i sgo
NK067(ju)004:4260: nas tshogs gnyis rlabs po che bsdu ba la bslab
NK067(ju)004:4261: par bya'o // gsang ba bla med 'dir bcas mtshams
NK067(ju)004:4262: thun mong ma yin pa 'di lta bu yod pa
NK067(ju)004:4263: par bya'o // la dgongs nas / bde gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs //
NK067(ju)004:4264: 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK067(ju)004:4265: zhes dam tshig bsrung na sangs rgyas nyid dang spyod
NK067(ju)004:4266: yul gcig pa dang kun tu bzang po'i rgyal srid
NK067(ju)004:4267: lag mthil na gnas pa lta bur gsungs pa yin
NK067(ju)004:4268: te / 'dul sdom 'dus pa'i che ba dang /
NK067(ju)004:4269: spyod sgo yangs pa'i che ba bshad pa rnams kyang
NK067(ju)004:4270: gnad 'di la gtug dgos par dam bsgrags kyi skabs
NK067(ju)004:4271: las shes shing / rtsa ba'i dam tshig lhag ma bzhi yang 'di'i ched du bcas par snang ngo //
NK067(ju)004:4273: bkur ba'i yul bde 'dus zhi rgyud las /
NK067(ju)004:4274: rgyud 'grol dbang bskur de nyid bstan //
NK067(ju)004:4278: snying po'i don gyi man ngag ston pa ste /
NK067(ju)004:4279: rdo rje theg pa'i chos kyi bka' drin nod pa'i
NK067(ju)004:4280: bla ma gang yin yang sangs rgyas thams cad dang
NK067(ju)004:4281: mnyam par bltas nas dngos po thams cad kyis mchod
NK067(ju)004:4283: bla ma sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam tshul ni /
NK067(ju)004:4284: sangs rgyas thams cad rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku
